Original English: Author of the danger trail, Philip Steels, etc.
English: author of the danger trail, philip steels, etc.
Hindi: ऑथर अव द डेंजर ट्रेल, फिलिप स्टील्स, एट्सेट्रा.
Korean: 어서 어브 더 데인저 트레일, 필립 스틸스, 엣세트라.

Original English: Not at this particular case, Tom, apologized Whittemore.
English: not at this particular case, tom, apologized whittemore.
Hindi: नॉट ऐट दिस पर्टिक्युलर केस, टॉम, अपालजाइज्ड विटिमोर.
Korean: 낫 앳 디스 퍼티큘러 케이스, 탐, 어폴러자이즈드 위트모어.

Original English: For the twentieth time that evening the two men shook hands.
English: for the twentieth time that evening the two men shook hands.
Hindi: फॉर द ट्वेंटीएथ टाइम दैट ईवनिंग द टू मेन शुक हैंड्स.
Korean: 포어 더 트웬티엣 타임 댓 이브닝 더 투 멘 슉 핸즈.

Original English: Lord, but I'm glad to see you again, Phil.
English: lord, but i am glad to see you again, phil.
Hindi: लॉर्ड, बट आई ऐम ग्लैड टू सी यू अगेन, फिल.
Korean: 로드, 벗 아이 앰 글래드 투 씨 유 어겐, 필.

Original English: Will we ever forget it.
English: will we ever forget it.
Hindi: विल वी एवर फरगेट इट.
Korean: 윌 위 에버 포겟 잇.

Original English: God bless 'em, I hope I'll go on seeing them forever.
English: god bless 'em, i hope i will go on seeing them forever.
Hindi: गॉड ब्लेस एम, आई होप आई विल गो ऑन सीइंग देम फॉरएवर.
Korean: 갓 블레스 엠, 아이 호프 아이 윌 고 온 씨잉 뎀 포에버.

Original English: And you always want to see it in the superlative degree.
English: and you always want to see it in the superlative degree.
Hindi: ऐंड यू ऑलवेज़ वांट टू सी इट इन द सुपरलैटिव डिग्री.
Korean: 앤드 유 올웨이즈 원트 투 씨 잇 인 더 수펄러티브 디그리.

Original English: Gad, your letter came just in time.
English: gad, your letter came just in time.
Hindi: गैड, योर लेटर केम जस्ट इन टाइम.
Korean: 갯, 유어 레터 케임 저스트 인 타임.

Original English: He turned sharply, and faced Gregson across the table.
English: he turned sharply, and faced gregson across the table.
Hindi: ही टर्न्ड शार्पली, ऐंड फेस्ड ग्रेगसन अक्रॉस द टेबल.
Korean: 히 턴드 샤플리, 앤드 페이스드 그렉슨 어크로스 더 테이블.

Original English: I'm playing a single hand in what looks like a losing game.
English: i am playing a single hand in what looks like a losing game.
Hindi: आई ऐम प्लेइंग अ सिंगल हैंड इन वट लुक्स लाइक अ लूजिंग गेम.
Korean: 아이 앰 플레잉 아 싱글 핸드 인 왓 룩스 라이크 아 루징 게임.

Original English: If I ever needed a fighter in my life I need one now.
English: if i ever needed a fighter in my life i need one now.
Hindi: इफ आई एवर नीडेड अ फाइटर इन माइ लाइफ आई नीड वन नाउ.
Korean: 이프 아이 에버 니디드 아 파이터 인 마이 라이프 아이 니드 원 나우.

Original English: Gregson shoved back his chair and rose to his feet.
English: gregson shoved back his chair and rose to his feet.
Hindi: ग्रेगसन शव्ड बैक हिज चेयर ऐंड रोज़ टू हिज फीट.
Korean: 그렉슨 셔브드 백 히즈 체어 앤드 로즈 투 히즈 피트.

Original English: He was a head shorter than his companion, of almost delicate physique.
English: he was a head shorter than his companion, of almost delicate physique.
Hindi: ही वज़ अ हेड शॉर्टर धन हिज कम्पैनियन, अव ऑलमोस्ट डेलिकेट फिजीक.
Korean: 히 워즈 아 헤드 쇼터 댄 히즈 컴패니언, 어브 올모스트 델리켓 피지크.

Original English: Now you're coming down to business, Phil, he exclaimed.
English: now you are coming down to business, phil, he exclaimed.
Hindi: नाउ यू आर कमिंग डाउन टू बिजनेस, फिल, ही एक्सक्लेम्ड.
Korean: 나우 유 아 커밍 다운 투 비즈니스, 필, 히 엑스클레임드.

Original English: It's the aurora borealis.
English: it's the aurora borealis.
Hindi: इट्स दि औरोरा बोरेलिस.
Korean: 잇츠 디 오로라 보리앨리스.

Original English: There's Fort Churchill, a rifle-shot beyond the ridge, asleep.
English: there's fort churchill, a rifle-shot beyond the ridge, asleep.
Hindi: देर्स फॉर्ट चर्चिल, अ राइफल-शॉट बियॉन्ड द रिज, अस्लीप.
Korean: 데어즈 포트 처칠, 아 라이플샷 비욘드 더 리지, 어슬립.

Original English: From that moment his friendship for Belize turns to hatred and jealousy.
English: from that moment his friendship for belize turns to hatred and jealousy.
Hindi: फ्रॉम धैट मोमेंट हिज फ्रेंडशिप फॉर बेलीज़ टर्न्स टू हेट्रेड एंड जेलसी.
Korean: 프럼 댓 모먼트 히즈 프렌드십 포어 벨리즈 턴즈 투 헤이트리드 앤드 젤러시.

Original English: There was a change now.
English: there was a change now.
Hindi: देयर वस अ चेंज नाउ.
Korean: 데어 워즈 아 체인지 나우.

Original English: I followed the line of the proposed railroad, looking for chances.
English: i followed the line of the proposed railroad, looking for chances.
Hindi: आई फालोड द लाइन अव द प्रपोज़्ड रेलरोड, लुकिंग फॉर चांसेज़.
Korean: 아이 팔로우드 더 라인 어브 더 프로포즈드 레일로드, 루킹 포 찬시즈.

Original English: Clubs and balls and cities grew to be only memories.
English: clubs and balls and cities grew to be only memories.
Hindi: क्लब्स ऐंड बॉल्स ऐंड सिटीज़ ग्रो टू बी ओनली मेमोरीज़.
Korean: 클럽즈 앤드 볼즈 앤드 시티즈 그루 투 비 온리 메모리즈.

Original English: It fairly clubbed me into recognizing it.
English: it fairly clubbed me into recognizing it.
Hindi: इट फेरली क्लब्ड मी इंटु रेकग्नाइजिंग इट.
Korean: 잇 페얼리 클럽드 미 인투 레커그나이징 잇.

Original English: Hardly were our plans made public before we were met by powerful opposition.
English: hardly were our plans made public before we were met by powerful opposition.
Hindi: हार्डली वर आवर प्लैन्स मेड पब्लिक बिफोर वी वर मेट बाय पावरफुल ऑपोज़िशन.
Korean: 하드리 워 아워 플랜즈 메이드 퍼블릭 비포어 위 워 메트 바이 파워풀 오퍼지션.

Original English: A combination of Canadian capital quickly organized and petitioned for the same privileges.
English: a combination of canadian capital quickly organized and petitioned for the same privileges.
Hindi: अ कॉम्बिनेशन अव कनेडियन कैपिटल क्विकली ऑर्गनाइज़्ड ऐंड पेटीशन्ड फॉर द सेम प्रिविलेजेस.
Korean: 아 컴비네이션 오브 캐네이디언 캐피털 퀵클리 오르가나이즈드 앤드 퍼티션드 포어 더 세임 프리빌리지즈.

Original English: It was my reports from the north which chiefly induced people to buy.
English: it was my reports from the north which chiefly induced people to buy.
Hindi: इट वज माई रिपोर्ट्स फ्रम द नॉर्थ विच चीफली इंड्यूस्ट पीपल टू बाई.
Korean: 잇 워즈 마이 리포츠 프럼 더 노스 위치 치플리 인듀스트 피플 투 바이.

Original English: I was about to do this when cooler judgment prevailed.
English: i was about to do this when cooler judgment prevailed.
Hindi: आई वस अबाउट टू डू दिस वेन कूलर जजमेंट प्रिवेल्ड.
Korean: 아이 워즈 어바웃 투 두 디스 웬 쿨러 저지먼트 프리베일드.

Original English: It occurred to me that there would have to be an accounting.
English: it occurred to me that there would have to be an accounting.
Hindi: इट अकर्ड टू मी दॅट धेर वुड हॅव टू बी अन अकाउंटिंग.
Korean: 잇 어커드 투 미 댓 데어 우드 해브 투 비 안 어카운팅.

Original English: To my surprise he began to show actual enthusiasm in my favor.
English: to my surprise he began to show actual enthusiasm in my favor.
Hindi: टू माई सरप्राइज ही बिगैन टू शो ऐक्चुअल एन्थुजियाज्म इन माई फेवर.
Korean: 투 마이 서프라이즈 히 비갠 투 쇼 액추얼 엔수시아즘 인 마이 페이버.

Original English: Robbery, bribery, fraud,
English: robbery, bribery, fraud,
Hindi: रॉबरी, ब्राइबरी, फ्रॉड,
Korean: 로버리, 브라이버리, 프로드,

Original English: Their forces were already moving into the north country.
English: their forces were already moving into the north country.
Hindi: देर फोर्सेस वेर ऑलरेडी मूविंग इंटु द नॉर्थ कंट्री.
Korean: 데어 포스 워 올레디 무빙 인투 더 노스 컨트리.

Original English: I had faith in them.
English: i had faith in them.
Hindi: आई हैड फेथ इन देम.
Korean: 아이 해드 페이스 인 뎀.

Original English: They were three hundred yards apart.
English: they were three hundred yards apart.
Hindi: थे वर थ्री हन्ड्रेड यार्ड्स अपार्ट.
Korean: 데이 워 쓰리 헌드레드 야즈 어파트.

Original English: Since then some mysterious force has been fighting us at every step.
English: since then some mysterious force has been fighting us at every step.
Hindi: सिंस देन सम मिस्टीरियस फोर्स हैज बीन फाइटिंग अस ऐट एवरी स्टेप.
Korean: 신스 덴 섬 미스테리어스 포스 해즈 빈 파이팅 어스 앳 에브리 스텝.

Original English: He unfolded a long typewritten letter, and handed it to Gregson.
English: he unfolded a long typewritten letter, and handed it to gregson.
Hindi: ही अनफोल्डेड अ लॉंग टाइपरिटन लेटर, ऐंड हैंडेड इट टू ग्रेगसन.
Korean: 히 언폴디드 아 롱 타이프리튼 레터, 앤드 핸디드 잇 투 그렉슨.

Original English: Men of Selden's stamp don't stop at women and children.
English: men of selden's stamp do not stop at women and children.
Hindi: मेन अव सेल्डन स्टैम्प डू नाट स्टॉप ऐट विमिन ऐन्ड चिल्ड्रन.
Korean: 멘 어브 셀든즈 스탬프 두 낫 스탑 앳 우먼 앤드 칠드런.

Original English: He stopped, and Philip nodded at the horrified question in his eyes.
English: he stopped, and philip nodded at the horrified question in his eyes.
Hindi: ही स्टॉप्ड, ऐंड फिलिप नॉडेड ऐट द हॉरिफाइड क्वेश्चन इन हिज आइज़.
Korean: 히 스탑트, 앤드 필립 나디드 앳 더 호리파이드 퀘스천 인 히즈 아이즈.

Original English: She turned in at the hotel.
English: she turned in at the hotel.
Hindi: शी टर्न्ड इन ऐट द होटल.
Korean: 시 턴드 인 앳 더 호텔.

Original English: I was the only one who remained sitting.
English: i was the only one who remained sitting.
Hindi: आई वज दि ओनली वन हू रिमेंड सिटिंग.
Korean: 아이 워즈 디 온리 원 후 리메인드 시팅.

Original English: We'll have to watch our chances.
English: we will have to watch our chances.
Hindi: वी विल हैव टू वॉच आवर चांसिस.
Korean: 위 윌 해브 투 와치 아우어 챈시즈.

Original English: The ship should be in within a week or ten days.
English: the ship should be in within a week or ten days.
Hindi: द शिप शुड बी इन विधिन अ वीक और टेन डेज.
Korean: 더 쉽 슏 비 인 위딘 아 윅 오 텐 데이즈.

Original English: I suppose you wonder why she is coming up here.
English: i suppose you wonder why she is coming up here.
Hindi: आई सपोज़ यू वंडर वाय शी इज़ कमिंग अप हियर.
Korean: 아이 서포즈 유 원더 와이 쉬 이즈 커밍 업 히어.

Original English: Meanwhile I'll go out to breathe a spell.
English: meanwhile i will go out to breathe a spell.
Hindi: मीनवाइल आई विल गो आउट टू ब्रीद अ स्पेल.
Korean: 민와일 아이 윌 고 아웃 투 브리드 아 스펠.

Original English: How could he explain his possession of the sketch.
English: how could he explain his possession of the sketch.
Hindi: हाउ कुड ही एक्सप्लेन हिस पज़ेशन अव द स्केच.
Korean: 하우 쿧 히 익스플레인 히즈 포세션 어브 더 스케치.

Original English: It seemed nearer to him since he had seen and talked with Gregson.
English: it seemed nearer to him since he had seen and talked with gregson.
Hindi: इट सीम्ड नियर टू हिम सिंस ही हैड सीन एंड टॉक्ड विद ग्रेगसन.
Korean: 잇 심드 니러 투 힘 신스 히 핫 신 앤드 톡트 위드 그렉슨.

Original English: Her own betrayal of herself was like tonic to Philip.
English: her own betrayal of herself was like tonic to philip.
Hindi: हर ओन बिट्रेयल अव हर्सेल्फ वज़ लाइक टॉनिक टू फिलिप.
Korean: 허 온 비트레이얼 어브 허셀프 워즈 라이크 토닉 투 필립.

Original English: He moved away as quietly as he had come.
English: he moved away as quietly as he had come.
Hindi: ही मूव्ड अवे अज क्वाइटली अज ही हैड कम.
Korean: 히 무브드 어웨이 애즈 콰이틀리 애즈 히 해드 컴.

Original English: The girl faced him, her eyes shining with sudden fear.
English: the girl faced him, her eyes shining with sudden fear.
Hindi: द गर्ल फेस्ड हिम, हर आइज़ शाइनिंग विद सडन फियर.
Korean: 더 걸 페이스트 힘, 허 아이즈 샤이닝 위드 서든 피어.

Original English: Close beside him gleamed the white fangs of the wolf-dog.
English: close beside him gleamed the white fangs of the wolf-dog.
Hindi: क्लोस बिसाइड हिम ग्लीम्ड द व्हाइट फैंग्स अव द वुल्फ-डॉग.
Korean: 클로즈 비사이드 힘 글림드 더 화이트 팽즈 어브 더 울프도그.

Original English: He looked at the handkerchief more, closely.
English: he looked at the handkerchief more, closely.
Hindi: ही लुकट ऐट द हैंडकरचीफ मोर, क्लोसली.
Korean: 히 룩트 앳 더 핸드커치프 모어, 클로슬리.

Original English: Gregson was asleep when he re-entered the cabin.
English: gregson was asleep when he re-entered the cabin.
Hindi: ग्रेगसन वज़ अस्लीप वेन ही री-एंटर्ड द कैबिन.
Korean: 그렉슨 워즈 어슬립 웬 히 리엔터드 더 캐빈.

Original English: In spite of their absurdity the words affected Philip curiously.
English: in spite of their absurdity the words affected philip curiously.
Hindi: इन स्पाइट अव देर अबसर्डिटी द वर्ड्स अफेक्टेड फिलिप क्यूरियसली.
Korean: 인 스파이트 어브 데어 앱설러티 더 워즈 어펙티드 필립 큐리어슬리.

Original English: The lace was of a delicate ivory color, faintly tinted with yellow.
English: the lace was of a delicate ivory color, faintly tinted with yellow.
Hindi: द लेस वज़ अव अ डेलिकेट आइवरी कलर, फेंटली टिन्टेड विथ येलो.
Korean: 더 레이스 워즈 어브 아 델리컷 아이보리 컬러, 페인트리 틴티드 위드 옐로우.

Original English: It was a curious coincidence.
English: it was a curious coincidence.
Hindi: इट वस अ क्यूरियस कोइंसिडेंस.
Korean: 잇 워즈 아 큐리어스 코인시던스.

Original English: Suddenly his fingers closed tightly over the handkerchief.
English: suddenly his fingers closed tightly over the handkerchief.
Hindi: सडनली हिस फिंगर्स क्लोज़्ड टाइटली ओवर द हैंडकरचीफ.
Korean: 서든리 히즈 핑거즈 클로즈드 타이틀리 오버 더 핸드커치프.

Original English: There was nothing on the rock.
English: there was nothing on the rock.
Hindi: देर वस नथिंग ऑन द रॉक.
Korean: 데어 와즈 너씽 온 더 락.

Original English: Philip stood undecided, his ears strained to catch the slightest sound.
English: philip stood undecided, his ears strained to catch the slightest sound.
Hindi: फिलिप स्टुड अनडिसाइडेड, हिज़ इयर्स स्ट्रेन्ड टू कैच द स्लाइटेस्ट साउंड.
Korean: 필립 스투드 언디사이디드, 히즈 이어즈 스트레인드 투 캐치 더 슬라이티스트 사운드.

Original English: Pearce's little eyes were fixed on him shrewdly.
English: pearce's little eyes were fixed on him shrewdly.
Hindi: पिर्सिज लिटल आइज़ वर फिक्स्ट ऑन हिम श्रूडली.
Korean: 피어시즈 리틀 아이즈 워 픽스트 온 힘 슈루들리.

Original English: I have no idea, replied Philip.
English: i have no idea, replied philip.
Hindi: आई हैव नो आइडिया, रिप्लाइड फिलिप.
Korean: 아이 해브 노 아이디어, 리플라이드 필립.

Original English: I came for information more out of curiosity than anything else.
English: i came for information more out of curiosity than anything else.
Hindi: आई केम फॉर इन्फ़ार्मेशन मोर आउट अव क्यूरिओसिटी धान एनीथिंग एल्स.
Korean: 아이 케임 포 인포메이션 모어 아웃 어브 큐리어시티 댄 애니씽 엘스.

Original English: His immaculate appearance was gone.
English: his immaculate appearance was gone.
Hindi: हिस इमैक्युलेट अपिरेंस वज़ गॉन.
Korean: 히즈 이매큘럿 어피어런스 워즈 곤.

Original English: Anyway, no one saw her like that.
English: anyway, no one saw her like that.
Hindi: ऐनिवे, नो वन सॉ हर लाइक दैट.
Korean: 에니웨이, 노 원 소 허 라이크 댓.

Original English: Philip snatched at the letter which Gregson held out to him.
English: philip snatched at the letter which gregson held out to him.
Hindi: फिलिप स्नैचट ऐट द लेटर विच ग्रेगसन हेल्ड आउट टू हिम.
Korean: 필립 스내치드 앳 더 레터 위치 그렉슨 헬드 아웃 투 힘.

Original English: The men stared into each other's face.
English: the men stared into each other's face.
Hindi: द मेन स्टेर्ड इंटू ईच अदर्स फेस.
Korean: 더 멘 스테어드 인투 이치 어더즈 페이스.

Original English: Yes, it was a man who asked, a stranger.
English: yes, it was a man who asked, a stranger.
Hindi: येस, इट वस अ मैन हू आस्क्ट, अ स्ट्रेंजर.
Korean: 예스, 잇 워즈 아 맨 후 애스크트, 아 스트레인저.

Original English: The fourth and fifth days passed without any developments.
English: the fourth and fifth days passed without any developments.
Hindi: द फोर्थ एंड फिफ्थ डेज़ पास्त विदाउट एनी डेवेलपमेंट्स.
Korean: 더 포스 앤드 피프스 데이즈 패스트 위다웃 에니 디벨롭먼츠.

Original English: They closed now until his fingers were like cords of steel.
English: they closed now until his fingers were like cords of steel.
Hindi: दे क्लोज्ड नाउ अंतिल हिज फिंगर्स वर लाइक कॉर्ड्स अव स्टील.
Korean: 데이 클로즈드 나우 언틸 히즈 핑거즈 워 라이크 코르즈 오브 스틸.

Original English: He saw Jeanne falter for a moment.
English: he saw jeanne falter for a moment.
Hindi: ही सॉ जीन फाल्टर फॉर अ मोमेंट.
Korean: 히 쏘 진 팔터 포 아 모먼트.

Original English: Surely I will excuse you, she cried.
English: surely i will excuse you, she cried.
Hindi: शुरली आई विल एक्सक्यूस यू, शी क्राइड.
Korean: 슈얼리 아이 윌 엑스큐즈 유, 쉬 크라이드.

Original English: In a flash Philip followed its direction.
English: in a flash philip followed its direction.
Hindi: इन अ फ्लैश फिलिप फॉलोड इट्स डिरेक्शन.
Korean: 인 아 플래시 필립 팔로우드 잇츠 디렉션.

Original English: It was his intention to return to Eileen and her father.
English: it was his intention to return to eileen and her father.
Hindi: इट वज़ हिज़ इंटेंशन टू रिटर्न टू आइलीन ऐंड हर फादर.
Korean: 잇 와즈 히즈 인텐션 투 리턴 투 아일린 앤드 허 파더.

Original English: He would first hunt up Gregson and begin his work there.
English: he would first hunt up gregson and begin his work there.
Hindi: ही वुड फर्स्ट हंट अप ग्रेगसन ऐंड बिगिन हिस वर्क देर.
Korean: 히 우드 퍼스트 헌트 업 그렉슨 앤드 비긴 히즈 워크 데어.

Original English: What was the object of your little sensation.
English: what was the object of your little sensation.
Hindi: व्हट वस दि ऑब्जेक्ट अव योर लिटल सेंसेशन.
Korean: 왓 워즈 디 옵젝트 오브 유어 리틀 센세이션.

Original English: But who was Eileen's double.
English: but who was eileen's double.
Hindi: बट हू वज आइलीन्स डबल.
Korean: 벗 후 워즈 아일린즈 더블.

Original English: The promoter's eyes were heavy, with little puffy bags under them.
English: the promoter's eyes were heavy, with little puffy bags under them.
Hindi: द प्रमोटर्स आइज़ वेर हेवी, विथ लिटल पफी बैग्स अंडर देम.
Korean: 더 프로모터즈 아이즈 워 헤비, 위드 리틀 퍼피 백스 언더 뎀.

Original English: And now, down there, Eileen was waiting for him.
English: and now, down there, eileen was waiting for him.
Hindi: एंड नाउ, डाउन देयर, आइलीन वस वेटिंग फॉर हिम.
Korean: 앤드 나우, 다운 데어, 아일린 워즈 웨이팅 포어 힘.

Original English: There has been a change, she interrupted him.
English: there has been a change, she interrupted him.
Hindi: धेर हैज़ बीन अ चेंज, शी इंटर्रप्टेड हिम.
Korean: 데어 해즈 빈 아 체인지, 쉬 인터럽티드 힘.

Original English: The gray eyes faltered; the flush deepened.
English: the gray eyes faltered the flush deepened.
Hindi: द ग्रे आइज़ फाल्टर्ड द फ्लश डीपेंड.
Korean: 더 그레이 아이즈 폴터드 더 플러쉬 디펀드.

Original English: It is the fire, partly, she said.
English: it is the fire, partly, she said.
Hindi: इट इज़ द फायर, पार्टली, शी सैड.
Korean: 잇 이즈 더 파이어, 파트리, 쉬 셋.

Original English: Then, and at supper, he tried to fathom her.
English: then, and at supper, he tried to fathom her.
Hindi: धेन, एंड ऐट सपर, ही ट्राइड टू फैदम हर.
Korean: 덴, 앤드 앳 서퍼, 히 트라이드 투 패덤 허.

Original English: It was a large canoe.
English: it was a large canoe.
Hindi: इट वज़ अ लार्ज कनू.
Korean: 잇 워즈 아 라지 카누.

Original English: What if Jeanne failed him.
English: what if jeanne failed him.
Hindi: वट इफ जीन फेल्ड हिम.
Korean: 왓 이프 진 페일드 힘.

Original English: What if she did not come to the rock.
English: what if she did not come to the rock.
Hindi: व्हट इफ शी डिड नॉट कम टू द रॉक.
Korean: 왓 이프 시 딛 낫 컴 투 더 록.

Original English: His face was streaming with blood.
English: his face was streaming with blood.
Hindi: हिज़ फेस वज़ स्ट्रीमिंग विद ब्लड.
Korean: 히즈 페이스 워즈 스트리밍 위드 블러드.

Original English: A shadow was creeping over Pierre's eyes.
English: a shadow was creeping over pierre's eyes.
Hindi: अ शैडो वज़ क्रीपिंग ओवर पियरेज़ आइज़.
Korean: 아 샤도우 워즈 크리핑 오버 피어레스 아이즈.

Original English: Scarcely had he uttered the name when Pierre's closing eyes shot open.
English: scarcely had he uttered the name when pierre's closing eyes shot open.
Hindi: स्कार्सली हैड ही अटर्ड द नेम वेन पिराज़ क्लोसिंग आइज़ शॉट ओपन.
Korean: 스케얼슬리 해드 히 어터드 더 네임 웬 피에레즈 클로징 아이즈 샷 오픈.

Original English: A trickle of fresh blood ran over his face.
English: a trickle of fresh blood ran over his face.
Hindi: अ ट्रिकल अव फ्रेश ब्लड रैन ओवर हिस फेस.
Korean: 아 트리클 어브 프레쉬 블러드 랜 오버 히즈 페이스.

Original English: Death had come with terrible suddenness.
English: death had come with terrible suddenness.
Hindi: डेथ हैड कम विथ टेरिबल सडनेस.
Korean: 데스 해드 컴 위드 테러블 서든니스.

Original English: Philip bent lower, and stared into the face of the dead man.
English: philip bent lower, and stared into the face of the dead man.
Hindi: फिलिप बेंट लोअर, एंड स्टेर्ड इंटू द फेस अव द डेड मैन.
Korean: 필립 벤트 로어, 앤드 스테어드 인투 더 페이스 오브 더 데드 맨.

Original English: He made sure that the magazine was loaded, and resumed his paddling.
English: he made sure that the magazine was loaded, and resumed his paddling.
Hindi: ही मेड शुर दॅट द मैगज़ीन वज़ लोडेड, ऐंड रिस्यूम्ड हिज़ पैडलिंग.
Korean: 히 메이드 슈어 댓 더 매거진 워즈 로디드, 앤드 리줌드 히즈 패들링.

Original English: The nightglow was treacherous to shoot by.
English: the nightglow was treacherous to shoot by.
Hindi: द नाइटग्लो वज़ ट्रेचरस टू शूट बाय.
Korean: 더 나잇글로우 워즈 트레처러스 투 슛 바이.

Original English: The singing voice approached rapidly.
English: the singing voice approached rapidly.
Hindi: द सिंगिंग वॉइस अप्रोच्ड रैपिडली.
Korean: 더 싱잉 보이스 어프로치트 래피들리.

Original English: His blood grew hot with rage at the thought.
English: his blood grew hot with rage at the thought.
Hindi: हिज़ ब्लड ग्रू हॉट विद रेज ऐट द थॉट.
Korean: 히즈 블러드 그루 핫 위드 레이지 앳 더 쏫.

Original English: He went down in midstream, searching the shadows of both shores.
English: he went down in midstream, searching the shadows of both shores.
Hindi: ही वेंट डाउन इन मिडस्ट्रीम, सर्चिंग द शैडोज़ अव बोथ शोर्स.
Korean: 히 웬트 다운 인 미드스트림, 서칭 더 섀도우즈 오브 보스 쇼어즈.

Original English: For a full minute he crouched and listened.
English: for a full minute he crouched and listened.
Hindi: फॉर अ फुल मिनिट ही क्राउच्ड एंड लिसन्ड.
Korean: 포어 아 풀 미닛 히 크라우치트 앤드 리슨드.

Original English: He had barely entered this when he saw the glow of a fire.
English: he had barely entered this when he saw the glow of a fire.
Hindi: ही हैड बेरली एन्टर्ड दिस वेन ही सॉ द ग्लो ऑफ अ फायर.
Korean: 히 핻 베얼리 엔터드 디스 웬 히 소 더 글로 어브 아 파이어.

Original English: A big canvas tent was the first thing to come within his vision.
English: a big canvas tent was the first thing to come within his vision.
Hindi: अ बिग कैनवस टेंट वज द फर्स्ट थिंग टू कम विथिन हिस विजन.
Korean: 아 빅 캔버스 텐트 워즈 더 퍼스트 씽 투 컴 위딘 히즈 비전.

Original English: Perhaps she had already met her fate a little deeper in the forest.
English: perhaps she had already met her fate a little deeper in the forest.
Hindi: परहैप्स शी हैड ऑलरेडी मेट हर फेट अ लिटल डीपर इन द फॉरेस्ट.
Korean: 퍼헵스 쉬 핻 올레디 메트 허 페이트 아 리틀 디퍼 인 더 포레스트.

Original English: Then you can arrange yourself comfortably among these robes in the bow.
English: then you can arrange yourself comfortably among these robes in the bow.
Hindi: देन यू कैन अरेंज योरसेल्फ कम्फटेबली अमंग दीज़ रोब्स इन द बो.
Korean: 덴 유 캔 어레인지 유어셀프 컴포터블리 어몽 디즈 로브스 인 더 보우.

Original English: Shall I carry you.
English: shall i carry you.
Hindi: शैल आई कैरी यू.
Korean: 샬 아이 캐리 유.

Original English: A maddening joy pounded in his brain.
English: a maddening joy pounded in his brain.
Hindi: अ मैडनिंग जॉय पाउंडेड इन हिस ब्रेन.
Korean: 아 매드닝 조이 파운디드 인 히즈 브레인.

Original English: You must sleep, he urged.
English: you must sleep, he urged.
Hindi: यू मस्ट स्लीप, ही अर्ज्ड.
Korean: 유 머스트 슬립, 히 얼지드.

Original English: You, you would not keep the truth from me.
English: you, you would not keep the truth from me.
Hindi: यू, यू वुड नॉट कीप द ट्रुथ फ्रॉम मी.
Korean: 유, 유 우드 낫 킵 더 트룻 프롬 미.

Original English: He will follow us soon.
English: he will follow us soon.
Hindi: ही विल फॉलो अस सून.
Korean: 히 윌 팔로우 어스 순.

Original English: But there came no promise from the bow of the canoe.
English: but there came no promise from the bow of the canoe.
Hindi: बट देर केम नो प्रामिस फ्रॉम द बो अव द कनू.
Korean: 버트 데어 케임 노 프로미스 프럼 더 보우 오브 더 카누.

Original English: She was sleeping under his protection as sweetly as a child.
English: she was sleeping under his protection as sweetly as a child.
Hindi: शी वज़ स्लीपिंग अंडर हिज़ प्रोटेक्शन ऐस स्वीटली ऐस अ चाइल्ड.
Korean: 쉬 워즈 슬리핑 언더 히즈 프로텍션 애즈 스위틀리 애즈 아 차일드.

Original English: Only, it is so wonderful, so almost impossible to believe.
English: only, it is so wonderful, so almost impossible to believe.
Hindi: ओनली, इट इज सो वंडरफुल, सो ऑलमोस्ट इम्पॉसिबल टू बिलीव.
Korean: 온리, 잇 이즈 소 원더풀, 소 올모스트 임퍼서블 투 빌리브.

Original English: The emotion which she had suppressed burst forth now in a choking sob.
English: the emotion which she had suppressed burst forth now in a choking sob.
Hindi: दि इमोशन विच शी हैड सप्रेस्ट बर्स्ट फोर्थ नाउ इन अ चोकिंग सॉब.
Korean: 디 이모션 위치 쉬 햇 서프레스트 버스트 포스 나우 인 아 쵸킹 섭.

Original English: If you only could know how I thank you.
English: if you only could know how i thank you.
Hindi: इफ यू ओनली कुड नो हाउ आई थैंक यू.
Korean: 이프 유 온리 쿠드 노우 하우 아이 땡크 유.

Original English: He waded into the edge of the water and began scrubbing himself.
English: he waded into the edge of the water and began scrubbing himself.
Hindi: ही वेडिड इंटू दि एज अव द वॉटर ऐंड बिगैन स्क्रबिंग हिमसेल्फ.
Korean: 히 웨이드 인투 디 에지 어브 더 워터 앤드 비갠 스크러빙 힘셀프.

Original English: Do you know that you are shaking my confidence in you.
English: do you know that you are shaking my confidence in you.
Hindi: डू यू नो दैट यू आर शेकिंग माई कॉन्फिडेंस इन यू.
Korean: 두 유 노우 댓 유 아르 쉐이킹 마이 컨피던스 인 유.

Original English: Much, replied Jeanne, as tersely.
English: much, replied jeanne, as tersely.
Hindi: मच, रिप्लाइड जीन, ऐज टर्सली.
Korean: 머치, 리플라이드 진, 애즈 터슬리.

Original English: Instead, he joined her; and they ate like two hungry children.
English: instead, he joined her and they ate like two hungry children.
Hindi: इंस्टेड, ही जॉइंड हर ऐंड थे एट लाइक टू हंग्री चिल्ड्रन.
Korean: 인스테드, 히 조인드 허 앤드 데이 에이트 라이크 투 헝그리 칠드런.

Original English: He was wounded in the arm.
English: he was wounded in the arm.
Hindi: ही वज़ वुंडेड इन दि आर्म.
Korean: 히 워즈 우운디드 인 디 암.

Original English: I suppose you picked that lingo up among the Indians.
English: i suppose you picked that lingo up among the indians.
Hindi: आई सपोज़ यू पिक्ट दैट लिंगो अप अमंग दि इंडियन्स.
Korean: 아이 서포스 유 피큿 댓 린고 업 어몽 디 인디언즈.

Original English: Her words sent a strange chill through Philip.
English: her words sent a strange chill through philip.
Hindi: हर वर्ड्स सेंट अ स्ट्रेंज चिल थ्रू फिलिप.
Korean: 허 워즈 센트 아 스트레인지 칠 스루 필립.

Original English: He had no excuse for the feelings which were aroused in him.
English: he had no excuse for the feelings which were aroused in him.
Hindi: ही हैड नो एक्सक्यूस फॉर द फीलिंग्स विच वर अराउज़्ड इन हिम.
Korean: 히 햇 노 익스큐즈 포 더 필링즈 위치 워 어라우즈드 인 힘.

Original English: Was it the rendezvous of those who were striving to work his ruin.
English: was it the rendezvous of those who were striving to work his ruin.
Hindi: वस इट द रांदेवू अव धोज़ हू वर स्ट्राइविंग टू वर्क हिज रुइन.
Korean: 워즈 잇 더 랑데뷔 어브 도즈 후 워 스트라이빙 투 워크 히즈 루인.

Original English: She added, with genuine sympathy in her face and voice.
English: she added, with genuine sympathy in her face and voice.
Hindi: शी ऐडेड, विथ जेन्यूइन सिम्पथी इन हर फेस ऐंड वॉइस.
Korean: 시 에디드, 위드 지뉴인 심퍼씨 인 허 페이스 앤드 보이스.

Original English: Pierre obeys me when we are together.
English: pierre obeys me when we are together.
Hindi: पियर ओबेज़ मी वेन वी आर टुगेदर.
Korean: 피에르 오베이즈 미 웬 위 아 투게더.

Original English: Jeanne was turning the bow shoreward.
English: jeanne was turning the bow shoreward.
Hindi: जीन वस टर्निंग द बो शोर्वार्ड.
Korean: 진 워즈 터닝 더 보우 쇼어워드.

Original English: My right foot feels like that of a Chinese debutante.
English: my right foot feels like that of a chinese debutante.
Hindi: माई राइट फुट फील्स लाइक दैट अव अ चाइनीज़ डेब्यूटांटे.
Korean: 마이 라이트 풋 필즈 라이크 댓 어브 아 차이니즈 데뷔탄트.

Original English: They ate dinner at the fifth, and rested for two hours.
English: they ate dinner at the fifth, and rested for two hours.
Hindi: थे एट डिनर ऐट द फिफ्थ, ऐंड रेस्टेड फॉर टू आउर्स.
Korean: 데이 에이트 디너 앳 더 피프스, 앤드 레스티드 포어 투 아이어스.

Original English: Two years ago I gave up civilization for this.
English: two years ago i gave up civilization for this.
Hindi: टू ईयर्ज़ अगो आई गेव अप सिविलाइज़ेशन फॉर दिस.
Korean: 투 이어즈 아고 아이 게이브 업 시빌라이제이션 포어 디스.

Original English: She had died from cold and starvation.
English: she had died from cold and starvation.
Hindi: शी हैड डाइड फ्रॉम कोल्ड ऐंड स्टार्वेशन.
Korean: 시 해드 다이드 프럼 콜드 앤드 스타베이션.

Original English: It was Jeanne singing softly over beyond the rocks.
English: it was jeanne singing softly over beyond the rocks.
Hindi: इट वज़ जीन सिंगिंग सॉफ्टली ओवर बियॉन्ड द रॉक्स.
Korean: 잇 워즈 진 싱잉 소프트리 오버 비욘드 더 록스.

Original English: He was determined now to maintain a more certain hold upon himself.
English: he was determined now to maintain a more certain hold upon himself.
Hindi: ही वस डिटरमाइंड नाउ टू मेंटेन अ मोर सर्टन होल्ड अपान हिम्सेल्फ.
Korean: 히 워즈 디터민드 나우 투 메인테인 아 모어 서튼 홀드 어폰 힘셀프.

Original English: Each day she became a more vital part of him.
English: each day she became a more vital part of him.
Hindi: ईच डे शी बिकेम अ मोर वाइटल पार्ट अव हिम.
Korean: 이치 데이 쉬 비케임 아 모어 바이털 파트 어브 힘.

Original English: It was a temptation, but he resisted it.
English: it was a temptation, but he resisted it.
Hindi: इट वज़ अ टेम्प्टेशन, बट ही रिसिस्टेड इट.
Korean: 잇 와즈 아 템테이션, 벗 히 리서스티드 잇.

Original English: This one hope was destroyed as quickly as it was born.
English: this one hope was destroyed as quickly as it was born.
Hindi: दिस वन होप वज डिस्ट्रॉयड ऐस क्विक्ली ऐस इट वज बॉर्न.
Korean: 디스 원 호프 워즈 디스트로이드 에즈 퀵리 에즈 잇 워즈 본.

Original English: Her face was against his breast.
English: her face was against his breast.
Hindi: हर फेस वज अगेंस्ट हिज़ ब्रेस्ट.
Korean: 허 페이스 워즈 어게인스트 히즈 브레스트.

Original English: She was his now, forever.
English: she was his now, forever.
Hindi: शी वस हिज़ नाउ, फरएवर.
Korean: 쉬 워즈 히즈 나우, 포레버.

Original English: Providence had delivered him through the maelstrom.
English: providence had delivered him through the maelstrom.
Hindi: प्राविडेंस हैड डिलीवर्ड हिम थ्रू द मेलस्ट्रॉम.
Korean: 프로비던스 해드 딜리버드 힘 스루 더 메일스트롬.

Original English: A cry of joy burst from Philip's lips.
English: a cry of joy burst from philip's lips.
Hindi: अ क्राइ अव जॉय बर्स्ट फ्रॉम फिलिप्स लिप्स.
Korean: 아 크라이 어브 조이 버스트 프롬 필립스 립스.

Original English: Philip began to feel that he had foolishly overestimated his strength.
English: philip began to feel that he had foolishly overestimated his strength.
Hindi: फिलिप बिगन टू फील दैट ही हैड फूलिशली ओवरएस्टिमेटेड हिज़ स्ट्रेंग्थ.
Korean: 필립 비건 투 필 댓 히 헤드 풀리쉴리 오버에스티메이티드 히즈 스트렝스.

Original English: He obeyed the pressure of her hand.
English: he obeyed the pressure of her hand.
Hindi: ही ओबेड द प्रेशर अव हर हैंड.
Korean: 히 오베이드 더 프레셔 어브 허 핸드.

Original English: I am going to surprise father, and you will go with Pierre.
English: i am going to surprise father, and you will go with pierre.
Hindi: आई ऐम गोइंग टू सरप्राइज़ फादर, ऐंड यू विल गो विथ पिएर.
Korean: 아이 앰 고잉 투 서프라이즈 파더, 앤드 유 윌 고 위드 피에르.

Original English: About him, everywhere, were the evidences of luxury and of age.
English: about him, everywhere, were the evidences of luxury and of age.
Hindi: अबाउट हिम, एवरीव्हेर, वेर दि एविडेंसेस अव लक्ज़री एंड अव एज.
Korean: 어바웃 힘, 에브리웨어, 워 디 에비던시즈 어브 럭셔리 앤드 어브 에이지.

Original English: Then he stepped back with a low cry of pleasure.
English: then he stepped back with a low cry of pleasure.
Hindi: धेन ही स्टेप्ट बैक विथ अ लो क्राई अव प्लेजर.
Korean: 덴 히 스텁트 백 위드 아 로우 크라이 오브 플레저.

Original English: In the picture he saw each moment a greater resemblance to Jeanne.
English: in the picture he saw each moment a greater resemblance to jeanne.
Hindi: इन द पिक्चर ही सॉ ईच मोमेंट अ ग्रेटर रिसेम्बलन्स टू जीन.
Korean: 인 더 픽처 히 소 이치 모먼트 아 그레이터 리셈블런스 투 진.

Original English: He told himself that as he washed himself and groomed his disheveled clothes.
English: he told himself that as he washed himself and groomed his disheveled clothes.
Hindi: ही टोल्ड हिम्सेल्फ दॅट ऐज़ ही वॉश्ड हिम्सेल्फ ऐंड ग्रूम्ड हिज़ डिशेवेल्ड क्लोथ्ज़.
Korean: 히 톨드 힘셀프 댓 애즈 히 워시트 힘셀프 앤드 그루메드 히즈 디셰블드 클로스.

Original English: Accept a father's blessing, and with it, this.
English: accept a father's blessing, and with it, this.
Hindi: अक्सेप्ट अ फादर्स ब्लेसिंग, एंड विथ इट, दिस.
Korean: 액셉트 아 파더즈 블레싱, 앤드 위드 잇, 디스.

Original English: It seems like a strange pointing of the hand of God.
English: it seems like a strange pointing of the hand of god.
Hindi: इट सीम्स लाइक अ स्ट्रेंज पॉइंटिंग अव द हैंड अव गॉड.
Korean: 잇 심즈 라이크 아 스트레인지 포인팅 어브 더 핸드 어브 갓.

Original English: Such things had occurred before, he told Philip.
English: such things had occurred before, he told philip.
Hindi: सच थिंग्स हैड अकर्ड बिफोर, ही टोल्ड फिलिप.
Korean: 서치 띵즈 해드 어컬드 비포어, 히 톨드 필립.

Original English: Ah, I had forgotten, he exclaimed.
English: ah, i had forgotten, he exclaimed.
Hindi: आ, आई हैड फरगोटन, ही एक्सक्लेम्ड.
Korean: 아, 아이 햇 포거튼, 히 익스클레임드.

Original English: But there was something even more startling than this resemblance.
English: but there was something even more startling than this resemblance.
Hindi: बट देर वज समथिंग ईवन मोर स्टार्टलिंग धन दिस रेसम्ब्लन्स.
Korean: 벗 데어 워즈 썸띵 이븐 모어 스타틀링 던 디스 리즘블런스.

Original English: I have to be careful of them, as they tear very easily.
English: i have to be careful of them, as they tear very easily.
Hindi: आई हैव टू बी केयरफुल अव देम, ऐज़ दे टीयर वेरी ईजिली.
Korean: 아이 해브 투 비 케어풀 오브 뎀, 애즈 데이 티어 베리 이지리.

Original English: Of course, that is uninteresting, she continued.
English: of course, that is uninteresting, she continued.
Hindi: अव कोर्स, दैट इज़ अनइंटरेस्टिंग, शी कंटिन्यूड.
Korean: 어브 코스, 댓 이즈 언인터레스팅, 쉬 컨티뉴드.

Original English: A moment before he was intoxicated by a joy that was almost madness.
English: a moment before he was intoxicated by a joy that was almost madness.
Hindi: अ मोमेंट बिफोर ही वज़ इन्टॉक्सीकेटेड बाय अ जॉय दैट वज़ ऑलमोस्ट मैडनेस.
Korean: 아 모먼트 비포어 히 워즈 인톡시케이티드 바이 아 조이 댓 워즈 올모스트 매드니스.

Original English: Now these things had been struck dead within him.
English: now these things had been struck dead within him.
Hindi: नाउ दीज़ थिंग्स हैड बीन स्ट्रक डेड विथिन हिम.
Korean: 나우 디즈 띵즈 해드 빈 스트럭 데드 위딘 힘.

Original English: For an instant he saw Pierre drawn like a silhouette against the sky.
English: for an instant he saw pierre drawn like a silhouette against the sky.
Hindi: फॉर अन इंस्टंट ही सॉ पियर ड्रॉन लाइक अ सिलुएट अगेंस्ट द स्काई.
Korean: 포 안 인스턴트 히 소 피에르 드론 라이크 아 실루엣 어게인스트 더 스카이.

Original English: Goodbye, Pierre, he shouted.
English: goodbye, pierre, he shouted.
Hindi: गुडबाई, पिएर, ही शाउटेड.
Korean: 굿바이, 피에르, 히 샤우티드.

Original English: And MacDougall was beyond the trail, with three weeks to spare.
English: and macdougall was beyond the trail, with three weeks to spare.
Hindi: ऐंड मकडूगल वज़ बियांड द ट्रेल, विथ थ्री वीक्स टू स्पेयर.
Korean: 앤 맥두골 워즈 비언드 더 트레일, 위드 쓰리 위크스 투 스페어.

Original English: Philip thrust himself against it and entered.
English: philip thrust himself against it and entered.
Hindi: फिलिप थ्रस्ट हिम्सेल्फ अगेन्स्ट इट एंड एंटर्ड.
Korean: 필립 쓰러스트 힘셀프 어게인스트 잇 앤드 엔터드.

Original English: MacDougall tapped his forehead suspiciously with a stubby forefinger.
English: macdougall tapped his forehead suspiciously with a stubby forefinger.
Hindi: मकडूगल टैप्ड हिज़ फॉरहेड सस्पिशस्ली विथ अ स्टबी फोरफिंगर.
Korean: 맥두걸 탭트 히즈 포어헤드 서스피셔슬리 위드 아 스터비 포어핑거.

Original English: He was smooth-shaven, and his hair and eyes were black.
English: he was smooth-shaven, and his hair and eyes were black.
Hindi: ही वस स्मूथ-शेवेन, एंड हिस हेयर एंड आईज़ वर ब्लैक.
Korean: 히 워즈 스무드쉐이븐, 앤드 히즈 헤어 앤드 아이즈 워 블랙.

Original English: Won't you draw up, gentlemen.
English: will not you draw up, gentlemen.
Hindi: विल नॉट यू ड्रॉ अप, जेंटलमेन.
Korean: 윌 낫 유 드로 업, 젠틀맨.

Original English: A strange fire burned in his eyes when Thorpe turned.
English: a strange fire burned in his eyes when thorpe turned.
Hindi: अ स्ट्रेंज फायर बर्न्ड इन हिस आइस वेन थॉर्प टर्न्ड.
Korean: 아 스트레인지 파이어 번드 인 히즈 아이즈 웬 소프 턴드.

Original English: He had worshiped her, as Dante might have worshiped Beatrice.
English: he had worshiped her, as dante might have worshiped beatrice.
Hindi: ही हैड वर्शिप्ट हर, ऐस डांटे माइट हैव वर्शिप्ट बेट्रिस.
Korean: 히 해드 워십트 허, 애즈 단테 마이트 해브 워십트 비아트리스.

Original English: Does that look good.
English: does that look good.
Hindi: डज़ दॅट लुक गुड.
Korean: 두즈 댓 룩 굿.

Original English: They look as though he had been drumming a piano all his life.
English: they look as though he had been drumming a piano all his life.
Hindi: थे लुक ऐज़ धो ही हैड बीन ड्रमिंग अ पिआनो ऑल हिस लाइफ.
Korean: 데이 룩 애즈 소우 히 해드 빈 드러밍 아 피아노 올 히즈 라이프.

Original English: You want to go over and see his gang throw dirt.
English: you want to go over and see his gang throw dirt.
Hindi: यू वांट टू गो ओवर ऐंड सी हिस गैंग थ्रो डर्ट.
Korean: 유 완트 투 고 오버 앤드 씨 히즈 갱 쓰로우 더트.

Original English: Take away their foreman and they wouldn't be worth their grub.
English: take away their foreman and they would not be worth their grub.
Hindi: टेक अवे देर फोरमैन एंड थे वुड नॉट बी वर्थ देर ग्रब.
Korean: 테이크 어웨이 더 포맨 앤드 데이 우드 낫 비 워스 더 그럽.

Original English: That's the sub-foreman, explained Thorpe.
English: that's the sub-foreman, explained thorpe.
Hindi: दॅट्स द सब-फोरमन, एक्सप्लेंड थॉर्प.
Korean: 댓츠 더 섭포어맨, 익스플레인드 소랩.

Original English: Philip made no effort to follow.
English: philip made no effort to follow.
Hindi: फिलिप मेड नो एफर्ट टू फॉलो.
Korean: 필립 메이드 노 에포트 투 팔로우.

Original English: He came first a year ago, and revealed himself to Jeanne.
English: he came first a year ago, and revealed himself to jeanne.
Hindi: ही केम फर्स्ट अ ईयर अगो, एंड रिवील्ड हिम्सेल्फ टू जीन.
Korean: 히 케임 퍼스트 아 이어 어고우, 앤드 리빌드 힘셀프 투 진.

Original English: They are to attack your camp tomorrow night.
English: they are to attack your camp tomorrow night.
Hindi: थेई आर टू अटैक योर कैम्प टुमारो नाइट.
Korean: 데이 아르 투 어택 유어 캄프 투모로우 나이트.

Original English: Two days ago Jeanne learned where her father's men were hiding.
English: two days ago jeanne learned where her father's men were hiding.
Hindi: टू डेज़ अगो जीन लर्न्ड वेयर हर फादर्स मेन वेर हाइडिंग.
Korean: 투 데이즈 어고 진 런드 웨어 허 파더즈 멘 워 하이딩.

Original English: I was near the cabin, and saw you.
English: i was near the cabin, and saw you.
Hindi: आई वज़ नीर द कैबिन, ऐंड सॉ यू.
Korean: 아이 워즈 니어 더 캐빈, 앤드 소 유.

Original English: Low bush whipped him in the face and left no sting.
English: low bush whipped him in the face and left no sting.
Hindi: लो बुश विप्ट हिम इन द फेस एंड लेफ्ट नो स्टिंग.
Korean: 로우 부시 휘프트 힘 인 더 페이스 앤드 레프트 노 스팅.

Original English: Suddenly Jeanne stopped for an instant.
English: suddenly jeanne stopped for an instant.
Hindi: सडनली जीन स्टॉप्ट फॉर अन इंस्टंट.
Korean: 써덜리 진 스탑트 포어 안 인스턴트.

Original English: There was none of the joy of meeting in his face.
English: there was none of the joy of meeting in his face.
Hindi: धेर वस नन अव द जॉय अव मीटिंग इन हिज़ फेस.
Korean: 데어 워즈 논 어브 더 조이 어브 미팅 인 히즈 페이스.

Original English: And when you come back in a few days, bring Eileen.
English: and when you come back in a few days, bring eileen.
Hindi: ऐंड वेन यू कम बैक इन अ फ्यू डेज, ब्रिंग आइलीन.
Korean: 앤드 웬 유 컴 백 인 아 퓨 데이즈, 브링 아일린.

Original English: Gregson had left the outer door slightly ajar.
English: gregson had left the outer door slightly ajar.
Hindi: ग्रेगसन हैड लेफ्ट दि आउटर डोर स्लाइटली अजार.
Korean: 그렉슨 해드 레프트 디 아우터 도어 슬라이틀리 어자르.

Original English: The date was nearly eighteen years old.
English: the date was nearly eighteen years old.
Hindi: द डेट वज़ नियरली एटीन इयर्स ओल्ड.
Korean: 더 데이트 워즈 니얼리 에이틴 이어즈 올드.

Original English: They were the presage of storm.
English: they were the presage of storm.
Hindi: थे वर द प्रेसिज अव स्टॉर्म.
Korean: 데이 워 더 프레시지 어브 스톰.

Original English: Down there the earth was already swelling with life.
English: down there the earth was already swelling with life.
Hindi: डाउन देर दि अर्थ वज़ ऑलरेडी स्वेलिंग विथ लाइफ.
Korean: 다운 데어 디 어스 와즈 올레디 스웰링 위드 라이프.

Original English: For the first time in his life he was yearning for a scrap.
English: for the first time in his life he was yearning for a scrap.
Hindi: फॉर द फर्स्ट टाइम इन हिज़ लाइफ ही वज़ यर्निंग फॉर अ स्क्रैप.
Korean: 포어 더 퍼스트 타임 인 히즈 라이프 히 워즈 이어닝 포어 아 스크랩.

Original English: She had been thoroughly and efficiently mauled.
English: she had been thoroughly and efficiently mauled.
Hindi: शी हैड बीन थरोली एंड इफिशेंटली मॉल्ड.
Korean: 쉬 햇 빈 써롤리 앤드 이피션틀리 몰드.

Original English: Every bone in her aged body seemed broken or dislocated.
English: every bone in her aged body seemed broken or dislocated.
Hindi: एवरी बोन इन हर एज्ड बॉडी सीम्ड ब्रोकन ऑर डिसलोकेटेड.
Korean: 에브리 본 인 허 에이지드 바디 심드 브로큰 오어 디스로케이티드.

Original English: Tomorrow I'm going after that bear, he said.
English: tomorrow i am going after that bear, he said.
Hindi: टुमारो आई ऐम गोइंग आफ्टर दैट बेयर, ही सेड.
Korean: 투모로우 아이 앰 고잉 애프터 댓 베어, 히 세드.

Original English: If not, let's say our prayers and go to bed.
English: if not, let us say our prayers and go to bed.
Hindi: इफ नॉट, लेट अस से आउर प्रेयर्स ऐंड गो टू बेड.
Korean: 이프 낫, 렛 어스 세이 아워 프레어즈 앤드 고우 투 베드.

Original English: So cheer up, and give us your paw.
English: so cheer up, and give us your paw.
Hindi: सो चीर अप, ऐंड गिव अस यूर पॉ.
Korean: 소 치어 업, 앤드 기브 어스 유어 포.

Original English: This time he did not yap for mercy.
English: this time he did not yap for mercy.
Hindi: दिस टाइम ही डिड नाट यैप फॉर मर्सी.
Korean: 디스 타임 히 디드 낫 예프 포 머시.

Original English: And the air was growing chilly.
English: and the air was growing chilly.
Hindi: एंड दि ऐर वज़ ग्रोइंग चिली.
Korean: 앤 디 에어 워스 그로잉 칠리.

Original English: Don't you see, I'm chewing this thing in two.
English: do not you see, i am chewing this thing in two.
Hindi: डू नाट यू सी, आई ऐम च्यूइंग दिस थिंग इन टू.
Korean: 두 낫 유 시, 아이 앰 추잉 디스 띵 인 투.

Original English: The questions may have come vaguely in his mind.
English: the questions may have come vaguely in his mind.
Hindi: द क्वेश्चन्स मे हैव कम वेगली इन हिज माइंड.
Korean: 더 퀘스천즈 메이 해브 컴 베이글리 인 히즈 마인드.

Original English: Like a flash he launched himself into the feathered mass of the owl.
English: like a flash he launched himself into the feathered mass of the owl.
Hindi: लाइक अ फ्लैश ही लॉन्च्ड हिम्सेल्फ इंटू द फेदर्ड मास अव दि आउल.
Korean: 라이크 아 플래쉬 히 런치드 힘셀프 인투 더 페더드 매스 어브 디 아울.

Original English: Ahead of them they saw a glimmer of sunshine.
English: ahead of them they saw a glimmer of sunshine.
Hindi: अहेड अव देम धे सॉ अ ग्लिमर अव सनशाइन.
Korean: 어헤드 어브 뎀 데이 쏘 아 글리머 어브 선샤인.

Original English: Two gigantic owls were tearing at the carcass.
English: two gigantic owls were tearing at the carcass.
Hindi: टू जायगैंटिक औल्स वर टेरिंग ऐट द कार्कस.
Korean: 투 자이갠틱 아울즈 워 테어링 앳 더 카카스.

Original English: The big-eyed, clucking moose-birds were most annoying.
English: the big-eyed, clucking moose-birds were most annoying.
Hindi: द बिग-आईड, क्लकिंग मूस-बर्ड्स वर मोस्ट अनॉयिंग.
Korean: 더 빅아이드, 클러킹 무스버즈 워 모스트 어노잉.

Original English: Next to them the Canada jays were most persistent.
English: next to them the canada jays were most persistent.
Hindi: नेक्स्ट टू देम द कनाडा जेज़ वर मोस्ट परसिस्टेंट.
Korean: 넥스트 투 뎀 더 캐나다 제이즈 워 모스트 퍼시스턴트.

Original English: For a time the exciting thrill of his adventure was gone.
English: for a time the exciting thrill of his adventure was gone.
Hindi: फॉर अ टाइम दि एक्साइटिंग थ्रिल अव हिज़ एडवेंचर वज़ गॉन.
Korean: 포어 아 타임 디 엑싸이팅 스릴 오브 히즈 어드벤처 워즈 곤.

Original English: He did not rush in.
English: he did not rush in.
Hindi: ही डिड नाट रश इन.
Korean: 히 디드 낫 러시 인.

Original English: It was edged with ice.
English: it was edged with ice.
Hindi: इट वज एज्ड विथ आइस.
Korean: 잇 워즈 에지드 위드 아이스.

Original English: He drank of the water cautiously.
English: he drank of the water cautiously.
Hindi: ही ड्रैंक अव द वॉटर कॉशस्ली.
Korean: 히 드랭크 어브 더 워터 커셔슬리.

Original English: But a strange thing happened.
English: but a strange thing happened.
Hindi: बट अ स्ट्रेंज थिंग हैपन्ड.
Korean: 벗 아 스트레인지 띵 해픈드.

Original English: He began to follow the footprints of the dog.
English: he began to follow the footprints of the dog.
Hindi: ही बिगैन टू फालो द फुटप्रिंट्स अव द डॉग.
Korean: 히 비간 투 팔로 더 풋프린츠 오브 더 도그.

Original English: Such a dog the wise driver kills, or turns loose.
English: such a dog the wise driver kills, or turns loose.
Hindi: सच अ डॉग द वाइज ड्राइवर किल्स, ऑर टर्न्स लूस.
Korean: 서치 아 도그 더 와이즈 드라이버 킬즈, 오어 턴스 루스.

Original English: Sometimes her dreams were filled with visions.
English: sometimes her dreams were filled with visions.
Hindi: समटाइम्स हेर ड्रीम्स वेर फिल्ड विथ विज़न्स.
Korean: 썸타임즈 허 드림스 워 필드 위드 비전즈.

Original English: Thus had the raw wilderness prepared him for this day.
English: thus had the raw wilderness prepared him for this day.
Hindi: दस हैड द रॉ वाइल्डर्नेस प्रिपेयर्ड हिम फॉर दिस डे.
Korean: 두스 해드 더 라우 와일더니스 프리퍼드 힘 포우어 디스 데이.

Original English: He leapt again, and the club caught him once more.
English: he leapt again, and the club caught him once more.
Hindi: ही लेप्ट अगेन, एंड द क्लब कॉट हिम वन्स मोर.
Korean: 히 렙트 어겐, 앤드 더 클럽 코트 힘 원스 모어.

Original English: He cried, and swung the club wildly.
English: he cried, and swung the club wildly.
Hindi: ही क्राइड, ऐंड स्वंग द क्लब वाइल्डली.
Korean: 히 크라이드, 앤드 스웡 더 클럽 와일들리.

Original English: She turned, fearing that Jacques might see what was in her face.
English: she turned, fearing that jacques might see what was in her face.
Hindi: शी टर्न्ड, फियरिंग दैट जैक माइट सी वट वज इन हर फेस.
Korean: 시 턴드, 페어링 댓 쟈끄 마이트 씨 와트 워즈 인 허어 페이스.

Original English: They were following the shore of a lake.
English: they were following the shore of a lake.
Hindi: धे वर फॉलोइंग द शोर अव अ लेक.
Korean: 데이 워 폴로잉 더 쇼어 어브 아 레이크.

Original English: The wolf-dog thrust his gaunt muzzle toward him.
English: the wolf-dog thrust his gaunt muzzle toward him.
Hindi: द वुल्फडॉग थ्रस्ट हिस गॉन्ट मजल तुवॉर्ड हिम.
Korean: 더 울프도그 쓰러스트 히즈 건트 머즐 투워드 힘.

Original English: From now on we're pals.
English: from now on we are pals.
Hindi: फ्रम नाउ ऑन वी आर पैल्स.
Korean: 프럼 나우 온 위 아 펠즈.

Original English: He says he bought him of Jacques Le Beau.
English: he says he bought him of jacques le beau.
Hindi: ही सेज़ ही बॉट हिम अव जैक ले बो.
Korean: 히 세즈 히 보우트 힘 어브 잭 르 보우.

Original English: How much was it.
English: how much was it.
Hindi: हाऊ मच वज़ इट.
Korean: 하우 머치 와즈 잇.

Original English: Youth had come back to her, freed from the yoke of oppression.
English: youth had come back to her, freed from the yoke of oppression.
Hindi: यूथ हैड कम बैक टू हर, फ्रीड फ्रॉम द योक ऑफ ऑप्रेशन.
Korean: 유스 해드 컴 백 투 허, 프리드 프롬 더 욕 어브 어프레션.

Original English: It was not a large lake, and almost round.
English: it was not a large lake, and almost round.
Hindi: इट वस नाट अ लार्ज लेक, ऐंड ऑलमोस्ट राउंड.
Korean: 잇 워즈 낫 아 라지 레이크, 앤드 올모스트 라운드.

Original English: Its diameter was not more than two hundred yards.
English: its diameter was not more than two hundred yards.
Hindi: इट्स डायमीटर वज़ नॉट मोर धन टू हंड्रेड यार्ड्स.
Korean: 이츠 다이아미터 워즈 낫 모어 댄 투 헌드레드 야즈.

Original English: It drowned all sound that brute agony and death may have made.
English: it drowned all sound that brute agony and death may have made.
Hindi: इट ड्राउंड ऑल साउंड दैट ब्रूट एगनी ऐंड डेथ मे हैव मेड.
Korean: 잇 드라운드 올 사운드 댓 브루트 애거니 앤드 데스 메이 해브 메이드.

Original English: Fresh cases, still able to walk, they clustered about the spokesman.
English: fresh cases, still able to walk, they clustered about the spokesman.
Hindi: फ्रेश केस, स्टिल एबल टू वॉक, थे क्लस्टर्ड अबाउट द स्पोक्समन.
Korean: 프레쉬 케이시스, 스틸 에이블 투 워크, 데이 클러스터드 어바웃 더 스포크스먼.

Original English: Between him and the beach was the cane-grass fence of the compound.
English: between him and the beach was the cane-grass fence of the compound.
Hindi: बिटवीन हिम ऐंड द बीच वज़ द केनग्रास फेंस अव द काम्पाउंड.
Korean: 비트윈 힘 앤드 더 비치 워즈 더 케인그라스 펜스 어브 더 컴파운드.

Original English: Besides, he was paid one case of tobacco per head.
English: besides, he was paid one case of tobacco per head.
Hindi: बिसाइड्स, ही वस पेड वन केस अव टोबैको पर हेड.
Korean: 비사이즈, 히 워즈 페이드 원 케이스 어브 토바코 퍼 헤드.

Original English: They die out of spite.
English: they die out of spite.
Hindi: थे डाई आउट अव स्पाइट.
Korean: 데이 다이 아웃 어브 스파이트.

Original English: The other felt a sudden wave of irritation rush through him.
English: the other felt a sudden wave of irritation rush through him.
Hindi: दि अदर फेल्ट अ सडन वेव अव इरिटेशन रश थ्रू हिम.
Korean: 디 어더 펠트 아 서든 웨이브 어브 이리테이션 러쉬 쓰루 힘.

Original English: Oppressive as the heat had been, it was now even more oppressive.
English: oppressive as the heat had been, it was now even more oppressive.
Hindi: अप्रेसिव ऐज़ द हीट हैड बीन, इट वज़ नाउ ईवन मोर अप्रेसिव.
Korean: 어프레시브 애즈 더 히트 해드 빈, 잇 워즈 나우 이븐 모어 어프레시브.

Original English: The ringing of the big bell aroused him.
English: the ringing of the big bell aroused him.
Hindi: द रिंगिंग अव द बिग बेल अराउज्ड हिम.
Korean: 더 링잉 어브 더 빅 벨 아라우즈드 힘.

Original English: At first he puzzled over something untoward he was sure had happened.
English: at first he puzzled over something untoward he was sure had happened.
Hindi: ऐट फर्स्ट ही पज़ल्ड ओवर समथिंग अन्टवर्ड ही वज़ शुर हैड हैपन्ड.
Korean: 앳 퍼스트 히 퍼즐드 오버 썸띵 언투어드 히 워즈 숴 핻 해펀드.

Original English: A dead man is of no use on a plantation.
English: a dead man is of no use on a plantation.
Hindi: अ डेड मैन इज़ ऑव नो यूज़ ऑन अ प्लांटेशन.
Korean: 아 데드 맨 이즈 어브 노 유스 온 아 플랜테이션.

Original English: I don't know why you're here at all.
English: i do not know why you are here at all.
Hindi: आई डू नॉट नो वाइ यू आर हीर ऐट ऑल.
Korean: 아이 두 낫 노 와이 유 아르 히어 앳 올.

Original English: What part of the United States is your home.
English: what part of the united states is your home.
Hindi: वट पार्ट अव द यूनाइटेड स्टेट्स इज योर होम.
Korean: 왓 파트 어브 더 유나이티드 스테이츠 이즈 유어 홈.

Original English: My, I'm almost homesick for it already.
English: my, i am almost homesick for it already.
Hindi: माय, आई ऐम ऑलमोस्ट होमसिक फॉर इट ऑलरेडी.
Korean: 마이, 아이 엠 올모스트 홈식 훠 잇 올레디.

Original English: She nodded, and her eyes grew soft and moist.
English: she nodded, and her eyes grew soft and moist.
Hindi: शी नाडेड, एंड हर आइज ग्रू सॉफ्ट एंड मॉइस्ट.
Korean: 쉬 나드, 앤드 허 아이즈 그루 소프트 앤드 모이스트.

Original English: I was brought up the way most girls in Hawaii are brought up.
English: i was brought up the way most girls in hawaii are brought up.
Hindi: आई वस ब्रॉट अप द वे मोस्ट गर्ल्स इन हवाई आर ब्रॉट अप.
Korean: 아이 워즈 브롯 업 더 웨이 모스트 걸스 인 하와이 아 브롯 업.

Original English: That came before my A B C's.
English: that came before my a b c's.
Hindi: दैट केम बिफोर माई अ बी सीज़.
Korean: 댓 케임 비포어 마이 아 비 시즈.

Original English: It was the same way with our revolvers and rifles.
English: it was the same way with our revolvers and rifles.
Hindi: इट वज़ द सेम वे विद औअर रिवॉलवर्स ऐंड राइफल्स.
Korean: 잇 워즈 더 세임 웨이 위드 아우어 리볼버즈 앤드 라이플즈.

Original English: But it contributed to the smash.
English: but it contributed to the smash.
Hindi: बट इट कॉन्ट्रिब्यूटेड टू द स्मैश.
Korean: 벗 잇 컨트리뷰티드 투 더 스매쉬.

Original English: The last one I knew was an overseer.
English: the last one i knew was an overseer.
Hindi: द लास्ट वन आई न्यू वस अन ओवरसीर.
Korean: 더 래스트 원 아이 누 워즈 안 오버시어.

Original English: Do you know any good land around here.
English: do you know any good land around here.
Hindi: डू यू नो एनी गुड लैंड अराउंड हीर.
Korean: 두 유 노 에니 굿 랜드 어라운드 히어.

Original English: The Resident Commissioner is away in Australia.
English: the resident commissioner is away in australia.
Hindi: द रेज़िडेंट कमिश्नर इज़ अवे इन ऑस्ट्रेलिया.
Korean: 더 리지덴트 커미션어 이즈 어웨이 인 오스트레일리아.

Original English: I cannot follow you, she said.
English: i cannot follow you, she said.
Hindi: आई कैनॉट फॉलो यू, शी सैड.
Korean: 아이 캐넛 폴로우 유, 쉬 세드.

Original English: I never allow what can't be changed to annoy me.
English: i never allow what can not be changed to annoy me.
Hindi: आई नेवर अलाउ वट कैन नॉट बी चेंज्ड टू अनॉय मी.
Korean: 아이 네버 얼라우 왓 캔 낫 비 체인지드 투 어나이 미.

Original English: Why, the average review is more nauseating than cod liver oil.
English: why, the average review is more nauseating than cod liver oil.
Hindi: वाय, दि ऐवरेज रिव्यू इज मोर नॉसिएटिंग दन काड लिवर ऑयल.
Korean: 와이, 디 에버리지 리뷰 이즈 모어 노지에이팅 댄 코드 리버 오일.

Original English: His voice was passionately rebellious.
English: his voice was passionately rebellious.
Hindi: हिज़ वॉइस वज़ पैशनेटली रिबेलियस.
Korean: 히즈 보이스 워즈 패셔넛리 리벨리어스.

Original English: Don't you see I hate you.
English: do not you see i hate you.
Hindi: डू नॉट यू सी आई हेट यू.
Korean: 두 낫 유 시 아이 헤이트 유.

Original English: So Hughie and I did the managing ourselves.
English: so hughie and i did the managing ourselves.
Hindi: सो ह्यूई एंड आई डिड द मैनेजिंग आउरसेल्व्ज़.
Korean: 소 휴이 앤드 아이 딛 더 매니징 아워셀브즈.

Original English: It happened to him at the Gallina Society in Oakland one afternoon.
English: it happened to him at the gallina society in oakland one afternoon.
Hindi: इट हैपन्ड तू हिम ऐट द गैलिना सोसाइटी इन ओकलैंड वन आफ्टरनून.
Korean: 잇 해픈드 투 힘 앳 더 갈리나 소사이어티 인 오클랜드 원 애프터눈.

Original English: He cried in such genuine dismay that she broke into hearty laughter.
English: he cried in such genuine dismay that she broke into hearty laughter.
Hindi: ही क्राइड इन सच जेनुइन डिस्मे दॅट शी ब्रोक इंटू हार्टी लाफ्टर.
Korean: 히 크라이드 인 서치 젠유인 디스메이 댓 쉬 브로크 인투 하티 래프터.

Original English: Wash your hands of me.
English: wash your hands of me.
Hindi: वॉश योर हैंड्स अव मी.
Korean: 워시 유어 핸즈 어브 미.

Original English: I think it's much nicer to quarrel.
English: i think it's much nicer to quarrel.
Hindi: आई थिंक इट्स मच नाइसर टू क्वॉरेल.
Korean: 아이 띵크 잇츠 머치 나이서 투 쿠어럴.

Original English: I saw it when she rolled.
English: i saw it when she rolled.
Hindi: आई सॉ इट वेन शी रोल्ड.
Korean: 아이 소 잇 웬 쉬 롤드.

Original English: I only read the quotations.
English: i only read the quotations.
Hindi: आई ओनली रीड द क्वोटेशन्स.
Korean: 아이 온리 리드 더 쿼테이션즈.

Original English: He was the soul of devotion to his employers.
English: he was the soul of devotion to his employers.
Hindi: ही वज द सोल अव डिवोशन टू हिस एम्प्लॉयर्स.
Korean: 히 워즈 더 솔 어브 디보션 투 히즈 엠플로이어스.

Original English: Out of his eighteen hundred, he laid aside sixteen hundred each year.
English: out of his eighteen hundred, he laid aside sixteen hundred each year.
Hindi: आउट अव हिज़ एटीन हंड्रेड, ही लेड असाइड सिक्सटीन हंड्रेड ईच ईयर.
Korean: 아웃 어브 히즈 에이틴 헌드레드, 히 레이드 어사이드 식스틴 헌드레드 이치 이어.

Original English: You have heard always how he was the lover of the Princess Naomi.
English: you have heard always how he was the lover of the princess naomi.
Hindi: यू हैव हर्ड ऑलवेज़ हाउ ही वज़ द लवर ऑफ द प्रिंसेस नेओमी.
Korean: 유 해브 허드 올웨이즈 하우 히 워즈 더 러버 어브 더 프린세스 나오미.

Original English: They ought to pass here some time today.
English: they ought to pass here some time today.
Hindi: दे ऑट टू पास हिर सम टाइम टुडे.
Korean: 더이 오트 투 파스 히어 썸 타임 투데이.

Original English: I had been sad too long already.
English: i had been sad too long already.
Hindi: आई हैड बीन सैड टू लॉन्ग ऑलरेडी.
Korean: 아이 해드 빈 새드 투 롱 올레디.

Original English: All eyes, however, were staring at him in certitude of expectancy.
English: all eyes, however, were staring at him in certitude of expectancy.
Hindi: ऑल आइज़, हाउएवर, वेर स्टेरिंग ऐट हिम इन सर्टिट्यूड अव एक्सपेक्टेंसी.
Korean: 올 아이즈, 하외버, 워 스테어링 앳 힘 인 서르튜드 업 엑스펙턴시.

Original English: He had observed the business life of Hawaii and developed a vaulting ambition.
English: he had observed the business life of hawaii and developed a vaulting ambition.
Hindi: ही हैड ऑब्ज़र्व्ड द बिज़नेस लाइफ अव हवाई एंड डेवेलप्ट अ वॉल्टिंग ऐम्बिशन.
Korean: 히 해드 압저브드 더 비즈니스 라이프 어브 하와이 앤드 디벨롭트 아 벌팅 앰비션.

Original English: I may manage to freight a cargo back as well.
English: i may manage to freight a cargo back as well.
Hindi: आई मे मैनेज टू फ्रेट अ कार्गो बैक ऐज़ वेल.
Korean: 아이 메이 매니지 투 프레이트 아 카고 백 애즈 웰.

Original English: O'Brien had been a clean living young man with ideals.
English: o'brien had been a clean living young man with ideals.
Hindi: ओब्रायन हैड बीन अ क्लीन लिविंग यंग मैन विद आइडीअल्स.
Korean: 오브라이언 해드 빈 아 클린 리빙 영 맨 위드 아이디얼스.

Original English: He it was that lived to found the family of the Patino.
English: he it was that lived to found the family of the patino.
Hindi: ही इट वज दैट लिव्ड टू फाउंड द फैमिली अव द पातीनो.
Korean: 히 잇 워즈 댓 리브드 투 파운드 더 패밀리 어브 더 패티노.

Original English: Straight out they swam, their heads growing smaller and smaller.
English: straight out they swam, their heads growing smaller and smaller.
Hindi: स्ट्रेट आउट थे स्वैम, दैर हेड्स ग्रोइंग स्मॉलर एंड स्मॉलर.
Korean: 스트레이트 아웃 데이 스왐, 데어 헤즈 그로잉 스몰러 앤드 스몰러.

Original English: You won't die of malnutrition, be sure of that.
English: you will not die of malnutrition, be sure of that.
Hindi: यू विल नॉट डाई अव मैलन्यूट्रिशन, बी श्योर अव दैट.
Korean: 유 윌 낫 다이 어브 말뉴트리션, 비 슈어 어브 댓.

Original English: See the length of the body and that elongated neck.
English: see the length of the body and that elongated neck.
Hindi: सी द लेंग्थ अव द बॉडी एंड दॅट इलॉन्गेटेड नेक.
Korean: 시 더 렝스 오브 더 바디 앤드 댓 일롱게이티드 넥.

Original English: They are coming ashore, whoever they are.
English: they are coming ashore, whoever they are.
Hindi: दे आर कमिंग अशोर, हूएवर दे आर.
Korean: 데이 아 커밍 아쇼어, 후에버 데이 아.

Original English: Soaked in seawater they offset the heat rays.
English: soaked in seawater they offset the heat rays.
Hindi: सोक्त इन सीवॉटर दे ऑफसेट द हीट रेज़.
Korean: 소크트 인 시워터 데이 오프셋 더 히트 레이즈.

Original English: Think of investing in such an adventure.
English: think of investing in such an adventure.
Hindi: थिंक अव इन्वेस्टिंग इन सच अन एडवेंचर.
Korean: 띵크 어브 인베스팅 인 서치 안 어드벤처.

Original English: Nobody knew his history, they of the Junta least of all.
English: nobody knew his history, they of the junta least of all.
Hindi: नोबडी न्यू हिज़ हिस्टरी, थे अव द जुंटा लीस्ट अव ऑल.
Korean: 노바디 뉴 히즈 히스토리, 데이 어브 더 준타 리스트 어브 올.

Original English: I have been doubly baptized.
English: i have been doubly baptized.
Hindi: आई हैव बिन डब्ली बैपटाइज्ड.
Korean: 아이 해브 빈 더블리 밥타이즈드.

Original English: They wouldn't be sweeping a big vessel like the Martha.
English: they would not be sweeping a big vessel like the martha.
Hindi: दे वुड नाट बी स्वीपिंग अ बिग वेसल लाइक द मार्था.
Korean: 데이 우드 낫 비 스위핑 아 빅 베슬 라이크 더 마르타.

Original English: Joan looked triumphantly at Sheldon, who bowed.
English: joan looked triumphantly at sheldon, who bowed.
Hindi: जोन लुक्ट ट्रायअंफन्ट्ली ऐट शेल्डन, हू बाउड.
Korean: 존 룩트 트라이엄펀틀리 앳 셸던, 후 바우드.

Original English: And I hope you've got plenty of chain out, Captain Young.
English: and i hope you have got plenty of chain out, captain young.
Hindi: ऐंड आई होप यू हैव गॉट प्लेंटी अव चेन आउट, कैप्टन यंग.
Korean: 앤드 아이 호프 유 해브 갓 플렌티 어브 체인 아웃, 캡틴 영.

Original English: The discovery seemed to have been made on the spur of the moment.
English: the discovery seemed to have been made on the spur of the moment.
Hindi: द डिस्कवरी सीम्ड टू हैव बीन मेड ऑन द स्पर अव द मॉमेंट.
Korean: 더 디스커버리 심드 투 해브 빈 메이드 온 더 스퍼 옵 더 모먼트.

Original English: They handled two men already, both grub-thieves.
English: they handled two men already, both grub-thieves.
Hindi: दे हैंडल्ड टू मेन ऑलरेडी, बोथ ग्रब-थीव्ज़.
Korean: 데이 핸들드 투 맨 알레디, 보스 그럽시브즈.

Original English: Eli Harding asked, as Shunk started to follow.
English: eli harding asked, as shunk started to follow.
Hindi: इली हार्डिंग आस्क्ट, ऐज़ शंक स्टार्टेड टू फॉलो.
Korean: 일리 하딩 애스크트, 애즈 숑크 스타티드 투 폴로우.

Original English: Now go ahead and tell me in a straightforward way what has happened.
English: now go ahead and tell me in a straightforward way what has happened.
Hindi: नाऊ गो अहेड एंड टेल मी इन अ स्ट्रेटफॉरवर्ड वे वट हैज़ हैपेंड.
Korean: 나우 고 어헤드 앤드 텔 미 인 아 스트레이트포워드 웨이 왓 해즈 해펜드.

Original English: That's where they cut off the Scottish Chiefs and killed all hands.
English: that's where they cut off the scottish chiefs and killed all hands.
Hindi: दैट्स वेयर थे कट ऑफ द स्कॉटिश चीफ्स ऐंड किल्ड ऑल हैंड्स.
Korean: 댓츠 웨어 데이 컷 오프 더 스코티시 치프스 앤드 킬드 올 핸즈.

Original English: And after the bath a shave would not be bad.
English: and after the bath a shave would not be bad.
Hindi: ऐंड आफ्टर द बाथ अ शेव वुड नॉट बी बैड.
Korean: 앤 애프터 더 배쓰 아 쉐이브 우드 낫 비 배드.

Original English: Now please give a plain statement of what occurred.
English: now please give a plain statement of what occurred.
Hindi: नौ प्लीज़ गिव अ प्लेन स्टेटमेंट अव व्हाट अकर्ड.
Korean: 나우 플리즈 기브 아 플레인 스테이트먼트 오브 왓 어커드.

Original English: You can take a vacation on pay.
English: you can take a vacation on pay.
Hindi: यू कैन टेक अ वेकेशन ऑन पे.
Korean: 유 캔 테이크 아 베이케이션 온 페이.

Original English: They are big trees and require plenty of room.
English: they are big trees and require plenty of room.
Hindi: दे आर बिग ट्रीज़ ऐंड रिक्वायर प्लेंटी अव रूम.
Korean: 데이 아르 빅 트리즈 앤드 리콰이어 플렌티 어브 룸.

Original English: And Raoul listened again to the tale of the house.
English: and raoul listened again to the tale of the house.
Hindi: ऐंड राउल लिसन्ड अगेन टू द टेल अव द हाउस.
Korean: 앤 라울 리스넛 어게인 투 더 테일 오브 더 하우스.

Original English: There are no kiddies and half grown youths among them.
English: there are no kiddies and half grown youths among them.
Hindi: देर आर नो किडिज़ ऐंड हाफ ग्रोन यूथ्स अमंग धेम.
Korean: 데어 아 노 키디즈 앤드 해프 그로운 유스 어몽 뎀.

Original English: Oolong Atoll was one hundred and forty miles in circumference.
English: oolong atoll was one hundred and forty miles in circumference.
Hindi: ऊलांग अटल वस वन हंड्रेड एंड फॉर्टी माइल्स इन सरकम्फरेंस.
Korean: 울롱 애톨 워즈 원 헌드레드 앤드 포티 마일즈 인 써컴퍼런스.

Original English: McCoy found a stifling, poisonous atmosphere in the pent cabin.
English: mccoy found a stifling, poisonous atmosphere in the pent cabin.
Hindi: मकॉय फाउंड अ स्टाइफलिंग, पॉइज़नस एट्मॉस्फीयर इन द पेंट कैबिन.
Korean: 맥코이 파운드 아 스타이플링, 포이즈너스 앳머스피어 인 더 펜트 캐빈.

Original English: It would give me nervous prostration.
English: it would give me nervous prostration.
Hindi: इट वुड गिव मी नर्वस प्रोस्ट्रेशन.
Korean: 잇 우드 기브 미 너버스 프로스트레이션.

Original English: She said with chattering teeth.
English: she said with chattering teeth.
Hindi: शी सेड विथ चैटरिंग टीथ.
Korean: 쉬 세드 위드 차터링 티스.

Original English: I'll be out of my head in fifteen minutes.
English: i will be out of my head in fifteen minutes.
Hindi: आई विल बी आउट अव माई हेड इन फिफ्टीन मिनट्स.
Korean: 아이 윌 비 아웃 어브 마이 헤드 인 피프틴 미닛.

Original English: I do not blame you for anything; remember that.
English: i do not blame you for anything remember that.
Hindi: आई डू नॉट ब्लेम यू फॉर एनीथिंग रिमेम्बर दैट.
Korean: 아이 두 낫 블레임 유 포 애니씽 리멤버 댓.

Original English: If you mean to insinuate, Brentwood began hotly.
English: if you mean to insinuate, brentwood began hotly.
Hindi: इफ यू मीन टू इंसिन्युएट, ब्रेंटवुड बिगैन हॉटली.
Korean: 이프 유 민 투 인시뉴에이트, 브렌트우드 비긴 핫리.

Original English: The woman in you is only incidental, accidental, and irrelevant.
English: the woman in you is only incidental, accidental, and irrelevant.
Hindi: द वुमन इन यू इस ओनली इन्सिडेंटल, एक्सिडेंटल, एंड इरेलेवेंट.
Korean: 더 우먼 인 유 이즈 온리 인시던털, 악시던털, 앤드 이러레벙트.

Original English: There was no forecasting this strange girl's processes.
English: there was no forecasting this strange girl's processes.
Hindi: देर वस नो फॉर्कास्टिंग दिस स्ट्रेंज गर्ल्स प्रॉसेसिज़.
Korean: 데어 와즈 노 포어캐스팅 디스 스트레인지 걸스 프로세스즈.

Original English: But what they want with your toothbrush is more than I can imagine.
English: but what they want with your toothbrush is more than i can imagine.
Hindi: बट वट दे वांट विथ योर टूथब्रश इज मोर धन आई कैन इमैजिन.
Korean: 벗 왓 데이 원트 위드 요우르 투스브러쉬 이즈 모어 댄 아이 캔 이매진.

Original English: Give them their choice between a fine or an official whipping.
English: give them their choice between a fine or an official whipping.
Hindi: गिव देम धेर चॉइस बिट्वीन अ फाइन ऑर अन ऑफिशियल विपिंग.
Korean: 기브 덤 더 초이스 비트윈 아 파인 오어 안 어피셜 위핑.

Original English: Keep an eye on him.
English: keep an eye on him.
Hindi: कीप अन आई ऑन हिम.
Korean: 킵 안 아이 온 힘.

Original English: Those are my oysters, he said at last.
English: those are my oysters, he said at last.
Hindi: धोज आर माई ऑइस्टर्स, ही सेड एट लास्ट.
Korean: 도우즈 아르 마이 오이스터즈, 히 세드 앗 라스트.

Original English: They are not regular oyster pirates, Nicholas continued.
English: they are not regular oyster pirates, nicholas continued.
Hindi: थे आर नॉट रेग्युलर ऑयस्टर पाइरेट्स, निकोलस कंटिन्यूड.
Korean: 데이 아르 낫 레귤러 오이스터 파이럿츠, 니콜러스 컨티뉴드.

Original English: One by one the boys were captured.
English: one by one the boys were captured.
Hindi: वन बाइ वन द बॉयज वर कैप्चर्ड.
Korean: 원 바이 원 더 보이즈 워 캡쳐드.

Original English: The weeks had gone by, and no overt acts had been attempted.
English: the weeks had gone by, and no overt acts had been attempted.
Hindi: द वीक्स हैड गॉन बाई, ऐंड नो ओवर्ट ऐक्ट्स हैड बीन अटेम्प्टेड.
Korean: 더 위크스 햇 곤 바이, 앤드 노 오버트 액츠 햇 빈 어템트드.

Original English: Here, in the midmorning, the first casualty occurred.
English: here, in the midmorning, the first casualty occurred.
Hindi: हिर, इन द मिडमॉर्निंग, द फर्स्ट कैजुअल्टी अकर्ड.
Korean: 히어, 인 더 미드모닝, 더 퍼스트 캐주얼티 어커드.

Original English: They were deep in the primeval forest.
English: they were deep in the primeval forest.
Hindi: दे वर दीप इन द प्राइमिवल फॉरेस्ट.
Korean: 데이 웨 딥 인 더 프라임이벌 포레스트.

Original English: He had been foiled in his attempt to escape.
English: he had been foiled in his attempt to escape.
Hindi: ही हैड बीन फॉइल्ड इन हिज़ अटेम्प्ट टू एस्केप.
Korean: 히 핻 빈 포일드 인 히즈 어템프트 투 에스케이프.

Original English: And twenty men could hold it with spears and arrows.
English: and twenty men could hold it with spears and arrows.
Hindi: एंड ट्वेंटी मेन कुड होल्ड इट विथ स्पीयर्स एंड एरोज़.
Korean: 앤 트웬티 멘 컬드 홀드 잇 위드 스피어즈 앤 에로우즈.

Original English: Bassett was a fastidious man.
English: bassett was a fastidious man.
Hindi: बैसिट वस अ फैस्टिडियस मैन.
Korean: 배싯 워즈 아 패스티디어스 맨.

Original English: There's a big English general right now whose name is Roberts.
English: there's a big english general right now whose name is roberts.
Hindi: देर अ बिग इंग्लिश जनरल राइट नाउ हूज़ नेम इज़ रॉबर्ट्स.
Korean: 데어즈 아 빅 잉글리쉬 제너럴 라이트 나우 후즈 네임 이즈 로버츠.

Original English: This tacit promise of continued acquaintance gave Saxon a little joy-thrill.
English: this tacit promise of continued acquaintance gave saxon a little joy-thrill.
Hindi: दिस टैसिट प्रॉमिस अव कंटिन्यूड अक्वेंटेंस गेव सैक्सन अ लिटल जॉय-थ्रिल.
Korean: 디스 태싯 프라미스 어브 컨티뉴드 어퀘인턴스 게이브 색슨 아 리틀 조이쓰릴.

Original English: I tell you I am disgusted with this adventure tomfoolery and rot.
English: i tell you i am disgusted with this adventure tomfoolery and rot.
Hindi: आई टेल यू आई ऐम डिसगस्टेड विथ दिस एडवेंचर टॉमफूलरी ऐंड रॉट.
Korean: 아이 텔 유 아이 앰 디스거스티드 위드 디스 어드벤처 탐풀이 앤드 랏.

Original English: From my earliest recollection my sleep was a period of terror.
English: from my earliest recollection my sleep was a period of terror.
Hindi: फ्रॉम माई अर्लीस्ट रिकलेक्शन माई स्लीप वज अ पीरियड अव टेरर.
Korean: 프롬 마이 얼리스트 리콜렉션 마이 슬립 워즈 아 피어리어드 어브 테러.

Original English: But all my dreams violated this law.
English: but all my dreams violated this law.
Hindi: बट ऑल माइ ड्रीम्स वायलेटेड दिस लॉ.
Korean: 벗 올 마이 드림즈 바이올레이티드 디스 로.

Original English: It is very plausible to such people, a most convincing hypothesis.
English: it is very plausible to such people, a most convincing hypothesis.
Hindi: इट इज वेरी प्लॉज़िबल टू सच पीपल, अ मोस्ट कन्विन्सिंग हायपोथेसिस.
Korean: 잇 이즈 베리 플로즈블 투 서치 피플, 아 모스트 컨빈싱 하이퍼씨스.

Original English: But they make the mistake of ignoring their own duality.
English: but they make the mistake of ignoring their own duality.
Hindi: बट दे मेक द मिस्टेक अव इग्नोरिंग धेर ओन डुअलिटी.
Korean: 벗 데 메이크 더 미스테이크 어브 이그노링 데어 오운 듀엘리티.

Original English: I graduated last of my class.
English: i graduated last of my class.
Hindi: आई ग्रैजुएटेड लास्ट अव माई क्लास.
Korean: 아이 그레듀에이티드 라스트 어브 마이 클래스.

Original English: They had no fixed values, to be altered by adjectives and adverbs.
English: they had no fixed values, to be altered by adjectives and adverbs.
Hindi: दे हैड नो फिक्स्ड वैल्यूज़, टू बी आल्टर्ड बाई ऐडजेक्टिव्ज ऐंड ऐडवर्ब्स.
Korean: 데이 헤드 노 픽스트 밸류즈, 투 비 올터드 바이 애드젝티브스 앤드 애드벌브즈.

Original English: He was pressing beyond the limits of his vocabulary.
English: he was pressing beyond the limits of his vocabulary.
Hindi: ही वज़ प्रेसिंग बियॉन्ड द लिमिट्स अव हिज़ वोकैब्युलरी.
Korean: 히 와즈 프레싱 비욘드 더 리미츠 어브 히즈 보캐뷸러리.

Original English: Very early in my life, I separated from my mother.
English: very early in my life, i separated from my mother.
Hindi: वेरी अर्ली इन माय लाइफ, आई सेपरेटेड फ्रम माय मदर.
Korean: 베리 얼리 인 마이 라이프, 아이 세퍼레이트 프럼 마이 마더.

Original English: His infernal chattering worries me even now as I think of it.
English: his infernal chattering worries me even now as i think of it.
Hindi: हिस इन्फर्नल चैटरिंग वरिज मी ईवन नाउ ऐज आई थिंक अव इट.
Korean: 히즈 인퍼널 채터링 워리즈 미 이븐 나우 애즈 아이 띵크 오브 잇.

Original English: White Leghorns, said Mrs Mortimer.
English: white leghorns, said missus mortimer.
Hindi: वाइट लेगहॉर्न्स, सेड मिसस मॉर्टिमर.
Korean: 화이트 레그혼스, 세드 미씨스 모티머.

Original English: Massage under tension, was the cryptic reply.
English: massage under tension, was the cryptic reply.
Hindi: मसाज अंडर टेंशन, वज़ द क्रिप्टिक रिप्लाई.
Korean: 마사지 언더 텐션, 워즈 더 크립틱 리플라이.

Original English: Therefore, hurrah for the game.
English: therefore, hurrah for the game.
Hindi: देरफोर, हुर्रा फॉर द गेम.
Korean: 데어포어, 허라 포어 더 게임.

Original English: It lived in perpetual apprehension of that quarter of the compass.
English: it lived in perpetual apprehension of that quarter of the compass.
Hindi: इट लिव्ड इन परपेचुअल अप्रिहेंशन अव दैट क्वार्टर अव द कम्पस.
Korean: 잇 리브드 인 퍼페추얼 앱리헨션 오브 댓 쿼터 오브 더 컴퍼스.

Original English: Broken-Tooth yelled with fright and pain.
English: broken-tooth yelled with fright and pain.
Hindi: ब्रोकेन टूथ येल्ड विथ फ्राइट ऐंड पेन.
Korean: 브로큰투스 옐드 위드 프라이트 앤드 페인.

Original English: Thus was momentum gained in the Younger World.
English: thus was momentum gained in the younger world.
Hindi: धस वस मोमेंटम गेन्ड इन द यंगर वर्ल्ड.
Korean: 따스 와즈 모멘텀 게인드 인 더 영거 월드.

Original English: Saxon waited, for she knew a fresh idea had struck Billy.
English: saxon waited, for she knew a fresh idea had struck billy.
Hindi: सैक्सन वेटिड, फॉर शी न्यू अ फ्रेश आइडिया हैड स्ट्रक बिली.
Korean: 삭슨 웨이티드, 포어 시 누 아 프레쉬 아이디어 햇 스트럭 빌리.

Original English: We had been chased by them ourselves, more than once.
English: we had been chased by them ourselves, more than once.
Hindi: वी हैड बीन चेस्ट बाय देम आउरसेल्व्ज़, मोर दन वन्स.
Korean: 위 핻 빈 체이스트 바이 뎀 아우어셀브스, 모어 댄 원스.

Original English: He was a wise hyena.
English: he was a wise hyena.
Hindi: ही वस अ वाइज हाईना.
Korean: 히 워즈 아 와이즈 하이에나.

Original English: Production is doubling and quadrupling upon itself.
English: production is doubling and quadrupling upon itself.
Hindi: प्रोडक्शन इस डबलिंग ऐंड क्वाड्रूपलिंग अपॉन इट्सेल्फ.
Korean: 프로덕션 이즈 더블링 앤드 콰드루플링 어폰 잇셀프.

Original English: And the Edinburgh Evening News says, with editorial gloom.
English: and the edinburgh evening news says, with editorial gloom.
Hindi: एंड दि एडिनबर्ग ईवनिंग न्यूज़ सेज़, विथ एडिटोरियल ग्लूम.
Korean: 앤드 디 에딘버러 이브닝 뉴스 세즈, 위드 에디토리얼 글룸.

Original English: With my strength I slammed it full into Red-Eye's face.
English: with my strength i slammed it full into red-eye's face.
Hindi: विथ माई स्ट्रेंथ आई स्लैम्ड इट फुल इंटू रेड-आईज़ फेस.
Korean: 위드 마이 스트렝쓰 아이 슬램드 잇 풀 인투 레드아이즈 페이스.

Original English: The log on which Lop-Ear was lying got adrift.
English: the log on which lop-ear was lying got adrift.
Hindi: द लॉग ऑन विच लॉप-ईर वस लाइइंग गॉट अड्रिफ्ट.
Korean: 더 로그 언 위치 랍이어 워즈 라잉 갓 어드리프트.

Original English: This is a common experience with all of us.
English: this is a common experience with all of us.
Hindi: दिस इज़ अ कॉमन एक्सपीरियंस विथ ऑल अव अस.
Korean: 디스 이즈 아 커먼 익스피리언스 위드 올 어브 어스.

Original English: He considered the victory already his and stepped forward to the meat.
English: he considered the victory already his and stepped forward to the meat.
Hindi: ही कन्सिडर्ड द विक्टरी ऑलरेडी हिस ऐंड स्टेप्ट फॉरवर्ड टू द मीट.
Korean: 히 컨시더드 더 빅토리 올레디 히즈 앤드 스텝트 포워드 투 더 미트.

Original English: It was not Red-Eye's way to forego revenge so easily.
English: it was not red-eye's way to forego revenge so easily.
Hindi: इट वस नॉट रेड-आइज़ वे टू फोरगो रिवेंज सो ईज़िली.
Korean: 잇 워즈 낫 레드아이즈 웨이 투 포어고 리벤지 소 이지리.

Original English: Whiz-zip-bang. Lop-Ear screamed with sudden anguish.
English: whiz-zip-bang. lop-ear screamed with sudden anguish.
Hindi: विज़-जिप-बैंग. लॉप-ईयर स्क्रीम्ड विद सडन एंग्विश.
Korean: 위즈집방. 랍이얼 스크림드 위드 서든 앵귀쉬.

Original English: Cherokee identified himself with his instinct.
English: cherokee identified himself with his instinct.
Hindi: चेरोकी आइडेंटिफाइड हिमसेल्फ विद हिज़ इंस्टिंक्ट.
Korean: 체로키 아이덴티파이드 힘셀프 위드 히즈 인스팅트.

Original English: They were less stooped than we, less springy in their movements.
English: they were less stooped than we, less springy in their movements.
Hindi: दे वर लेस स्टूप्ड धन वी, लेस स्प्रिंगी इन धेर मूवमेंट्स.
Korean: 데이 워 레스 스툽트 단 위, 레스 스프링이 인 데어 무브먼츠.

Original English: The Fire People, like ourselves, lived in caves.
English: the fire people, like ourselves, lived in caves.
Hindi: द फायर पीपल, लाइक आउरसेल्व्ज़, लिव्ड इन केव्स.
Korean: 더 파이어 피플, 라이크 아우어셀브즈, 리브드 인 케이브즈.

Original English: Ah, indeed.
English: ah, indeed.
Hindi: आ, इंडीड.
Korean: 아, 인디드.

Original English: Red-Eye never committed a more outrageous deed.
English: red-eye never committed a more outrageous deed.
Hindi: रेड-आई नेवर कमिटेड अ मोर आउटरेजस डीड.
Korean: 레드아이 네버 커미티드 아 모어 아웃레이지어스 디드.

Original English: Poor little Crooked-Leg was terribly scared.
English: poor little crooked-leg was terribly scared.
Hindi: पूर लिटल क्रुक्ड-लेग वस टेरिब्ली स्केयर्ड.
Korean: 푸어 리틀 크룩레그 워즈 테러블리 스케어드.

Original English: Unconsciously, our yells and exclamations yielded to this rhythm.
English: unconsciously, our yells and exclamations yielded to this rhythm.
Hindi: अंकांशसली, आउर येल्स ऐंड एक्स्कलमेशंस यील्डिड टू धिस रिदम.
Korean: 언컨셔슬리, 아우어 옐스 앤드 익스클러메이션스 일디드 투 디스 리듬.

Original English: This is no place for you.
English: this is no place for you.
Hindi: दिस इज नो प्लेस फॉर यू.
Korean: 디스 이즈 노우 플레이스 포어 유.

Original English: He'll knock you off a few sticks in no time.
English: he will knock you off a few sticks in no time.
Hindi: ही विल नॉक यू ऑफ अ फ्यू स्टिक्स इन नो टाइम.
Korean: 히 윌 낙 유 오프 아 퓨 스틱스 인 노 타임.

Original English: Red-Eye swung back and forth on the branch farther down.
English: red-eye swung back and forth on the branch farther down.
Hindi: रेडआई स्वंग बैक ऐंड फॉर्थ ऑन द ब्रांच फारदर डाउन.
Korean: 레드아이 스웅 백 앤드 포스 온 더 브랜치 파더 다운.

Original English: So unexpected was my charge that I knocked him off his feet.
English: so unexpected was my charge that i knocked him off his feet.
Hindi: सो अनएक्सपेक्टेड वज माई चार्ज दैट आई नॉक्ड हिम ऑफ हिज फीट.
Korean: 소 언익스펙티드 와즈 마이 차지 댓 아이 녹트 힘 오프 히즈 피트.

Original English: Encouraged by my conduct, Big-Face became a sudden ally.
English: encouraged by my conduct, big-face became a sudden ally.
Hindi: इंकरिज्ड बाई माई कंडक्ट, बिगफेस बिकेम अ सडन ऐलाई.
Korean: 엔커리지드 바이 마이 컨덕트, 빅페이스 비케임 아 서든 앨라이.

Original English: The fighting had now become intermittent.
English: the fighting had now become intermittent.
Hindi: द फाइटिंग हैड नाउ बिकम इंटरमिटेंट.
Korean: 더 파이팅 해드 나우 비컴 인터미턴트.

Original English: They obeyed him, and went here and there at his commands.
English: they obeyed him, and went here and there at his commands.
Hindi: दे ओबेड हिम, ऐंड वेंट हीर ऐंड धेर ऐट हिज कमांड्स.
Korean: 데이 오베이드 힘, 앤드 웬트 히어 앤드 데어 앳 히즈 커맨즈.

Original English: It was like the beating of hoofs.
English: it was like the beating of hoofs.
Hindi: इट वज़ लाइक द बीटिंग अव हूफ्स.
Korean: 잇 와즈 라이크 더 비팅 어브 후프스.

Original English: Why, doggone you all, shake again.
English: why, doggone you all, shake again.
Hindi: वाय, डॉगन यू ऑल, शेक अगेन.
Korean: 와이, 도곤 유 올, 쉐이크 어게인.

Original English: Seventeen, no, eighteen days ago.
English: seventeen, no, eighteen days ago.
Hindi: सेवेंटीन, नो, ऐटीन डेज़ अगो.
Korean: 세븐틴, 노, 에이틴 데이즈 어고.

Original English: You mean for this State, General, Alberta.
English: you mean for this state, general, alberta.
Hindi: यू मीन फॉर दिस स्टेट, जनरल, अल्बर्टा.
Korean: 유 민 포 디스 스테이트, 제너럴, 앨버타.

Original English: He seemed to fill it with his tremendous vitality.
English: he seemed to fill it with his tremendous vitality.
Hindi: ही सीम्ड टू फिल इट विथ हिज ट्रेमेंडस वाइटैलिटी.
Korean: 히 심드 투 필 잇 위드 히즈 트레멘더스 바이탤리티.

Original English: She was trying to pass the apron string around him.
English: she was trying to pass the apron string around him.
Hindi: शी वज ट्रायिंग टू पास दि एप्रन स्ट्रिंग अराउंड हिम.
Korean: 시 워즈 트라이잉 투 패스 디 에이프런 스트링 어라운드 힘.

Original English: Get down and dig in.
English: get down and dig in.
Hindi: गेट डाउन ऐंड डिग इन.
Korean: 겟 다운 앤드 딕 인.

Original English: They are greatly delighted with anything that is bright or giveth a sound.
English: they are greatly delighted with anything that is bright or giveth a sound.
Hindi: दे आर ग्रेटली डिलाइटेड विथ एनिथिंग दैट इज ब्राइट ऑर गिवेथ अ साउंड.
Korean: 데이 아르 그레이트리 딜라이티드 위드 애니씽 댓 이즈 브라이트 오르 기브스 아 사운드.

Original English: They only lifted seven hundred and fifty.
English: they only lifted seven hundred and fifty.
Hindi: थेई ओनली लिफ्टेड सेवन हंड्रेड ऐंड फिफ्टी.
Korean: 데이 온리 리프티드 세븐 헌드레드 앤드 피프티.

Original English: It was simple, in its way, and no virtue of his.
English: it was simple, in its way, and no virtue of his.
Hindi: इट वज सिंपल, इन इट्स वे, एंड नो वर्चू अव हिस.
Korean: 잇 워즈 심플, 인 잇츠 웨이, 앤드 노 버츄 어브 히즈.

Original English: Is that Pat Hanrahan's mug looking hungry and willing.
English: is that pat hanrahan's mug looking hungry and willing.
Hindi: इस दैट पैट हैनरहैंज़ मग लुकिंग हंग्री ऐंड विलिंग.
Korean: 이즈 댓 팻 한라누한즈 머그 룩킹 헝그리 앤드 윌링.

Original English: It was more like sugar.
English: it was more like sugar.
Hindi: इट वस मोर लाइक शुगर.
Korean: 잇 워즈 모어 라이크 슈가.

Original English: I'm sure going along with you all, Elijah.
English: i am sure going along with you all, elijah.
Hindi: आई ऐम शुर गोइंग अलांग विथ यू ऑल, इलाइजा.
Korean: 아이 앰 슈어 고잉 어롱 위드 유 올, 일라자.

Original English: Here the explosion of mirth drowned him out.
English: here the explosion of mirth drowned him out.
Hindi: हीर दि एक्सप्लोजन अव मर्थ ड्राउंड हिम आउट.
Korean: 히어 디 익스플로전 오브 머스 드라운드 힘 아웃.

Original English: Fresh meat they failed to obtain.
English: fresh meat they failed to obtain.
Hindi: फ्रेश मीट थे फेल्ड टू अबटेन.
Korean: 프레쉬 메트 데이 페일드 투 어브테인.

Original English: A burst of laughter was his reward.
English: a burst of laughter was his reward.
Hindi: अ बर्स्ट अव लाफ्टर वाज़ हिज़ रिवॉर्ड.
Korean: 아 버스트 어브 래프터 워즈 히즈 리워드.

Original English: You don't catch me at any such foolishness.
English: you do not catch me at any such foolishness.
Hindi: यू डू नाट कैच मी ऐट एनी सच फूलिशनेस.
Korean: 유 두 낫 캐치 미 앳 에니 서치 풀리쉬니스.

Original English: A month passed by, and Bonanza Creek remained quiet.
English: a month passed by, and bonanza creek remained quiet.
Hindi: अ मन्थ पास्ट बाई, ऐंड बनान्ज़ा क्रीक रिमेन्ड क्वायट.
Korean: 아 먼스 패스트 바이, 앤드 보난자 크릭 리메인드 콰이어트.

Original English: They continued valiantly to lie, but the truth continued to outrun them.
English: they continued valiantly to lie, but the truth continued to outrun them.
Hindi: थे कंटिन्युड वैलियंटली टू लाई, बट द ट्रूथ कंटिन्युड टू आउटरन देम.
Korean: 데이 컨티뉴드 밸리언틀리 투 라이, 벗 더 트루스 컨티뉴드 투 아웃런 뎀.

Original English: Earth and gravel seemed to fill the pan.
English: earth and gravel seemed to fill the pan.
Hindi: अर्थ एंड ग्रैवल सीम्ड टू फिल द पैन.
Korean: 어스 앤드 그래블 심드 투 필 더 팬.

Original English: But he no longer cared quite so much for that form of diversion.
English: but he no longer cared quite so much for that form of diversion.
Hindi: बट ही नो लॉन्गर केर्ड क्वाइट सो मच फॉर दैट फॉर्म अव डाइवर्ज़न.
Korean: 벗 히 노 롱거 캐어드 콰이트 소 머치 포어 댓 폼 어브 다이버전.

Original English: But he did not broach it, preferring to mature it carefully.
English: but he did not broach it, preferring to mature it carefully.
Hindi: बट ही डिड नॉट ब्रोच इट, प्रिफरिंग टू मेचुर इट केयरफुली.
Korean: 버트 히 딛 낫 브로치 잇, 프리퍼링 투 머쳐 잇 캐어폴리.

Original English: Nope, not the slightest idea.
English: nope, not the slightest idea.
Hindi: नोप, नॉट द स्लाइटेस्ट आइडिया.
Korean: 놉, 낫 더 슬라이티스트 아이디어.

Original English: It is not an attempt to smash the market.
English: it is not an attempt to smash the market.
Hindi: इट इज नॉट अन अटेम्प्ट टू स्मैश द मार्केट.
Korean: 잇 이즈 낫 안 어템프트 투 스매쉬 더 마켓.

Original English: We have plenty of capital ourselves, and yet we want more.
English: we have plenty of capital ourselves, and yet we want more.
Hindi: वी हैव प्लेंटी अव कैपिटल आवरसेल्व्स, ऐंड येट वी वांट मोर.
Korean: 위 해브 플렌티 오브 캐피털 아우어셀브즈, 앤드 옛 위 원트 모어.

Original English: These rumors may even originate with us.
English: these rumors may even originate with us.
Hindi: दीज़ रूमर्स मे ईवन ओरिजिनेट विद अस.
Korean: 디즈 루머즈 메이 이븐 오리지네이트 위드 어스.

Original English: A wildly exciting time was his during the week preceding Thursday the eighteenth.
English: a wildly exciting time was his during the week preceding thursday the eighteenth.
Hindi: अ वाइल्डली एक्साइटिंग टाइम वज हिज़ ड्यूरिंग द वीक प्रिसीडिंग थर्सडे दि एटीन्थ.
Korean: 아 와일드리 엑사이팅 타임 워즈 히즈 듀링 더 위크 프리시딩 서즈데이 디 에이틴스.

Original English: There is not an iota of truth in it, certainly not.
English: there is not an iota of truth in it, certainly not.
Hindi: देर इस नाट अन आयोरा अव ट्रूथ इन इट, सर्टनली नाट.
Korean: 데어 이즈 낫 안 아이오타 오브 트루스 인 잇, 서튼리 낫.

Original English: I just do appreciate it without being able to express my feelings.
English: i just do appreciate it without being able to express my feelings.
Hindi: आई जस्ट डू एप्रिशिएट इट विदाउट बीइंग एबल टू एक्सप्रेस माय फीलिंग्स.
Korean: 아이 저스트 두 어프리시에이트 잇 위다웃 빙 에이블 투 엑스프레스 마이 필링즈.

Original English: In partnership with Daylight, the pair raided the San Jose Interurban.
English: in partnership with daylight, the pair raided the san jose interurban.
Hindi: इन पार्टनरशिप विथ डेलाइट, द पेअर रेडिड द सैन होसे इंटरअर्बन.
Korean: 인 파트너십 위드 데이라이트, 더 페어 레이디드 더 산 호세 인터어번.
