Original English: He saw all men in the business game doing this.
English: he saw all men in the business game doing this.
Hindi: ही सॉ ऑल मेन इन द बिजनेस गेम डूइंग दिस.
Korean: 히 소 올 멘 인 더 비즈니스 게임 두잉 디스.

Original English: It issued a rate of forty two dollars a car on charcoal.
English: it issued a rate of forty two dollars a car on charcoal.
Hindi: इट इशूड अ रेट अव फॉर्टी टू डॉलर्स अ कार ऑन चारकोल.
Korean: 잇 이슈드 아 레이트 어브 포티 투 달러즈 아 카 온 차콜.

Original English: He saw only the effect in a general, sketchy way.
English: he saw only the effect in a general, sketchy way.
Hindi: ही सॉ ओनली दि इफेक्ट इन अ जनरल, स्केची वे.
Korean: 히 소 온리 디 이펙트 인 아 제너럴, 스케치 웨이.

Original English: Points of view, new ideas, life.
English: points of view, new ideas, life.
Hindi: पॉइंट्स अव व्यू, न्यू आइडियाज, लाइफ.
Korean: 포인츠 어브 뷰, 뉴 아이디어즈, 라이프.

Original English: But life's worth more than cash, she argued.
English: but life's worth more than cash, she argued.
Hindi: बट लाइफ्ज़ वर्थ मोर दन कैश, शी आर्ग्यूड.
Korean: 벗 라이프즈 워쓰 모어 댄 캐쉬, 쉬 아규드.

Original English: The butchers and meat cutters refused to handle meat destined for unfair restaurants.
English: the butchers and meat cutters refused to handle meat destined for unfair restaurants.
Hindi: द बुचरज़ एंड मीट कटर्स रिफ्यूज़्ड टू हैंडल मीट डेस्टिन्ड फॉर अनफेयर रेस्टोरेंट्स.
Korean: 더 부처스 앤드 미트 커터즈 리퓨즈드 투 핸들 미트 데스틴드 포 언페어 레스토랑츠.

Original English: Your price, my son, is just about thirty per week.
English: your price, my son, is just about thirty per week.
Hindi: योर प्राइस, माई सन, इस जस्ट अबाउट थर्टी पर वीक.
Korean: 유어 프라이스, 마이 선, 이즈 저스트 어바웃 서티 퍼 위크.

Original English: This sound did not disturb the hush and awe of the place.
English: this sound did not disturb the hush and awe of the place.
Hindi: दिस साउंड डिड नॉट डिस्टर्ब द हश ऐंड ऑ ऑव द प्लेस.
Korean: 디스 사운드 딛 낫 디스터브 더 허쉬 앤드 오 오브 더 플레이스.

Original English: That's why its boundaries are all gouged and jagged.
English: that's why its boundaries are all gouged and jagged.
Hindi: दैट्स वाय इट्स बाउंडरिज़ आर ऑल गाउज्ड एन्ड जैग्ड.
Korean: 댓츠 와이 잇츠 바운더리즈 알 올 가우지드 앤드 재그드.

Original English: How old are you, daddy.
English: how old are you, daddy.
Hindi: हाउ ओल्ड आर यू, डैडी.
Korean: 하우 올드 아르 유, 대디.

Original English: But in the canyons water was plentiful and also a luxuriant forest growth.
English: but in the canyons water was plentiful and also a luxuriant forest growth.
Hindi: बट इन द कैन्यन्स वॉटर वज़ प्लेंटिफुल ऐंड ऑल्सो अ लक्स्यूरियंट फॉरेस्ट ग्रोथ.
Korean: 버트 인 더 캐니언즈 워터 워즈 플렌티풀 앤드 올소 아 럭셔리언트 포레스트 그로우스.

Original English: My name's Ferguson.
English: my name's ferguson.
Hindi: माई नेम्ज़ फर्गुसन.
Korean: 마이 네임즈 퍼거슨.

Original English: Daylight found himself charmed and made curious by the little man.
English: daylight found himself charmed and made curious by the little man.
Hindi: डेलाइट फाउंड हिम्सेल्फ चार्म्ड ऐंड मेड क्यूरियस बाई द लिटल मैन.
Korean: 데이라이트 파운드 힘셀프 참드 앤드 메이드 큐리어스 바이 더 리틀 맨.

Original English: To his surprise, her answer was flat and uncompromising.
English: to his surprise, her answer was flat and uncompromising.
Hindi: टू हिस सरप्राइज, हर ऐंसर वॉज़ फ्लैट ऐंड अनकमप्रोमाइजिंग.
Korean: 투 히즈 서프라이즈, 허 앤서 워즈 플랫 앤드 언컴프라마이징.

Original English: The farmer works the soil and produces grain.
English: the farmer works the soil and produces grain.
Hindi: द फार्मर वर्क्स द सॉइल एंड प्रोडूसेस ग्रेन.
Korean: 더 파머 웍스 더 소일 앤드 프로듀스 그레인.

Original English: That's what Carnegie did.
English: that's what carnegie did.
Hindi: दैट्स वट कारनेगी डिड.
Korean: 댓츠 왓 카네기 딛.

Original English: I can't argue with you, and you know that.
English: i can not argue with you, and you know that.
Hindi: आई कैन नाट आर्ग्यू विथ यू, ऐंड यू नो दैट.
Korean: 아이 캔 낫 아규 위드 유, 앤드 유 노우 댓.

Original English: Bob, growing disgusted, turned back suddenly and attempted to pass Mab.
English: bob, growing disgusted, turned back suddenly and attempted to pass mab.
Hindi: बाब, ग्रोइंग डिसगस्टेड, टर्न्ड बैक सडनली ऐंड अटेम्पटेड टू पास मैब.
Korean: 밥, 그로잉 디스거스티드, 턴드 백 서든리 앤드 어템프티드 투 패스 맵.

Original English: It was my idea to a tee.
English: it was my idea to a tee.
Hindi: इट वज़ माई आईडिया टू अ टी.
Korean: 잇 워즈 마이 아이디어 투 아 티.

Original English: Mab, she said.
English: mab, she said.
Hindi: मैब, शी सैड.
Korean: 맵, 시 셋.

Original English: I'll go over tomorrow afternoon.
English: i will go over tomorrow afternoon.
Hindi: आई विल गो ओवर टुमारो आफ्टरनून.
Korean: 아이 윌 고 오버 투모로우 애프터눈.

Original English: But he reconciled himself to it by an act of faith.
English: but he reconciled himself to it by an act of faith.
Hindi: बट ही रेकनसाइल्ड हिम्सेल्फ टू इट बाई अन ऐक्ट अव फेथ.
Korean: 버트 히 레컨사일드 힘셀프 투 잇 바이 언 액트 어브 페이스.

Original English: There is that magnificent Bob, eating his head off in the stable.
English: there is that magnificent bob, eating his head off in the stable.
Hindi: देर इस दैट मैग्निफिसेंट बॉब, ईटिंग हिज हेड ऑफ इन द स्टेबल.
Korean: 대어 이즈 댓 매그니피센트 밥, 이팅 히즈 헤드 오프 인 더 스테이블.

Original English: Already he had begun borrowing from the banks.
English: already he had begun borrowing from the banks.
Hindi: ऑलरेडी ही हैड बिगन बॉरोइंग फ्रम द बैंक्स.
Korean: 알레디 히 해드 비건 보로잉 프롬 더 뱅크스.

Original English: It's the strap hangers that'll keep us from going under.
English: it's the strap hangers that will keep us from going under.
Hindi: इट्स द स्ट्रैप हैंगर्स दॅट विल कीप अस फ्रॉम गोइंग अंडर.
Korean: 잇츠 더 스트랩 행어즈 댓 윌 킵 어스 프럼 고잉 언더.

Original English: As for himself, weren't the street railway earnings increasing steadily.
English: as for himself, were not the street railway earnings increasing steadily.
Hindi: ऐज़ फॉर हिम्सेल्फ, वर नॉट द स्ट्रीट रेलवे अर्निंग्स इन्क्रीसिंग स्टेडिली.
Korean: 애즈 포어 힘셀프, 워 낫 더 스트리트 레일웨이 어닝스 인크리싱 스테디리.

Original English: A rising tide of fat had submerged them.
English: a rising tide of fat had submerged them.
Hindi: अ राइजिंग टाइड अव फैट हैड सबमर्ज्ड देम.
Korean: 아 라이징 타이드 어브 팻 핻 섭머지드 뎀.

Original English: Call me that again, he murmured ecstatically.
English: call me that again, he murmured ecstatically.
Hindi: कॉल मी दैट अगेन, ही मर्मर्ड एक्सटैटिकली.
Korean: 콜 미 댓 어게인, 히 머머드 엑스타티칼리.

Original English: In the car were Unwin and Harrison, while Jones sat with the chauffeur.
English: in the car were unwin and harrison, while jones sat with the chauffeur.
Hindi: इन द कार वर अनविन एंड हैरिसन, वाइल जोन्स सैट विद द शोफर.
Korean: 인 더 카 워 언윈 앤드 해리슨, 와일 존스 샛 위드 더 쇼퍼.

Original English: And here's another idea.
English: and here's another idea.
Hindi: ऐंड हिर्ज़ अनदर आइडिया.
Korean: 앤드 히어즈 어나더 아이디어.

Original English: Manuel had one besetting sin.
English: manuel had one besetting sin.
Hindi: मैनुएल हैड वन बिसेटिंग सिन.
Korean: 매뉴엘 해드 원 비세팅 신.

Original English: The man smiled grimly, and brought a hatchet and a club.
English: the man smiled grimly, and brought a hatchet and a club.
Hindi: द मैन स्माइल्ड ग्रिमली, एंड ब्रॉट अ हैचेट एंड अ क्लब.
Korean: 더 맨 스마일드 그림리, 앤드 브로트 아 해쳇 앤드 아 클럽.

Original English: Curly rushed her antagonist, who struck again and leaped aside.
English: curly rushed her antagonist, who struck again and leaped aside.
Hindi: कर्ली रश्ट हर ऐन्टैगनिस्ट, हू स्ट्रक अगेन एंड लीप्त असाइड.
Korean: 컬리 러쉬트 허 앤태거니스트, 후 스트럭 어갠 앤드 립트 어사이드.

Original English: His newborn cunning gave him poise and control.
English: his newborn cunning gave him poise and control.
Hindi: हिस न्यूबॉर्न कनिंग गेव हिम पॉइज़ ऐंड कंट्रोल.
Korean: 히즈 뉴본 커닝 게이브 힘 포이즈 앤드 컨트롤.

Original English: Perrault found one with head buried in the grub box.
English: perrault found one with head buried in the grub box.
Hindi: पेरॉल्ट फाउंड वन विथ हेड बेरिड इन द ग्रब बॉक्स.
Korean: 페로 파운드 원 위드 헤드 베리드 인 더 그럽 박스.

Original English: It seemed the ordained order of things that dogs should work.
English: it seemed the ordained order of things that dogs should work.
Hindi: इट सीम्ड दि ओर्डेइन्ड ऑर्डर अव थिंग्ज़ दॅट डॉग्ज़ शुड वर्क.
Korean: 잇 심드 디 오어드에인드 오더 어브 씽즈 댓 독스 슈드 웍.

Original English: And that was the last of Francois and Perrault.
English: and that was the last of francois and perrault.
Hindi: ऐंड दैट वस द लास्ट अव फ्रांस्वा ऐंड पेरॉल्ट.
Korean: 앤드 댓 워즈 더 라스트 어브 프랑수아 앤드 페로.

Original English: Mercedes screamed, cried, laughed, and manifested the chaotic abandonment of hysteria.
English: mercedes screamed, cried, laughed, and manifested the chaotic abandonment of hysteria.

Original English: The Eldorado emptied its occupants into the street to see the test.
English: the eldorado emptied its occupants into the street to see the test.
Hindi: दि एलडोराडो एम्प्टिड इट्स ऑक्यूपेंट्स इंटू द स्ट्रीट टू सी द टेस्ट.
Korean: 디 엘도라도 엠티드 잇츠 악큐펀츠 인투 더 스트리트 투 시 더 테스트.

Original English: He could feel a new stir in the land.
English: he could feel a new stir in the land.
Hindi: ही कुड फील अ न्यू स्टर इन द लैंड.
Korean: 히 쿳 필 아 누 스터 인 더 랜드.

Original English: So we have to fit the boat throughout with oil lamps as well.
English: so we have to fit the boat throughout with oil lamps as well.
Hindi: सो वी हैव टू फिट द बोट थ्रूआउट विथ ऑइल लैम्प्स ऐज़ वेल.
Korean: 소 위 해브 투 핏 더 보트 쓰루아웃 위드 오일 램프스 애즈 웰.

Original English: It will break our hearts and our backs to hoist anchor by hand.
English: it will break our hearts and our backs to hoist anchor by hand.
Hindi: इट विल ब्रेक आवर हार्ट्स ऐंड आवर बैक्स टू हॉइस्ट ऐंकर बाई हैंड.
Korean: 잇 윌 브레이크 아워 하츠 앤드 아워 백스 투 호이스트 앵커 바이 핸드.

Original English: There is another virtue in these bulkheads.
English: there is another virtue in these bulkheads.
Hindi: देर इस अनदर वर्चू इन दीज बुल्कहेड्स.
Korean: 데어 이즈 어나더 버츄 인 디즈 벌크헤즈.

Original English: But I am at the end of my resources.

Hindi: बट आई ऐम ऐट दि एंड अव माई रिसोर्सेस.

Original English: Now our figuring was all right.
English: now our figuring was all right.
Hindi: नाउ आऊर फिग्युरिंग वस ऑल राइट.
Korean: 나우 아우어 피규어링 워즈 올 라이트.

Original English: It lasted as a deterrent for two days.
English: it lasted as a deterrent for two days.
Hindi: इट लास्टेड ऐज़ अ डिटरेंट फॉर टू डेज़.
Korean: 잇 래스티드 애즈 아 디터런트 포어 투 데이즈.

Original English: The added weight had a velocity of fifteen miles per hour.
English: the added weight had a velocity of fifteen miles per hour.
Hindi: दि ऐडेड वेट हैड अ वेलोसिटी अव फिफ्टीन माइल्स पर आवर.

Original English: It is also an insidious, deceitful sun.
English: it is also an insidious, deceitful sun.
Hindi: इट इज आलसो अन इन्सिडियस, डिसीटफुल सन.
Korean: 잇 이즈 알소 안 인시디어스, 디시트풀 선.

Original English: The Portuguese boy crawled nearer and nearer.

Hindi: द पोर्टुगीज़ बॉय क्रॉल्ड नियरर एंड नियरर.
Korean: 더 포르투갈어 보이 크롤드 니어러 앤드 니어러.

Original English: The Portuguese boy passed the Hawaiian.

Korean: 더 포르투기즈 보이 패스트 더 하와이언.

Original English: When I came to I was waving my hat and murmuring ecstatically.
English: when i came to i was waving my hat and murmuring ecstatically.
Hindi: वेन आई केम टू आई वज़ वेविंग माय हैट एंड मर्मरिंग एक्सटैटिकली.
Korean: 웬 아이 케임 투 아이 워즈 웨이빙 마이 햇 앤드 머머링 엑스타티컬리.

Original English: By golly, the boy wins.
English: by golly, the boy wins.
Hindi: बाय गाली, द बॉय विन्स.
Korean: 바이 골리, 더 보이 윈즈.

Original English: Halfway around the track one donkey got into an argument with its rider.
English: halfway around the track one donkey got into an argument with its rider.
Hindi: हैफवे अराउंड द ट्रैक वन डॉनकी गॉट इंटू अन आर्ग्यूमेंट विद इट्स राइडर.

Original English: McVeigh when he returns from a trip to Honolulu.
English: mcveigh when he returns from a trip to honolulu.
Hindi: मक्वे वेन ही रिटर्न्ज़ फ्रम अ ट्रिप टू होनोलूलू.

Original English: Obviously, it was a disease that could be contracted by contact.
English: obviously, it was a disease that could be contracted by contact.
Hindi: आब्वियस्ली, इट वस अ डिज़ीज़ दैट कुड बी कंट्रैक्टिड बाय कॉन्टैक्ट.
Korean: 압비어슬리, 잇 워즈 아 디지즈 댓 쿳 비 컨트랙티드 바이 컨택트.

Original English: Otherwise no restriction is put upon their seafaring.
English: otherwise no restriction is put upon their seafaring.
Hindi: अदरवाइज नो रिस्ट्रिक्शन इस पुट अपॉन देर सीफेरिंग.

Original English: They do not know the length of time of incubation.
English: they do not know the length of time of incubation.
Hindi: दे डू नाट नो द लेंथ अव टाइम अव इन्क्यूबेशन.

Original English: Enters now the psychology of the situation.
English: enters now the psychology of the situation.
Hindi: एंटर्स नाउ द साइकालोजी अव द सिचुएशन.

Original English: It was not exactly a deportation.
English: it was not exactly a deportation.

Original English: Quick was the disappointment in his face, yet smiling was the acquiescence.
English: quick was the disappointment in his face, yet smiling was the acquiescence.
Hindi: क्विक वज़ द डिसअपॉइंटमेंट इन हिस फेस, येट स्माइलिंग वज़ दि एक्विएसेंस.

Original English: Nevertheless we found ourselves once more in the high seat of abundance.
English: nevertheless we found ourselves once more in the high seat of abundance.

Original English: Wada and Nakata were in a bit of a funk.
English: wada and nakata were in a bit of a funk.
Hindi: वादा ऐंड नकाता वेर इन अ बिट अव अ फंक.

Original English: The boy at the wheel lost his head.
English: the boy at the wheel lost his head.
Hindi: द बॉय ऐट द वील लॉस्ट हिज हेड.
Korean: 더 보이 앳 더 휠 로스트 히즈 헤드.

Original English: To her the bridge was tambo, which is the native for taboo.
English: to her the bridge was tambo, which is the native for taboo.
Hindi: टू हर द ब्रिज वस टैंबो, विच इज द नैटिव फॉर टैबू.

Original English: A half a case of tobacco was worth three pounds.
English: a half a case of tobacco was worth three pounds.
Hindi: अ हाफ अ केस अव टबैको वस वर्थ थ्री पाउंड्स.

Original English: What do you mean by this outrageous conduct.
English: what do you mean by this outrageous conduct.
Hindi: वट डू यू मीन बाय दिस आउटरेजस कंडक्ट.

Original English: But Martin smiled a superior smile.
English: but martin smiled a superior smile.
Hindi: बट मार्टिन स्माइल्ड अ सुपीरियर स्माइल.

Original English: By that answer my professional medical prestige stood or fell.

Hindi: बाई धैट आन्सर माई प्रोफेशनल मेडिकल प्रेस्टीज स्टूड ऑर फेल.

Original English: At sea, Monday, March 16, 1908.
English: at sea, monday, march 16, 1908.
Hindi: एट सी, मंडे, मार्च सिक्सटीन, नाइनटीन हंड्रेड.

Original English: At sea, Wednesday, March 18, 1908.
English: at sea, wednesday, march 18, 1908.

Korean: 앳 시, 웬즈데이, 마치 에이틴, 나인틴헌드레드.

Original English: Yes, sir, I corrected.
English: yes, sir, i corrected.
Hindi: यस, सर, आई करेक्टेड.
Korean: 예스, 써, 아이 커렉티드.

Original English: Violent life and athletic sports had never appealed to me.
English: violent life and athletic sports had never appealed to me.

Korean: 바이올런트 라이프 앤드 애슬레틱 스포츠 해드 네버 어필드 투 미.

Original English: You live on an income which your father earned.
English: you live on an income which your father earned.
Hindi: यू लाइव ऑन अन इनकम विच योर फादर अर्न्ड.
Korean: 유 라이브 온 안 인컴 위치 유어 파더 언드.

Original English: He was worth nothing to the world.
English: he was worth nothing to the world.
Hindi: ही वज़ वर्थ नथिंग टू द वर्ल्ड.
Korean: 히 워즈 워스 너씽 투 더 월드.

Original English: Then you don't believe in altruism.
English: then you do not believe in altruism.
Hindi: देन यू डू नाट बिलीव इन ऑल्ट्रूइज़म.
Korean: 덴 유 두 낫 빌리브 인 알트루이즘.

Original English: The creative joy, I murmured.
English: the creative joy, i murmured.
Hindi: द क्रिएटिव जॉय, आई मर्मर.
Korean: 더 크리에이티브 조이, 아이 머머드.

Original English: He deluged me, overwhelmed me with argument.
English: he deluged me, overwhelmed me with argument.
Hindi: ही डेल्यूज्ड मी, ओवरवेल्म्ड मी विथ आर्ग्युमेंट.
Korean: 히 델류지드 미, 오버웰름드 미 위드 아규먼트.

Original English: Ah, it is growing dark and darker.
English: ah, it is growing dark and darker.
Hindi: आ, इट इज ग्रोइंग डार्क ऐंड डार्कर.
Korean: 아, 잇 이즈 그로잉 다크 앤드 다커.

Original English: I was Hump, cabin boy on the schooner Ghost.
English: i was hump, cabin boy on the schooner ghost.
Hindi: आई वस हम्प, कैबिन बॉय ऑन द स्कूनर घोस्ट.
Korean: 아이 워즈 험프, 캐빈 보이 온 더 스쿠너 고스트.

Original English: A sinewy hand, dripping with water, was clutching the rail.
English: a sinewy hand, dripping with water, was clutching the rail.
Hindi: अ सिन्यूई हैंड, ड्रिपिंग विथ वॉटर, वज क्लचिंग द रेल.
Korean: 아 시뉴이 핸드, 드리핑 위드 워터, 워즈 클러칭 더 레일.

Original English: No man ate of the seal meat or the oil.
English: no man ate of the seal meat or the oil.
Hindi: नो मैन एट अव द सील मीट और दि ऑइल.
Korean: 노 맨 에이트 어브 더 씰 미트 오어 디 오일.

Original English: I noticed blood spouting from Kerfoot's left hand.
English: i noticed blood spouting from kerfoot's left hand.
Hindi: आई नोटिस्ड ब्लड स्पाउटिंग फ्रम करफूट्स लेफ्ट हैंड.
Korean: 아이 노티스드 블러드 스파우팅 프롬 커풋츠 레프트 핸드.

Original English: Three oilers and a fourth engineer, was his greeting.
English: three oilers and a fourth engineer, was his greeting.
Hindi: थ्री ऑयलर्स एंड अ फोर्थ इंजिनियर, वस हिस ग्रीटिंग.
Korean: 쓰리 오일러즈 앤드 아 포스 엔지니어, 워즈 히즈 그리팅.

Original English: Eighteen hundred, he calculated.
English: eighteen hundred, he calculated.
Hindi: एटीन हंड्रेड, ही कैल्कुलैटेड.
Korean: 에이틴 헌드레드, 히 캘큘레이트.

Original English: The sharp voice of Wolf Larsen aroused me.
English: the sharp voice of wolf larsen aroused me.
Hindi: द शार्प वॉइस अव वुल्फ लार्सन अराउज़्ड मी.
Korean: 더 샤프 보이스 어브 울프 라센 어라우즈드 미.

Original English: I obeyed, and a minute or two later they stood before him.
English: i obeyed, and a minute or two later they stood before him.
Hindi: आई ओबेड, एंड अ मिनट ऑर टू लेटर दे स्टूड बिफोर हिम.
Korean: 아이 오베이드, 앤드 아 미닛 오어 투 레이터 데이 스투드 비포어 힘.

Original English: But it won't continue, she said with easy confidence.
English: but it will not continue, she said with easy confidence.
Hindi: बट इट विल नाट कंटिन्यू, शी सेड विद ईज़ी कान्फिडेंस.
Korean: 벗 잇 윌 낫 컨티뉴, 쉬 세드 위드 이지 컨피던스.

Original English: What I saw I could not at first believe.
English: what i saw i could not at first believe.
Hindi: वट आई सॉ आई कुड नाट ऐट फर्स्ट बिलीव.
Korean: 왓 아이 소 아이 쿧 낫 앳 퍼스트 빌리브.

Original English: The stout wood was crushed like an eggshell.
English: the stout wood was crushed like an eggshell.
Hindi: द स्टाउट वुड वस क्रश्ड लाइक अन एगशेल.
Korean: 더 스타우트 우드 워즈 크러쉬드 라이크 안 엑셸.

Original English: There's too much of the schoolboy in me.
English: there's too much of the schoolboy in me.
Hindi: धेअर्स तू मच अव द स्कूलबॉय इन मी.
Korean: 데어즈 투 머치 어브 더 스쿨보이 인 미.

Original English: I had forgotten their existence.
English: i had forgotten their existence.
Hindi: आई हैड फॉरगोटन देयर एग्जिस्टन्स.
Korean: 아이 해드 포거튼 데어 엑지스턴스.

Original English: Ah, we were very close together in that moment.
English: ah, we were very close together in that moment.
Hindi: आ, वी वर वेरी क्लोस टुगेदर इन दॅट मोमेंट.
Korean: 아, 위 워 베리 클로스 투게더 인 댓 모멘트.

Original English: But she swung obediently on her heel into the wind.
English: but she swung obediently on her heel into the wind.
Hindi: बट शी स्वंग ओबीडीएन्ट्ली ऑन हर हील इंटू द विंड.
Korean: 벗 쉬 스웅 오비디언틀리 온 허 힐 인투 더 윈드.

Original English: They are his tongue, by which he makes his knowledge articulate.
English: they are his tongue, by which he makes his knowledge articulate.
Hindi: दे आर हिज़ टंग, बाई विच ही मेक्स हिज़ नॉलेज आर्टिकलेट.
Korean: 데이 아르 히즈 텅, 바이 위치 히 메이크스 히즈 날리지 아티큘레이트.

Original English: Between the rush of the cascades, streaks of rust showed everywhere.
English: between the rush of the cascades, streaks of rust showed everywhere.
Hindi: बिटवीन द रश अव द कैस्केड्स, स्ट्रीक्स अव रस्ट शोड एवरिवेर.
Korean: 비트윈 더 러쉬 오브 더 캐스케이즈, 스트릭스 오브 러스트 쇼드 에브리웨어.

Original English: He'll never do a tap of work the whole Voyage.
English: he will never do a tap of work the whole voyage.
Hindi: ही विल नेवर डू अ टैप अव वर्क द होल वॉयज.
Korean: 히 윌 네버 두 아 탭 어브 워크 더 홀 보이지.

Original English: Captain West may be a Samurai, but he is also human.
English: captain west may be a samurai, but he is also human.
Hindi: कैप्टन वेस्ट मे बी अ समुराई, बट ही इस आल्सो ह्यूमन.
Korean: 캡틴 웨스트 메이 비 아 사무라이, 버트 히 이즈 알소 휴먼.

Original English: And so early in the voyage, too.
English: and so early in the voyage, too.
Hindi: एंड सो अर्ली इन द वॉयज, टू.
Korean: 앤드 소 얼리 인 더 보이지, 투.

Original English: In the matter of curry she is a sheer genius.
English: in the matter of curry she is a sheer genius.
Hindi: इन द मैटर अव करी शी इस अ शीर जीनियस.
Korean: 인 더 매터 어브 커리 쉬 이즈 아 시어 지니어스.

Original English: The eastern heavens were equally spectacular.
English: the eastern heavens were equally spectacular.
Hindi: दि ईस्टर्न हेवन्स वर इक्वली स्पेक्टैक्युलर.
Korean: 디 이스턴 헤븐즈 워 이퀄리 스펙태큘러.

Original English: He spat it out like so much venom.
English: he spat it out like so much venom.
Hindi: ही स्पैट इट आउट लाइक सो मच वेनम.
Korean: 히 스팻 잇 아웃 라이크 소 머치 베넘.

Original English: I saw Mr Pike nod his head grimly and sarcastically.
English: i saw mister pike nod his head grimly and sarcastically.
Hindi: आई सॉ मिस्टर पाइक नॉड हिज़ हेड ग्रिमली ऐंड सार्कास्टिकली.
Korean: 아이 쏘 미스터 파이크 나드 히즈 헤드 그림리 앤드 사커스티컬리.

Original English: He is too keenly intelligent, too sharply sensitive, successfully to endure.
English: he is too keenly intelligent, too sharply sensitive, successfully to endure.
Hindi: ही इज़ टू कीनली इंटेलिजेंट, टू शार्पली सेंसिटिव, सक्सेसफुली टू एंड्योर.
Korean: 히 이즈 투 킨리 인텔리전트, 투 샤플리 센시티브, 석세스풀리 투 엔듀어.

Original English: The night was calm and snowy.
English: the night was calm and snowy.
Hindi: द नाइट वस कालम ऐंड स्नोइ.
Korean: 더 나잇 워즈 캄 앤드 스노이.

Original English: I sailed third mate in the little Vampire before you were born.
English: i sailed third mate in the little vampire before you were born.
Hindi: आई सेल्ड थर्ड मेट इन द लिटल वैम्पायर बिफोर यू वेर बॉर्न.
Korean: 아이 세일드 써드 메이트 인 더 리틀 뱀파이어 비포어 유 워 본.

Original English: His outstretched arm dropped to his side, and he paused.
English: his outstretched arm dropped to his side, and he paused.
Hindi: हिस आउटस्ट्रेट्च्ड आर्म ड्रॉप्ड टू हिस साइड, ऐंड ही पॉज़्ड.
Korean: 히즈 아웃스트레치트 아름 드랍트 투 히즈 사이드, 앤드 히 포즈드.

Original English: At this moment I felt a stir at my shoulder.
English: at this moment i felt a stir at my shoulder.
Hindi: ऐट दिस मोमेंट आई फेल्ट अ स्टर ऐट माय शोल्डर.
Korean: 앳 디스 모먼트 아이 펠트 아 스터 앳 마이 숄더.

Original English: Wada, Louis, and the steward are servants of Asiatic breed.
English: wada, louis, and the steward are servants of asiatic breed.
Hindi: वाडा, लूई, एंड द स्टूअर्ड आर सर्वेंट्स अव एशियाटिक ब्रीड.
Korean: 와다, 루이, 앤드 더 스튜어드 아 서번츠 어브 에이시아틱 브리드.

Original English: Also, she has forbidden them smoking their pipes in the after-room.
English: also, she has forbidden them smoking their pipes in the after-room.
Hindi: ऑलसो, शी हैज़ फरबिडन देम स्मोकिंग देर पाइप्स इन दि आफ्टरूम.
Korean: 알소, 쉬 해즈 포비든 뎀 스모킹 데어 파이프스 인 디 애프터룸.

Original English: I tried to read George Moore last night, and was dreadfully bored.
English: i tried to read george moore last night, and was dreadfully bored.
Hindi: आई ट्राइड टू रीड जॉर्ज मूर लास्ट नाइट, एंड वज़ ड्रेडफुली बोर्ड.
Korean: 아이 트라이드 투 리드 조지 무어 라스트 나이트, 앤드 워즈 드레드풀이 보어드.

Original English: Tom Spink has a harpoon.
English: tom spink has a harpoon.
Hindi: टॉम स्पिंक हैज़ अ हार्पून.
Korean: 탐 스핑크 해즈 아 하푼.

Original English: Nimrod replied, with a slight manifestation of sensitiveness.
English: nimrod replied, with a slight manifestation of sensitiveness.
Hindi: निमरॉड रिप्लाइड, विथ अ स्लाइट मैनिफेस्टेशन ऑफ सेंसिटिवनेस.
Korean: 님로드 리플라이드, 위드 아 슬라이트 매니페스테이션 어브 센시티브니스.

Original English: And their chief virtue lies in that they will never wear out.
English: and their chief virtue lies in that they will never wear out.
Hindi: एंड देर चीफ वर्चू लाइज़ इन दैट थे विल नेवर वेअर आउट.
Korean: 앤드 데어 치프 버츄 라이즈 인 댓 데이 윌 네버 웨어 아웃.

Original English: Beyond dispute, Corry Hutchinson had married Mabel Holmes.
English: beyond dispute, corry hutchinson had married mabel holmes.
Hindi: बियॉन्ड डिस्प्यूट, कॉरी हचिन्सन हैड मैरीड मेबल होल्म्स.
Korean: 비욘드 디스퓨트, 코리 허친슨 해드 매리드 메이블 홈즈.

Original English: No-sir-ee.
English: no-sir-ee.
Hindi: नो-सिर-ई.
Korean: 노서리.

Original English: Each insult added to the value of the claim.
English: each insult added to the value of the claim.
Hindi: इच इंसल्ट ऐडेड टू द वैल्यू अव द क्लेम.
Korean: 이치 인설트 애디드 투 더 밸류 어브 더 클레임.

Original English: For the rest, he was a mere automaton.
English: for the rest, he was a mere automaton.
Hindi: फॉर द रेस्ट, ही वज़ अ मीर ऑटोमेटन.
Korean: 포어 더 레스트, 히 워즈 아 미어 오토마톤.

Original English: The river bared its bosom, and snorting steamboats challenged the wilderness.
English: the river bared its bosom, and snorting steamboats challenged the wilderness.
Hindi: द रिवर बेर्ड इट्स बुसम, एंड स्नॉर्टिंग स्टीमबोट्स चैलेंज्ड द वाइल्डरनेस.
Korean: 더 리버 베어드 잇츠 부숨, 앤드 스노어링 스팀보츠 챌린지드 더 윌더니스.

Original English: Their love burned with increasing brightness.
English: their love burned with increasing brightness.
Hindi: धेर लव बर्न्ड विथ इन्क्रीसिंग ब्राइटनेस.
Korean: 데어 러브 번드 위드 인크리씽 브라이트니스.

Original English: They were artists, not biologists.
English: they were artists, not biologists.
Hindi: दे वेर आर्टिस्ट्स, नॉट बायोलॉजिस्ट्स.
Korean: 데이 워 아티스트, 낫 바이올러지스트.

Original English: Both Johnny and his mother shuffled their feet as they walked.
English: both johnny and his mother shuffled their feet as they walked.
Hindi: बोथ जॉनी ऐंड हिज़ मदर शफल्ड देर फीट ऐज़ दे वॉक्ट.
Korean: 보스 쟈니 앤드 히즈 머더 셔플드 데어 피트 애즈 데이 워크트.

Original English: And as in denial of guilt, the one-legged boy replied.
English: and as in denial of guilt, the one-legged boy replied.
Hindi: ऐंड ऐज इन डिनाइल अव गिल्ट, द वन-लेग्ड बॉय रिप्लाइड.
Korean: 앤드 애즈 인 디나이얼 어브 길트, 더 원레그드 보이 리플라이드.

Original English: Burnt out like the crater of a volcano.
English: burnt out like the crater of a volcano.
Hindi: बर्न्ट आउट लाइक द क्रेटर अव अ वोल्कैनो.
Korean: 번트 아웃 라이크 더 크레이터 오브 아 볼케이노.

Original English: The boy, O'Brien, was specially maltreated.
English: the boy, o'brien, was specially maltreated.
Hindi: द बॉय, ओब्रायन, वज़ स्पेशली मालट्रीटिड.
Korean: 더 보이, 오브라이언, 워즈 스페셜리 멀트리티드.

Original English: O'Brien took off his coat and bared his right arm.
English: o'brien took off his coat and bared his right arm.
Hindi: ओब्रायन टुक ऑफ हिस कोट ऐंड बेर्ड हिस राइट आर्म.
Korean: 오브라이언 툭 오프 히즈 코트 앤드 배어드 히즈 라이트 암.

Original English: He bore no grudges and had few enemies.
English: he bore no grudges and had few enemies.
Hindi: ही बोर नो ग्रजेस एंड हैड फ्यू एनिमीज़.
Korean: 히 보 노 그러지스 앤드 해드 퓨 에너미즈.

Original English: And Tom King patiently endured.
English: and tom king patiently endured.
Hindi: एंड टॉम किंग पेशेंटली एंड्युओर्ड्.
Korean: 앤드 탐 킹 페이션틀리 엔듀어드.

Original English: King took every advantage he knew.
English: king took every advantage he knew.
Hindi: किंग टुक एव्री एडवांटेज ही न्यू.
Korean: 킹 툭 에브리 어드밴티지 히 뉴.

Original English: The lines were now very taut.
English: the lines were now very taut.
Hindi: द लाइन्स वर नाउ वेरी टॉट.
Korean: 더 라인즈 워 나우 베리 타우트.

Original English: And right there I saw and knew it all.
English: and right there i saw and knew it all.
Hindi: एंड राइट देर आई सॉ एंड न्यू इट ऑल.
Korean: 앤드 라이트 데어 아이 소 앤드 뉴 잇 올.

Original English: Who the devil gave it to you to be judge and jury.
English: who the devil gave it to you to be judge and jury.
Hindi: हू द डेविल गेव इट टू यू टू बी जज ऐंड जूरी.
Korean: 후 더 데빌 게이브 잇 투 유 투 비 저지 앤드 주리.

Original English: You're joking me, sir, the other managed to articulate.
English: you are joking me, sir, the other managed to articulate.
Hindi: यू आर जोकिंग मी, सर, दि अदर मैनेज्ड टू आर्टिक्युलेट.
Korean: 유 아 조킹 미, 서, 디 어더 매니지드 투 아티큘레이트.

Original English: Anything unusual or abnormal was sufficient to send a fellow to Molokai.
English: anything unusual or abnormal was sufficient to send a fellow to molokai.
Hindi: एनीथिंग अनुज़ूअल ऑर अब्नॉर्मल वज़ सफ़िशन्ट टू सेंड अ फेलो टू मालकाइ.
Korean: 에니띵 언유주얼 오어 어브노멀 워즈 서피션트 투 센드 아 펠로우 투 몰로카이.

Original English: His beady black eyes saw bargains where other men saw bankruptcy.
English: his beady black eyes saw bargains where other men saw bankruptcy.
Hindi: हिस बीडी ब्लैक आइज़ सॉ बार्गिन्स वेयर अदर मेन सॉ बैंक्रप्सी.
Korean: 히즈 비디 블랙 아이즈 소 바겐즈 웨어 어더 멘 소 뱅크럽시.

Original English: He was an athlete and a giant.
English: he was an athlete and a giant.
Hindi: ही वज़ अन ऐथलीट ऐंड अ जायंट.
Korean: 히 워즈 안 애슬리트 앤드 아 자이언트.

Original English: We fished sharks on Niihau together.
English: we fished sharks on niihau together.
Hindi: वी फिश्ट शार्क्स ऑन निहाउ टुगेदर.
Korean: 위 피쉬트 샤크스 온 니이하우 투게더.

Original English: The Claudine was leaving next morning for Honolulu.
English: the claudine was leaving next morning for honolulu.
Hindi: द क्लॉडीन वस लीविंग नेक्स्ट मॉर्निंग फॉर होनोलूलू.
Korean: 더 클로딘 워즈 리빙 넥스트 모닝 포어 호놀룰루.

Original English: In short, my joyous individualism was dominated by the orthodox bourgeois ethics.
English: in short, my joyous individualism was dominated by the orthodox bourgeois ethics.
Hindi: इन शॉर्ट, माई जॉयस इंडिविज़म वज़ डॉमिनेटेड बाई दि ऑर्थोडॉक्स बुर्जुआ एथिक्स.
Korean: 인 숏, 마이 조이어스 인디비쥬얼리즘 워즈 도미네이티드 바이 디 오소독스 부르주아 에틱스.

Original English: Soon shall it be thrust back from off prostrate humanity.
English: soon shall it be thrust back from off prostrate humanity.
Hindi: सून शैल इट बी थ्रस्ट बैक फ्रम ऑफ प्रॉस्ट्रेट ह्यूमैनिटी.
Korean: 순 샬 잇 비 쓰러스트 백 프롬 오프 프로스트레이트 휴매니티.

Original English: Yet, in accordance with Ernest's test of truth, it worked.
English: yet, in accordance with ernest's test of truth, it worked.
Hindi: येट, इन अकॉर्डेंस विथ अर्नेस्ट्स टेस्ट अव ट्रूथ, इट वर्क्ड.
Korean: 예트, 인 어코던스 위드 어니스트스 테스트 어브 트루스, 잇 워크트.

Original English: Much more Ernest told them of themselves and of his disillusionment.
English: much more ernest told them of themselves and of his disillusionment.
Hindi: मच मोर अर्नेस्ट टोल्ड देम अव धेम्सेल्व्स ऐंड अव हिज डिसिलुजनमेंट.
Korean: 머치 모어 어니스트 톨드 뎀 어브 뎀셀브즈 앤드 어브 히즈 디스일루전먼트.

Original English: There is more behind this than a mere university ideal.
English: there is more behind this than a mere university ideal.
Hindi: देयर इज़ मोर बिहाइंड दिस धन अ मेर यूनिवर्सिटी आइडियल.
Korean: 데어 이즈 모어 비하인드 디스 댄 아 미어 유니버시티 아이디얼.

Original English: No, it is a palace, wherein there are many servants.
English: no, it is a palace, wherein there are many servants.
Hindi: नो, इट इज अ पैलेस, वेरिन देर आर मेनी सर्वेंट्स.
Korean: 노, 잇 이즈 아 펠리스, 웨어린 데어 아 매니 서번츠.

Original English: We must give ourselves and not our money alone.
English: we must give ourselves and not our money alone.
Hindi: वी मस्ट गिव आउर्सेल्व्ज़ ऐंड नॉट आउर मनी अलोन.
Korean: 위 머스트 기브 아워셀브즈 앤드 낫 아워 머니 얼론.

Original English: We are consumed in our own flesh-pots.
English: we are consumed in our own flesh-pots.
Hindi: वी आर कंस्यूम्ड इन आउर ओन फ्लेश्पॉट्स.
Korean: 위 아 컨슘드 인 아우어 온 플레쉬포츠.

Original English: But here amongst ourselves let us speak out.
English: but here amongst ourselves let us speak out.
Hindi: बट हीर अमंगस्ट आउर्सेल्व्ज़ लेट अस स्पीक आउट.
Korean: 벗 히어 어몽스트 아우셀브즈 렛 어스 스피크 아웃.

Original English: Also, there was awe in their faces.
English: also, there was awe in their faces.
Hindi: आल्सो, देर वस ऑ इन देर फेसिज़.
Korean: 알소, 데어 워즈 오 인 데어 페이시즈.

Original English: Out of abstractions Ernest had conjured a vision and made them see it.
English: out of abstractions ernest had conjured a vision and made them see it.
Hindi: आउट अव एब्स्ट्रैक्शंस अर्नेस्ट हैड कंजर्ड अ विजन एंड मेड देम सी इट.
Korean: 아웃 어브 앱스트랙션즈 어니스트 해드 컨저드 아 비전 앤드 메이드 뎀 씨 잇.

Original English: Illuminating oil was becoming all profit.
English: illuminating oil was becoming all profit.
Hindi: इलूमिनेटिंग ऑइल वस बिकमिंग ऑल प्रॉफिट.
Korean: 일루미네이팅 오일 워즈 비커밍 올 프로핏.

Original English: Such an act was in direct violation of the laws of the land.
English: such an act was in direct violation of the laws of the land.
Hindi: सच अन ऐक्ट वज़ इन डाइरेक्ट वायलेशन अव द लॉज अव द लैंड.
Korean: 서치 안 액트 워즈 인 디렉트 바이올레이션 오브 더 로즈 오브 더 랜드.

Original English: He was fond of quoting a fragment from a certain poem.
English: he was fond of quoting a fragment from a certain poem.
Hindi: ही वज़ फॉन्ड ऑव क्वोटिंग अ फ्रैगमेंट फ्रॉम अ सर्टन पोएम.
Korean: 히 워즈 폰드 어브 쿼팅 아 프래그먼트 프럼 아 서튼 포엠.

Original English: Without them he could not run his empire.
English: without them he could not run his empire.
Hindi: विदआउट थेम ही कुड नाट रन हिस एम्पायर.
Korean: 위다우트 뎀 히 쿠드 낫 런 히즈 엠파이어.

Original English: For such countries nothing remained but reorganization.
English: for such countries nothing remained but reorganization.
Hindi: फॉर सच कंट्रीज नथिंग रिमेन्ड बट रीऑर्गनाइज़ेशन.
Korean: 포어 서치 컨트리즈 너씽 리메인드 벗 리오거나이제이션.

Original English: They could not continue their method of producing surpluses.
English: they could not continue their method of producing surpluses.
Hindi: थे कुद नाट कंटिन्यू देर मेथड अव प्रोड्यूसिंग सर्प्लसेज़.
Korean: 데이 쿨드 낫 컨티뉴 데어 메소드 어브 프로듀싱 서플러스.

Original English: At once would be instituted a dozen cooperative commonwealth states.
English: at once would be instituted a dozen cooperative commonwealth states.
Hindi: एट वन्स वुड बी इंस्टिट्यूटिड अ डजन कोऑपरेटिव कामनवेल्थ स्टेट्स.
Korean: 앳 원스 우드 비 인스티튜티드 아 더즌 코오퍼러티브 커먼웰스 스테이츠.

Original English: The Oligarchy wanted violence, and it set its agents provocateurs to work.
English: the oligarchy wanted violence, and it set its agents provocateurs to work.
Hindi: दि ऑलिगार्की वॉन्टेड वायलेन्स, एंड इट सेट इट्स एजेंट्स प्रोवोकटर्स टू वर्क.
Korean: 디 알리거키 원티드 바이얼런스, 앤드 잇 셋 잇츠 에이전츠 프로보카터즈 투 워크.

Original English: Nowhere did the raw earth appear.
English: nowhere did the raw earth appear.
Hindi: नोवेर डिड द रॉ अर्थ अपीर.
Korean: 노웨어 디드 더 로 어스 어피어.

Original English: The lush vegetation of that sheltered spot make a natural shield.
English: the lush vegetation of that sheltered spot make a natural shield.
Hindi: द लश वेजिटेशन अव दैट शेल्टर्ड स्पॉट मेक अ नैचरल शील्ड.
Korean: 더 러쉬 베지테이션 어브 댓 쉘터드 스팟 메이크 아 내츄럴 쉴드.

Original English: Men who endure it, call it living death.
English: men who endure it, call it living death.
Hindi: मेन हू एंड्यूर इट, कॉल इट लिविंग डेथ.
Korean: 멘 후 엔두르 잇, 콜 잇 리빙 데스.

Original English: As I say, he had tapped the message very rapidly.
English: as i say, he had tapped the message very rapidly.
Hindi: ऐज़ आई से, ही हैड टैप्ट द मैसेज वेरी रैपिडली.
Korean: 애즈 아이 세이, 히 해드 탭트 더 메시지 베리 래피들리.

Original English: Ask him, I laughed, then turned to Pasquini.
English: ask him, i laughed, then turned to pasquini.
Hindi: आस्क हिम, आई लाफ्ड, धेन टर्न्ड टू पैस्क्वीनी.
Korean: 애스크 힘, 아이 래프드, 덴 턴드 투 파스크위니.

Original English: In what bucolic school of fence he had been taught was beyond imagining.
English: in what bucolic school of fence he had been taught was beyond imagining.
Hindi: इन वट ब्यूकालिक स्कूल अव फेंस ही हैड बीन टॉट वॉज बियॉन्ड इमेजिनिंग.
Korean: 인 왓 뷰콜릭 스쿨 어브 펜스 히 해드 빈 톳 워즈 비욘드 이미지닝.

Original English: May drought destroy your crops.
English: may drought destroy your crops.
Hindi: मे ड्राउट डिस्ट्रॉय योर क्रॉप्स.
Korean: 메이 드라우트 디스트로이 유어 크롭스.

Original English: Dunham, can your boy go along with Jesse.
English: dunham, can your boy go along with jesse.
Hindi: डनम, कैन यूर बॉय गो अलॉंग विथ जेसी.
Korean: 던햄, 캔 유어 보이 고 얼롱 위드 제시.

Original English: But Johannes could, and did.
English: but johannes could, and did.
Hindi: बट जोहान्स कुड, ऐंड डिड.
Korean: 벗 조한스 쿧, 앤드 딛.

Original English: A new preacher and a new doctrine come to Jerusalem.
English: a new preacher and a new doctrine come to jerusalem.
Hindi: अ न्यू प्रीचर एंड अ न्यू डॉक्ट्रिन कम टू जेरूसलम.
Korean: 아 뉴 프리처 앤드 아 뉴 닥트린 컴 투 제루살렘.

Original English: He would destroy all things that are fixed.
English: he would destroy all things that are fixed.
Hindi: ही वूड डिस्ट्रॉय ऑल थिंग्स दैट आर फिक्स्ड.
Korean: 히 우드 디스트로이 올 띵스 댓 아 픽스트.

Original English: He was an enthusiast and a desert dweller.
English: he was an enthusiast and a desert dweller.
Hindi: ही वज़ अन एन्थुज़ीऐस्ट ऐन्ड अ डेज़र्ट ड्वेलर.
Korean: 히 워즈 안 엔뚜지애스트 앤드 아 데저트 드웰러.

Original English: What Pascal glimpsed with the vision of a seer, I have lived.
English: what pascal glimpsed with the vision of a seer, i have lived.
Hindi: वट पैस्कल ग्लिम्प्स्ड विथ द विजन अव अ सीर, आई हैव लिव्ड.
Korean: 왓 파스칼 글림스드 위드 더 비전 어브 아 시어, 아이 해브 리브드.

Original English: I should like to engage just for one whole life in that.
English: i should like to engage just for one whole life in that.
Hindi: आई शुद लाइक टू एंगेज जस्ट फॉर वन होल लाइफ इन दैट.
Korean: 아이 슈드 라이크 투 엔게이지 저스트 포어 원 홀 라이프 인 댓.

Original English: Yea, so are all the lesser animals of today clean.
English: yea, so are all the lesser animals of today clean.
Hindi: ये, सो आर ऑल द लेसर एनिमल्स अव टुडे क्लीन.
Korean: 예이, 소 아르 올 더 레서 애니멀즈 어브 투데이 클린.

Original English: The Warden with a quart of champagne.
English: the warden with a quart of champagne.
Hindi: द वॉर्डन विथ अ क्वार्ट अव शैम्पेन.
Korean: 더 워든 위드 아 쿼트 오브 샴페인.

Original English: Without a doubt, some of them have dinner engagements.
English: without a doubt, some of them have dinner engagements.
Hindi: विदआउट अ डाउट, सम अव देम हैव डिनर एंगेजमेंट्स.
Korean: 위드아웃 아 다우트, 썸 업 뎀 해브 디너 엔게이지먼츠.

Original English: I had been born with no organic, chemical predisposition toward alcohol.
English: i had been born with no organic, chemical predisposition toward alcohol.
Hindi: आई हैड बिन बॉर्न विथ नो ऑर्गैनिक, केमिकल प्रेडिस्पोज़िशन टुवॉर्ड अल्कोहल.
Korean: 아이 해드 빈 본 위드 노 오가닉, 케미컬 프리디스포지션 투워드 알코올.

Original English: He may anticipate the day of his death.
English: he may anticipate the day of his death.
Hindi: ही मे एंटिसिपेट द डे अव हिज़ डेथ.
Korean: 히 메이 앤티시페이트 더 데이 어브 히즈 데스.

Original English: The Italian rancho was a bachelor establishment.
English: the italian rancho was a bachelor establishment.
Hindi: दि इटैलियन रैंचो वस अ बैचलर एस्टैब्लिश्मेंट.
Korean: 디 이탈리안 랜초 워즈 아 배철러 이스타블리시먼트.

Original English: I lost my balance and pitched head foremost into the ooze.
English: i lost my balance and pitched head foremost into the ooze.
Hindi: आई लॉस्ट माई बैलेंस एंड पिच्ड हेड फॉरमोस्ट इंटू दि ऊज़.
Korean: 아이 로스트 마이 밸런스 앤드 피치드 헤드 포어모스트 인투 디 우즈.

Original English: Men like Joe Goose dated existence from drunk to drunk.
English: men like joe goose dated existence from drunk to drunk.
Hindi: मेन लाइक जो गूस डेटेड एग्जिस्टेंस फ्रॉम ड्रंक टू ड्रंक.
Korean: 맨 라이크 조 구스 데이티드 엑지스턴스 프럼 드렁크 투 드렁크.

Original English: Also, churches and preachers I had never known.
English: also, churches and preachers i had never known.
Hindi: ऑल्सो, चर्चिज़ ऐंड प्रीचर्स आई हैड नेवर नोन.
Korean: 알소, 처치스 앤드 프리처즈 아이 해드 네버 노운.

Original English: Do you know that we weigh every pound of coal we burn.
English: do you know that we weigh every pound of coal we burn.
Hindi: डू यू नो दॅट वी वे एवरी पाउंड अव कोल वी बर्न.
Korean: 두 유 노 댓 위 웨이 에브리 파운드 어브 콜 위 번.

Original English: This also became part of the daily schedule.
English: this also became part of the daily schedule.
Hindi: दिस आल्सो बिकेम पार्ट अव द डेली स्केड्यूल.
Korean: 디스 알소 비케임 파트 어브 더 데일리 스케줄.

Original English: All an appearance can know is mirage.
English: all an appearance can know is mirage.
Hindi: ऑल अन अपीअरन्स कैन नो इज़ मिराज.
Korean: 올 안 어피어런스 캔 노 이즈 미라지.

Original English: Yet he dreams he is immortal, I argue feebly.
English: yet he dreams he is immortal, i argue feebly.
Hindi: येट ही ड्रीम्ज़ ही इज़ इमॉर्टल, आई आर्ग्यू फीब्ली.
Korean: 옛 히 드림즈 히 이즈 이모털, 아이 아규 피블리.

Original English: I am writing these lines in Honolulu, Hawaii.
English: i am writing these lines in honolulu, hawaii.
Hindi: आई ऐम राइटिंग दीज लाइन्स इन होनोलूलू, हवाई.
Korean: 아이 앰 라이팅 디즈 라인즈 인 호놀룰루, 하와이.

Original English: Jack London, Waikiki Beach, Honolulu, Oahu.
English: jack london, waikiki beach, honolulu, oahu.
Hindi: जैक लंदन, वैकिकी बीच, होनोलूलू, ओआहू.
Korean: 잭 런던, 와이키키 비치, 호놀룰루, 오아후.

Original English: Jerry was so secure in his nook that he did not roll away.
English: jerry was so secure in his nook that he did not roll away.
Hindi: जेरी वज़ सो सिक्योर इन हिस नुक दैट ही डिड नॉट रोल अवे.
Korean: 제리 워즈 소 시큐어 인 히즈 눅 댓 히 디드 낫 롤 어웨이.

Original English: Why, he's bought forty pounds of goods from you already.
English: why, he's bought forty pounds of goods from you already.
Hindi: वाई, हीज़ बॉट फॉर्टी पाउंड्स अव गुड्स फ्रॉम यू ऑलरेडी.
Korean: 와이, 히즈 보트 포티 파운즈 오브 굿즈 프럼 유 올레디.

Original English: The last refugee had passed.
English: the last refugee had passed.
Hindi: द लास्ट रेफ्यूजी हैड पास्ट.
Korean: 더 라스트 레퓨지 해드 패스트.

Original English: And the foundation stone of service, in his case, was obedience.
English: and the foundation stone of service, in his case, was obedience.
Hindi: ऐंड द फाउंडेशन स्टोन अव सर्विस, इन हिज़ केस, वॉज़ ओबीडिएंस.
Korean: 앤드 더 파운데이션 스톤 오브 서비스, 인 히즈 케이스, 워즈 오비디언스.

Original English: Peace be unto you and grace before the Lord.
English: peace be unto you and grace before the lord.
Hindi: पीस बी अंतु यू एंड ग्रेस बिफोर द लॉर्ड.
Korean: 피스 비 언투 유 앤드 그레이스 비포어 더 로드.

Original English: His mouth opened; words shaped vainly on his lips.
English: his mouth opened words shaped vainly on his lips.
Hindi: हिज़ माउथ ओपेंड वर्ड्स शेप्ड वेनली ऑन हिज़ लिप्स.
Korean: 히스 마우스 오픈드 워즈 쉐이프트 베인리 온 히스 립스.

Original English: Bill lingered, contemplating his work with artistic appreciation.
English: bill lingered, contemplating his work with artistic appreciation.
Hindi: बिल लिंगर्ड, कांटेम्प्लेटिंग हिज़ वर्क विथ आर्टिस्टिक अप्रीशियेशन.
Korean: 빌 링거드, 컨템플레이팅 히즈 워크 위드 아티스틱 어프리시에이션.

Original English: What the flaming.
English: what the flaming.
Hindi: व्हट द फ्लेमिंग.
Korean: 왓 더 플레밍.

Original English: Mrs McFee's jaws brought together with a snap.
English: missus mcfee's jaws brought together with a snap.
Hindi: मिसस मैकफ़ीज़ जॉज़ ब्रॉट टुगेदर विथ अ स्नैप.
Korean: 미서스 맥피즈 죠즈 브로트 투게더 위드 아 스냅.

Original English: Then it is as I said, Womble announced with finality.
English: then it is as i said, womble announced with finality.
Hindi: देन इट इस ऐज़ आई सेड, वॉम्बल अनाउन्स्ड विद फाइनलिटी.
Korean: 덴 잇 이즈 애즈 아이 세드, 웜블 어나운스트 위드 파이낼리티.

Original English: With them were Indians, also three other men.
English: with them were indians, also three other men.
Hindi: विथ देम वर इंडियंस, आल्सो थ्री अदर मेन.
Korean: 위드 뎀 워 인디언스, 알소 쓰리 어더 멘.

Original English: Dennin's hands were released long enough for him to sign the document.
English: dennin's hands were released long enough for him to sign the document.
Hindi: डेनिन्स हैंड्स वर रिलीस्ड लॉन्ग इनफ फॉर हिम टू साइन द डॉक्यूमेंट.
Korean: 덴닌즈 핸즈 워 릴리스드 롱 이너프 포어 힘 투 사인 더 다큐먼트.

Original English: Now Irvine was a man of impulse, a poet.
English: now irvine was a man of impulse, a poet.
Hindi: नाउ अर्वाइन वज अ मैन अव इम्पल्स, अ पोएट.
Korean: 나우 어바인 워즈 아 맨 어브 임펄스, 아 포잇.

Original English: He was just bursting with joy, joy over what.
English: he was just bursting with joy, joy over what.
Hindi: ही वज़ जस्ट बर्स्टिंग विथ जॉय, जॉय ओवर वट.
Korean: 히 워즈 저스트 버스팅 위드 조이, 조이 오버 왓.

Original English: At Lake Linderman I had one canoe, very good Peterborough canoe.
English: at lake linderman i had one canoe, very good peterborough canoe.
Hindi: ऐट लेक लिन्डर्मन आई हैड वन कनू, वेरी गुड पीटरबरो कनू.
Korean: 앳 레이크 린더먼 아이 해드 원 카누, 베리 굿 피터버러 카누.

Original English: Behind him lay the thousand-years-long road across all Siberia and Russia.
English: behind him lay the thousand-years-long road across all siberia and russia.
Hindi: बिहाइंड हिम ले द थाउज़ंड-ईयरज़-लॉन्ग रोड अक्रॉस आल साइबेरिया एंड रशिया.
Korean: 비하인드 힘 레이 더 싸우쟌지이얼즈롱 로드 어크로스 올 사이베리아 앤드 러시아.

Original English: He had forgotten to build a fire and thaw out.
English: he had forgotten to build a fire and thaw out.
Hindi: ही हैड फरगाटन टू बिल्ड अ फायर ऐंड थॉ आउट.
Korean: 히 핻 포거튼 투 빌드 아 파이어 앤드 쏘 아웃.

Original English: I never saw anything like her in my life.
English: i never saw anything like her in my life.
Hindi: आई नेवर सॉ एनीथिंग लाइक हर इन माई लाइफ.
Korean: 아이 네버 소 에니씽 라이크 허 인 마이 라이프.

Original English: There was no law on the Yukon save what they made for themselves.
English: there was no law on the yukon save what they made for themselves.
Hindi: धेर वज़ नो लॉ ऑन द यूकन सेव वट थे मेड फॉर देम्सेल्व्ज.
Korean: 데어 워즈 노 로 온 더 유콘 세이브 왓 데이 메이드 포어 뎀셀브즈.

Original English: Good business man, Curly, O'Brien was saying.
English: good business man, curly, o'brien was saying.
Hindi: गुड बिज़नेस मैन, कर्ली, ओ'ब्रायन वस सेइंग.
Korean: 굿 비즈니스 맨, 컬리, 오브라이언 워즈 세잉.

Original English: There weren't any missions, and he was the man to know.
English: there were not any missions, and he was the man to know.
Hindi: दैर वर नाट एनी मिशन्स, ऐंड ही वज़ द मैन टू नो.
Korean: 데어 워 낫 애니 미션즈, 앤드 히 워즈 더 맨 투 노우.

Original English: And the big Persian knew of his existence before he did of hers.
English: and the big persian knew of his existence before he did of hers.
Hindi: ऐंड द बिग पर्शियन न्यू अव हिज़ एक्ज़िस्टेंस बिफोर ही डिड अव हर्स.
Korean: 앤드 더 빅 퍼션 뉴 어브 히즈 이그지스턴스 비포어 히 디드 어브 허즈.

Original English: Once the jews harp began emitting its barbaric rhythms, Michael was helpless.
English: once the jews harp began emitting its barbaric rhythms, michael was helpless.
Hindi: वन्स द जूज़ हार्प बिगैन इमिटिंग इट्स बारबरिक रिदम्स, माइकल वज़ हेल्पलेस.
Korean: 원스 더 쥬스 하프 비갠 이밋팅 잇츠 바바릭 리듬즈, 마이클 워즈 헬플리스.

Original English: But we'll just postpone this.
English: but we will just postpone this.
Hindi: बट वी विल जस्ट पोस्टपोन दिस.
Korean: 벗 위 윌 저스트 포스트폰 디스.

Original English: There was the Emma Louisa.
English: there was the emma louisa.
Hindi: देर वज़ दि एमा लुइसा.
Korean: 데어 워즈 디 엠마 루이사.

Original English: This is my fifth voyage.
English: this is my fifth voyage.
Hindi: दिस इस माय फिफ्थ वॉयज.
Korean: 디스 이즈 마이 피프스 보이지.

Original English: It was this proposition that started the big idea in Daughtry's mind.
English: it was this proposition that started the big idea in daughtry's mind.
Hindi: इट वज़ दिस प्रपोजिशन दैट स्टार्टेड द बिग आइडिया इन डॉटरिज माइंड.
Korean: 잇 워즈 디스 프로포지션 댓 스타티드 더 빅 아이디어 인 도트리즈 마인드.

Original English: Daughtry elaborated on the counting trick by bringing Cocky along.
English: daughtry elaborated on the counting trick by bringing cocky along.
Hindi: डॉट्री इलैबरेटेड ऑन द काउंटिंग ट्रिक बाई ब्रिंगिंग कॉकी अलांग.
Korean: 도트리 일래보레티드 온 더 카운팅 트릭 바이 브링잉 코키 얼롱.

Original English: Enjoy it he did, but principally for Steward's sake.
English: enjoy it he did, but principally for steward's sake.
Hindi: एन्जॉय इट ही डिड, बट प्रिंसिपली फॉर स्ट्यूअर्ड्स सेक.
Korean: 엔조이 잇 히 디드, 벗 프린시펄리 포 스튜어즈 세이크.

Original English: I have long noted your thirst unquenchable.
English: i have long noted your thirst unquenchable.
Hindi: आई हैव लॉन्ग नोटेड योर थर्स्ट अनक्वेंचबल.
Korean: 아이 해브 롱 노티드 유어 서스트 언퀜처블.

Original English: Wonder if he's a lion dog, Charles suggested.
English: wonder if he's a lion dog, charles suggested.
Hindi: वंडर इफ हीज़ अ लायन डॉग, चार्ल्स सजेस्टेड.
Korean: 원더 이프 히즈 아 라이언 도그, 찰스 서제스티드.

Original English: We don't see ourselves as foolish.
English: we do not see ourselves as foolish.
Hindi: वी डू नाट सी आइउर्सेल्व्ज़ ऐज़ फूलिश.
Korean: 위 두 낫 시 아이얼브즈 애즈 풀리쉬.

Original English: He had comparatively no advantages at first.
English: he had comparatively no advantages at first.
Hindi: ही हैड कम्परेटिवली नो एडवांटेजेस ऐट फर्स्ट.
Korean: 히 핻 컴패러티블리 노 어드밴티지스 앳 퍼스트.

Original English: He had proved it today, with his amateurish and sophomoric productions.
English: he had proved it today, with his amateurish and sophomoric productions.
Hindi: ही हैड प्रूव्ड इट टुडे, विथ हिस अमेट्यूरिश एंड सोफोमोरिक प्रोडक्शन्स.
Korean: 히 핫 프루브드 잇 투데이, 위드 히즈 에머츄리쉬 앤드 소포모릭 프러덕션즈.

Original English: I was sick once, typhoid.
English: i was sick once, typhoid.
Hindi: आई वस सिक वन्स, टाइफॉइड.
Korean: 아이 워즈 식 원스, 타이포이드.

Original English: In a way he is my protege.
English: in a way he is my protege.
Hindi: इन अ वे ही इज़ माई प्रोटेज.
Korean: 인 아 웨이 히 이즈 마이 프로테제.

Original English: We are both children together.
English: we are both children together.
Hindi: वी आर बोथ चिल्ड्रेन टुगेदर.
Korean: 위 아르 보스 칠드런 투게더.

Original English: It's only his indigestion I find fault with.
English: it's only his indigestion i find fault with.
Hindi: इट्स ओनली हिस इन्डिजेशन आई फाइंड फॉल्ट विथ.
Korean: 이츠 온리 히즈 인디제스천 아이 파인드 폴트 위드.

Original English: She'd make a good wife for the cashier.
English: she would make a good wife for the cashier.
Hindi: शी वुड मेक अ गुड वाइफ फॉर द कैशियर.
Korean: 시 우드 메이크 아 굿 와이프 포 더 캐셔.

Original English: Gad, do I remember it.
English: gad, do i remember it.
Hindi: गैड, डू आई रिमेम्बर इट.
Korean: 가드, 두 아이 리멤버 잇.

Original English: You got out by fighting, and I through a pretty girl.
English: you got out by fighting, and i through a pretty girl.
Hindi: यू गॉट आउट बाई फाइटिंग, एंड आई थ्रू अ प्रिटी गर्ल.
Korean: 유 갓 아웃 바이 파이팅, 앤드 아이 쓰루 아 프리티 걸.

Original English: I can see that knife now.
English: i can see that knife now.
Hindi: आई कैन सी दैट नाइफ नाउ.
Korean: 아이 캔 씨 댓 나이프 나우.

Original English: When I can't see beauty in woman I want to die.
English: when i can not see beauty in woman i want to die.
Hindi: वेन आई कैन नॉट सी ब्यूटी इन वुमन आई वांट टू डाई.
Korean: 웬 아이 캔 낫 씨 뷰티 인 우먼 아이 원트 투 다이.

Original English: His slim fingers closed like steel about Philip's.
English: his slim fingers closed like steel about philip's.
Hindi: हिस स्लिम फिंगर्स क्लोज़्ड लाइक स्टील अबाउट फिलिप्स.
Korean: 히즈 슬림 핑거즈 클로즈드 라이크 스틸 어바웃 필립스.

Original English: He seized Gregson by the arm and led him to the door.
English: he seized gregson by the arm and led him to the door.
Hindi: ही सीज़्ड ग्रेगसन बाई दि आर्म एंड लेड हिम टू द डोर.
Korean: 히 시즈드 그렉슨 바이 디 암 앤드 레드 힘 투 더 도어.

Original English: Hear the Indian dogs wailing down at Churchill.
English: hear the indian dogs wailing down at churchill.
Hindi: हियर दि इंडियन डॉग्स वेलिंग डाउन ऐट चर्चिल.
Korean: 히어 디 인디언 독스 웨일링 다운 앳 처칠.

Original English: Burke himself had criticized it because of the smile.
English: burke himself had criticized it because of the smile.
Hindi: बर्क हिम्सेल्फ हैड क्रिटिसाइज्ड इट बिकॉज अव द स्माइल.
Korean: 버크 힘셀프 핻 크리티사이즈드 잇 비커즈 어브 더 스마일.

Original English: I'd say there was going to be a glorious scrap.
English: i would say there was going to be a glorious scrap.
Hindi: आई वुड से देर वस गोइंग टू बी अ ग्लोरियस स्क्रैप.
Korean: 아이 우드 세이 데어 워즈 고잉 투 비 아 글로리어스 스크랩.

Original English: He turned the map to Gregson, pointing with his finger.
English: he turned the map to gregson, pointing with his finger.
Hindi: ही टर्न्ड द मैप टू ग्रेगसन, पॉइन्टिंग विद हिज़ फिंगर.
Korean: 히 턴드 더 맵 투 그레그슨, 포인팅 위드 히즈 핑거.

Original English: His eyes never took themselves for an instant from his companion's face.
English: his eyes never took themselves for an instant from his companion's face.
Hindi: हिज़ आइज़ नेवर टुक देमेंसैल्व्स फॉर अन इंस्टंट फ्रॉम हिज़ कम्पैनियन्स फेस.
Korean: 히즈 아이즈 네버 툭 뎀셀브즈 포어 안 인스턴트 프럼 히즈 컴패니언즈 페이스.

Original English: Something that Whittemore had not yet said thrilled him.
English: something that whittemore had not yet said thrilled him.
Hindi: समथिंग दॅट विटमोर हैड नाट येट सेड थ्रिल्ड हिम.
Korean: 썸띵 댓 위리모어 해드 낫 옛 세드 쓰릴드 힘.

Original English: Lakes and rivers, hundreds of them, thousands of them.
English: lakes and rivers, hundreds of them, thousands of them.
Hindi: लेक्स ऐंड रिवर्स, हंड्रेड्स अव देम, थाउज़ंड्स अव देम.
Korean: 레이크스 앤드 리버즈, 헌드레즈 어브 뎀, 싸우전즈 어브 뎀.

Original English: Whitefish, Gregson, whitefish and trout.
English: whitefish, gregson, whitefish and trout.
Hindi: व्हाइटफिश, ग्रेगसन, व्हाइटफिश एंड ट्राउट.
Korean: 와이트피쉬, 그렉슨, 와이트피쉬 앤드 트라우트.

Original English: They robbed me a few years later.
English: they robbed me a few years later.
Hindi: दे रॉब्ड मी अ फ्यू इयर्स लेटर.
Korean: 데이 랍드 미 아 퓨 이어즈 레이터.

Original English: He chuckled as he pulled out his pipe and began filling it.
English: he chuckled as he pulled out his pipe and began filling it.
Hindi: ही चक्ल्ड ऐज़ ही पुल्ड आउट हिज़ पाइप एंड बिगैन फिलिंग इट.
Korean: 히 척클드 애즈 히 풀드 아웃 히즈 파이프 앤드 비갠 필링 잇.

Original English: Everything was working smoothly, better than I had expected.
English: everything was working smoothly, better than i had expected.
Hindi: एवरिथिंग वस वर्किंग स्मूथली, बेटर धन आई हैड एक्स्पेक्टेड.
Korean: 에브리띵 워즈 워킹 스무드리, 베터 댄 아이 해드 엑스펙티드.

Original English: I was completely lost in my work.
English: i was completely lost in my work.
Hindi: आई वाज़ कम्प्लीटली लॉस्ट इन माई वर्क.
Korean: 아이 워즈 컴플리틀리 로스트 인 마이 워크.

Original English: His slim hands gripped the edges of the table.
English: his slim hands gripped the edges of the table.
Hindi: हिज़ स्लिम हैंड्स ग्रिप्ट दि एड्ज़ अव द टेबल.
Korean: 히즈 슬림 핸즈 그립트 디 에지즈 어브 더 테이블.

Original English: He made no reply as he waited for Whittemore to continue.
English: he made no reply as he waited for whittemore to continue.
Hindi: ही मेड नो रिप्लाइ ऐज़ ही वेटिड फॉर विटिमोर टू कंटिन्यू.
Korean: 히 메이드 노 리플라이 애즈 히 웨이티드 포어 위터모어 투 컨티뉴.

Original English: Philip dropped back into his chair.
English: philip dropped back into his chair.
Hindi: फिलिप ड्रॉप्ट बैक इंटू हिज़ चेयर.
Korean: 필립 드랍트 백 인투 히즈 체어.

Original English: If I was out of the game it would be easily made.
English: if i was out of the game it would be easily made.
Hindi: इफ आई वज़ आउट अव द गेम इट वुड बी ईज़िली मेड.
Korean: 이프 아이 워즈 아웃 어브 더 게임 잇 우드 비 이지리 메이드.

Original English: MacDougall, my engineer, believes it.
English: macdougall, my engineer, believes it.
Hindi: मैकडूगल, माई इंजीनियर, बिलीव्स इट.
Korean: 맥도걸, 마이 엔지니어, 빌리브즈 잇.

Original English: It is growing, every day, every hour.
English: it is growing, every day, every hour.
Hindi: इट इज़ ग्रोइंग, एव्री डे, एव्री आवर.
Korean: 잇 이즈 그로잉, 에브리 데이, 에브리 아워.

Original English: Now, you understand.
English: now, you understand.
Hindi: नाउ, यू अंडरस्टैंड.
Korean: 나우, 유 언더스탠드.

Original English: You have associated with some of these men.
English: you have associated with some of these men.
Hindi: यू हैव असोसिएटेड विथ सम अव थीज़ मेन.
Korean: 유 해브 어소시에이티드 위드 썸 오브 디즈 멘.

Original English: And there's no chivalry, no quarter shown in this fight.
English: and there's no chivalry, no quarter shown in this fight.
Hindi: ऐंड धेरज़ नो चिवल्री, नो क्वार्टर शोन इन दिस फाइट.
Korean: 앤드 데어즈 노 치벌리, 노 쿼터 쇼운 인 디스 파이트.

Original English: Lord Fitzhugh is the key to the whole situation.
English: lord fitzhugh is the key to the whole situation.
Hindi: लॉर्ड फिट्सह्यू इज़ द की टू द होल सिचुएशन.
Korean: 로드 피츠휴 이즈 더 키 투 더 홀 시츄에이션.

Original English: All operations have been carried on from Montreal and Toronto.
English: all operations have been carried on from montreal and toronto.
Hindi: ऑल ऑपरेशंस हैव बीन कैरीड ऑन फ्रॉम मॉन्ट्रियल ऐंड टोरंटो.
Korean: 올 오퍼레이션즈 해브 빈 캐리드 온 프럼 몬트리올 앤드 토론토.

Original English: Gregson held a lighted match until it burnt his fingertips.
English: gregson held a lighted match until it burnt his fingertips.
Hindi: ग्रेगसन हेल्ड अ लाइटेड मैच अन्टिल इट बर्न्ट हिस फिंगरटिप्स.
Korean: 그렉슨 헬드 아 라이티드 매치 언틸 잇 번트 히즈 핑거팁스.

Original English: Gregson had seated himself under the lamp and was sharpening a pencil.
English: gregson had seated himself under the lamp and was sharpening a pencil.
Hindi: ग्रेगसन हैड सीटेड हिमसेल्फ अंडर द लैम्प एंड वज़ शार्पनिंग अ पेंसिल.
Korean: 그렉슨 해드 시티드 힘셀프 언더 더 램프 앤드 워즈 샤프닝 아 펜슬.

Original English: He caught himself with a jerk.
English: he caught himself with a jerk.
Hindi: ही कॉट हिम्सेल्फ विद अ जर्क.
Korean: 히 코트 힘셀프 위드 아 저크.

Original English: How does your wager look now.
English: how does your wager look now.
Hindi: हाउ डज़ योर वेजर लुक नाउ.
Korean: 하우 더즈 유어 웨이저 룩 나우.

Original English: He confessed that the sketch had startled him.
English: he confessed that the sketch had startled him.
Hindi: ही कन्फेस्ट दॅट द स्केच हैड स्टार्टल्ड हिम.
Korean: 히 컨페스트 댓 더 스케치 해드 스타틀드 힘.

Original English: After all, the picture was only a resemblance.
English: after all, the picture was only a resemblance.
Hindi: ऐफ्टर ऑल, द पिक्चर वज़ ओनली अ रेसम्बलन्स.
Korean: 애프터 올, 더 픽쳐 워즈 온리 아 리젬블런스.

Original English: He wondered, too, where Roscoe was.
English: he wondered, too, where roscoe was.
Hindi: ही वंडर्ड, टू, वेयर रॉस्को वज़.
Korean: 히 원더드, 투, 웨어 로스코 워즈.

Original English: Philip knew that she was not an Indian.
English: philip knew that she was not an indian.
Hindi: फिलिप न्यू धैट शी वज़ नॉट अन इंडियन.
Korean: 필립 뉴 댓 쉬 워즈 낫 안 인디언.

Original English: In her haste to get away she had forgotten these things.
English: in her haste to get away she had forgotten these things.
Hindi: इन हर हेस्ट टू गेट अवे शी हैड फॉरगॉटन दीज़ थिंग्स.
Korean: 인 허 헤이스트 투 겟 어웨이 쉬 해드 퍼가튼 디즈 싱즈.

Original English: Philip took a step toward Gregson, half determined to awaken him.
English: philip took a step toward gregson, half determined to awaken him.
Hindi: फिलिप टुक अ स्टेप टुवर्ड ग्रेगसन, हाफ डिटरमाइंड टू अवेकन हिम.
Korean: 필립 툭 아 스텝 투월드 그렉슨, 핲 디터민드 투 어웨이큰 힘.

Original English: The thought set his blood tingling.
English: the thought set his blood tingling.
Hindi: द थॉट सेट हिज़ ब्लड टिंगलिंग.
Korean: 더 쏫 셋 히즈 블러드 팅글링.

Original English: But if Pierre did not return, until tomorrow.
English: but if pierre did not return, until tomorrow.
Hindi: बट इफ पियर डिड नाट रिटर्न, अनटिल टुमारो.
Korean: 벗 이프 피에르 딛 낫 리턴, 언틸 투모로우.

Original English: Ten minutes had not elapsed since he had dropped the handkerchief.
English: ten minutes had not elapsed since he had dropped the handkerchief.
Hindi: टेन मिनिट्स हैड नॉट इलैप्सड सिन्स ही हैड ड्रॉप्ट द हैंडकरचीफ.
Korean: 텐 미닛 해드 낫 일랩스드 신스 히 해드 드랍트 더 핸커치프.

Original English: It won't be for sale.
English: it will not be for sale.
Hindi: इट विल नॉट बी फॉर सेल.
Korean: 잇 윌 낫 비 포 세일.

Original English: For a few moments he ate in silence.
English: for a few moments he ate in silence.
Hindi: फॉर अ फ्यू मोमेंट्स ही एट इन साइलेंस.
Korean: 포 아 퓨 모먼츠 히 에이트 인 사일런스.

Original English: Philip did not pursue the subject.
English: philip did not pursue the subject.
Hindi: फिलिप डिड नॉट परस्यू द सब्जेक्ट.
Korean: 필립 딛 낫 퍼수 더 섭젝트.

Original English: Philip produced a couple of cigars and took a chair opposite him.
English: philip produced a couple of cigars and took a chair opposite him.
Hindi: फिलिप प्रोड्यूस्ट अ कपल अव सिगार्स एंड टुक अ चेयर ऑपोसिट हिम.
Korean: 필립 프로듀스트 아 커플 오브 시가즈 앤드 툭 아 체어 오퍼짓 힘.

Original English: Suppose you saw me at work through the window.
English: suppose you saw me at work through the window.
Hindi: सपोज़ यू सॉ मी ऐट वर्क थ्रू द विंडो.
Korean: 서포즈 유 소 미 앳 워크 쓰루 더 윈도우.

Original English: He looked like one who had passed through an uncomfortable hour or two.
English: he looked like one who had passed through an uncomfortable hour or two.
Hindi: ही लुक्त लाइक वन हू हैड पास्ट थ्रू अन अनकंफर्टेबल आयुर ऑर टू.
Korean: 히 룩트 라이크 원 후 해드 패스트 쓰루 안 언컴퍼터블 아유어 오어 투.

Original English: There was nothing more, except a large ink blot under the words.
English: there was nothing more, except a large ink blot under the words.
Hindi: धेर वस नथिंग मोर, एक्सेप्ट अ लार्ज इंक ब्लॉट अंडर द वर्ड्स.
Korean: 데어 워즈 너띵 모어, 엑셉트 아 라지 잉크 블랏 언더 더 워즈.

Original English: All this day Gregson remained in the cabin.
English: all this day gregson remained in the cabin.
Hindi: ऑल दिस डे ग्रेगसन रिमेन्ड इन द कैबिन.
Korean: 올 디스 데이 그렉슨 리메인드 인 더 캐빈.

Original English: The sixth day he spent in the cabin with Gregson.
English: the sixth day he spent in the cabin with gregson.
Hindi: द सिक्स्थ डे ही स्पेंट इन द कैबिन विथ ग्रेगसन.
Korean: 더 식스 데이 히 스펜트 인 더 캐빈 위드 그렉슨.

Original English: The flush was gone from her face.
English: the flush was gone from her face.
Hindi: द फ्लश वस गॉन फ्रॉम हर फेस.
Korean: 더 플러시 워즈 곤 프롬 허 페이스.

Original English: That is why I am, am rattled, he laughed.
English: that is why i am, am rattled, he laughed.
Hindi: दॅट इस वाई आई ऐम, ऐम रैटल्ड, ही लाफ्ड.
Korean: 댓 이즈 와이 아이 앰, 앰 래틀드, 히 래프드.

Original English: He understood the meaning of the look.
English: he understood the meaning of the look.
Hindi: ही अंडरस्टूड द मीनिंग अव द लुक.
Korean: 히 언더스투드 더 미닝 어브 더 룩.

Original English: She was even more beautiful than when I saw her, before.
English: she was even more beautiful than when i saw her, before.
Hindi: शी वस ईवन मोर ब्यूटीफुल धन वेन आई सॉ हर, बिफोर.
Korean: 쉬 워즈 이븐 모어 뷰티풀 댄 웬 아이 소 허, 비포어.

Original English: I'll give a thousand if you produce her, retorted Gregson.
English: i will give a thousand if you produce her, retorted gregson.
Hindi: आई विल गिव अ थाउज़ेंड इफ यू प्रोड्यूस हर, रिटॉर्टेड ग्रेगसन.
Korean: 아이 윌 기브 아 싸우전드 이프 유 프로듀스 허, 리토티드 그렉슨.

Original English: They have won popular sentiment through the newspapers.
English: they have won popular sentiment through the newspapers.
Hindi: थे हैव वन पॉपुलर सेंटिमेंट थ्रू द न्यूज़पेपर्स.
Korean: 데이 해브 원 파퓰러 센티먼트 쓰루 더 뉴스페이퍼즈.

Original English: We must achieve our own salvation.
English: we must achieve our own salvation.
Hindi: वी मस्ट अचीव आउर ओन सैल्वेशन.
Korean: 위 머스트 어치브 아워 오운 살베이션.

Original English: In moments of mental energy Philip was restless.
English: in moments of mental energy philip was restless.
Hindi: इन मोमेंट्स ऑफ मेंटल एनर्जी फिलिप वज़ रेस्टलेस.
Korean: 인 모먼츠 어브 멘탈 에너지 필립 워즈 레슬리스.

Original English: He would keep his faith with Gregson for the promised day or two.
English: he would keep his faith with gregson for the promised day or two.
Hindi: ही वुड कीप हिज़ फेथ विध ग्रेगसन फॉर द प्रॉमिस्ड डे ऑर टू.
Korean: 히 우드 킵 히즈 페이스 위드 그렉슨 포어 더 프로미즈드 데이 오어 투.

Original English: Something about it seemed to fascinate him, to challenge his presence.
English: something about it seemed to fascinate him, to challenge his presence.
Hindi: समथिंग अबाउट इट सीम्ड टू फैसिनेट हिम, टू चैलेंज हिज़ प्रेज़ेंस.
Korean: 썸띵 어바웃 잇 심드 투 패시네이트 힘, 투 챌린지 히즈 프레즌스.

Original English: Now it was missing from the wall.
English: now it was missing from the wall.
Hindi: नाऊ इट वज़ मिसिंग फ्रम द वॉल.
Korean: 나우 잇 워즈 미싱 프롬 더 월.

Original English: He boiled himself some coffee and sat down to wait.
English: he boiled himself some coffee and sat down to wait.
Hindi: ही बॉइल्ड हिम्सेल्फ सम कॉफी ऐंड सैट डाउन टू वेट.
Korean: 히 보일드 힘셀프 섬 커피 앤드 샛 다운 투 웨이트.

Original English: I'm going down there with you, and I'm going to fight.
English: i am going down there with you, and i am going to fight.
Hindi: आई ऐम गोइंग डाउन धेर विथ यू, एंड आई ऐम गोइंग टू फाइट.
Korean: 아이 앰 고잉 다운 데어 위드 유, 앤드 아이 앰 고잉 투 파이트.

Original English: Now have you got anything to say against me, Mr Philip.
English: now have you got anything to say against me, mister philip.
Hindi: नाऊ हैव यू गॉट एनीथिंग टू से अगेंस्ट मी, मिस्टर फिलिप.
Korean: 나우 해브 유 갓 애니씽 투 세이 어겐스트 미, 미스터 필립.

Original English: If I meet her again I shall apologize, said Eileen.
English: if i meet her again i shall apologize, said eileen.
Hindi: इफ आई मीट हर अगेन आई शैल अपोलोजाइज़, सेड आइलीन.
Korean: 이프 아이 밋 허 어겐 아이 샬 어폴러자이즈, 쎄드 아일린.

Original English: Below him the shadow was broken into a pool of rippling starlight.
English: below him the shadow was broken into a pool of rippling starlight.
Hindi: बिलो हिम द शैडो वज ब्रोकन इंटू अ पूल अव रिपलिंग स्टारलाइट.
Korean: 빌로우 힘 더 샤도우 워즈 브로큰 인투 아 풀 오브 리플링 스타라이트.

Original English: Only the chance sound had led him to observe them.
English: only the chance sound had led him to observe them.
Hindi: ओनली द चांस साउंड हैड लेड हिम टू अब्ज़र्व देम.
Korean: 온리 더 찬스 사운드 해드 레드 힘 투 옵저브 뎀.

Original English: Could the incident have anything to do with Jeanne and Pierre.
English: could the incident have anything to do with jeanne and pierre.
Hindi: कुड दि इन्सिडेंट हैव एनिथिंग टू डू विद जीन एंड पियर.
Korean: 쿧 디 인시던트 해브 애니씽 투 두 윗 진 앤드 피에르.

Original English: There was no chance to fire without hitting him.
English: there was no chance to fire without hitting him.
Hindi: देर वज़ नो चांस टू फायर विदाउट हिटिंग हिम.
Korean: 데얼 워즈 노 찬스 투 파이어 위덧 히팅 힘.

Original English: There was no answer from the other side.
English: there was no answer from the other side.
Hindi: देर वस नो आंसर फ्रम दि अदर साइड.
Korean: 데어 와즈 노 앤서 프럼 디 어더 사이드.

Original English: Then he hastened on, as Pierre had guided him.
English: then he hastened on, as pierre had guided him.
Hindi: धेन ही हासनड ऑन, ऐज़ पिएर हैड गाइडेड हिम.
Korean: 덴 히 헤이슨드 온, 애즈 피에르 해드 가이드 힘.

Original English: With these arguments he convinced himself that he should go on alone.
English: with these arguments he convinced himself that he should go on alone.
Hindi: विथ दीज आर्ग्युमेंट्स ही कन्विंस्ट हिम्सेल्फ दैट ही शुद गो ऑन अलोन.
Korean: 위드 디즈 아규먼츠 히 컨빈스트 힘셀프 댓 히 슏 고 온 얼론.

Original English: Yet, behind them there was another and more powerful motive.
English: yet, behind them there was another and more powerful motive.
Hindi: येट, बिहाइंड देम धेर वज़ अनदर एंड मोर पावरफुल मोटिव.
Korean: 옛, 비하인드 뎀 데어 워즈 어나더 앤드 모어 파워풀 모티브.

Original English: In that case he could not miss them, if he used caution.
English: in that case he could not miss them, if he used caution.
Hindi: इन दैट केस ही कुड नाट मिस धेम, इफ ही यूज़्ड कॉशन.
Korean: 인 댓 케이스 히 쿧 낫 미스 뎀, 이프 히 유즈드 코션.

Original English: Before Philip could recover himself Jeanne's startled guards were upon him.
English: before philip could recover himself jeanne's startled guards were upon him.
Hindi: बिफोर फिलिप कुड रिकवर हिम्सेल्फ जीन्स स्टार्टल्ड गार्ड्स वेर अपॉन हिम.
Korean: 비포어 필립 쿧 리커버 힘셀프 진즈 스타틀드 가즈 워 어폰 힘.

Original English: It is the nearest refuge.
English: it is the nearest refuge.
Hindi: इट इज द निरस्ट रेफ्यूज.
Korean: 잇 이즈 더 니어레스트 레퓨지.

Original English: There was pride and strength, the ring of triumph in his voice.
English: there was pride and strength, the ring of triumph in his voice.
Hindi: धेर वज़ प्राइड ऐंड स्ट्रेंथ, द रिंग अव ट्रायम्फ इन हिज़ वॉइस.
Korean: 데어 워즈 프라이드 앤드 스트렝스, 더 링 어브 트라이엄프 인 히즈 보이스.

Original English: The truth of it set Jeanne quivering.
English: the truth of it set jeanne quivering.
Hindi: द ट्रुथ अव इट सेट जीन क्विवरिंग.
Korean: 더 트루스 어브 잇 셋 진 퀴버링.

Original English: Tomorrow it will be strong enough for you to stand upon.
English: tomorrow it will be strong enough for you to stand upon.
Hindi: टमॉरो इट विल बी स्ट्रॉंग इनफ फॉर यू टू स्टैंड अपॉन.
Korean: 투모로우 잇 윌 비 스트롱 이너프 포 유 투 스탠드 어폰.

Original English: You were going to leave after you saw me on the rock.
English: you were going to leave after you saw me on the rock.
Hindi: यू वेर गोइंग टू लीव आफ्टर यू सॉ मी ऑन द रॉक.
Korean: 유 워 고잉 투 리브 애프터 유 쏘 미 온 더 락.

Original English: He bit his tongue, and cursed himself at this fresh break.
English: he bit his tongue, and cursed himself at this fresh break.
Hindi: ही बिट हिज टंग, ऐंड कर्स्ड हिम्सेल्फ ऐट दिस फ्रेश ब्रेक.
Korean: 히 빗 히즈 텅, 앤드 커스드 힘셀프 앳 디스 프레시 브레이크.

Original English: In it there was something that was almost tragedy.
English: in it there was something that was almost tragedy.
Hindi: इन इट देर वस समथिंग दॅट वस ऑलमोस्ट ट्रैजेडी.
Korean: 인 잇 데어 워즈 썸씽 댓 워즈 올모스트 트래저디.

Original English: Your face is red with blood.
English: your face is red with blood.
Hindi: योर फेस इज़ रेड विथ ब्लड.
Korean: 유어 페이스 이즈 레드 위드 블러드.

Original English: Her eyes smiled truth at him as he came up the bank.
English: her eyes smiled truth at him as he came up the bank.
Hindi: हर आईज़ स्माइल्ड ट्रूथ ऐट हिम ऐज़ ही केम अप द बैंक.
Korean: 허 아이즈 스마일드 트루스 앳 힘 애즈 히 케임 업 더 뱅크.

Original English: He can care for himself.
English: he can care for himself.
Hindi: ही कैन केयर फॉर हिम्सेल्फ.
Korean: 히 캔 케어 포어 힘셀프.

Original English: They will search for us between their camp and Churchill.
English: they will search for us between their camp and churchill.
Hindi: धे विल सर्च फॉर अस बिटवीन देर कैंप एंड चर्चिल.
Korean: 데이 윌 서치 포어 어스 비트윈 데어 캠프 앤드 처칠.

Original English: Until I die, he exclaimed.
English: until i die, he exclaimed.
Hindi: अन्टिल आई डाई, ही एक्सक्लेम्ड.
Korean: 언틸 아이 다이, 히 엑스클레임드.

Original English: Her beautiful hair was done up in shining coils.
English: her beautiful hair was done up in shining coils.
Hindi: हर ब्यूटिफुल हेयर वाज़ डन अप इन शाइनिंग कॉयल्स.
Korean: 허 뷰리풀 헤어 워즈 던 업 인 샤이닝 코일즈.

Original English: The Churchill narrowed and its current became swifter as they progressed.
English: the churchill narrowed and its current became swifter as they progressed.
Hindi: द चर्चिल नैरोड एंड इट्स करेंट बिकेम स्विफ्टर ऐज दे प्रोग्रेस्ट.
Korean: 더 처칠 내로우드 앤드 잇츠 커런트 비케임 스위프터 애즈 데이 프로그레스트.

Original English: For a full half minute Jeanne looked at him without speaking.
English: for a full half minute jeanne looked at him without speaking.
Hindi: फॉर अ फुल हाफ मिनट जीन लुक्ट ऐट हिम विदाउट स्पीकिंग.
Korean: 포어 아 풀 해프 미닛 진 룩트 앳 힘 위다웃 스피킹.

Original English: I want to die in it.
English: i want to die in it.
Hindi: आई वांट टू डाई इन इट.
Korean: 아이 완트 투 다이 인 잇.

Original English: Darkness hid him from Jeanne.
English: darkness hid him from jeanne.
Hindi: डार्कनेस हिड हिम फ्रम जीन.
Korean: 다크니스 히드 힘 프럼 진.

Original English: And yet if she came he had no words to say.
English: and yet if she came he had no words to say.
Hindi: ऐंड येट इफ शी केम ही हैड नो वर्ड्स टू से.
Korean: 앤드 옛 이프 쉬 케임 히 해드 노 워즈 투 세이.

Original English: He heard a sound which brought him quickly into consciousness of day.
English: he heard a sound which brought him quickly into consciousness of day.
Hindi: ही हर्ड अ साउंड विच ब्रॉट हिम क्विक्ली इंटु कॉन्शसनेस अव डे.
Korean: 히 허드 아 사운드 위치 브로트 힘 퀵리 인투 컨셔스니스 어브 데이.

Original English: Within himself he called it no longer his own.
English: within himself he called it no longer his own.
Hindi: विथिन हिम्सेल्फ ही कॉल्ड इट नो लॉन्गर हिज़ ओन.
Korean: 위딘 힘셀프 히 콜드 잇 노 롱거 히즈 온.

Original English: Besides, that noise makes me deaf.
English: besides, that noise makes me deaf.
Hindi: बिसाइड्स, दॅट नॉइज़ मेक्स मी डेफ.
Korean: 비사이즈, 댓 노이즈 메익스 미 데프.

Original English: Philip looked back from the crest and saw Jeanne leaning over the canoe.
English: philip looked back from the crest and saw jeanne leaning over the canoe.
Hindi: फिलिप लुक्ट बैक फ्रम द क्रेस्ट ऐंड सॉ जीन लीनिंग ओवर द कनू.
Korean: 필립 룩트 백 프럼 더 크레스트 앤드 소 진 리닝 오버 더 카누.

Original English: Fifty yards ahead of her were the first of the rocks.
English: fifty yards ahead of her were the first of the rocks.
Hindi: फिफ्टी यार्ड्स अहेड अव हर वेर द फर्स्ट अव द रॉक्स.
Korean: 피프티 야즈 어헤드 어브 허 워 더 퍼스트 어브 더 록스.

Original English: There was one chance, and only one, of saving Jeanne.
English: there was one chance, and only one, of saving jeanne.
Hindi: देर वज़ वन चांस, ऐंड ओनली वन, अव सेविंग जीन.
Korean: 데어 워즈 원 찬스, 앤드 온리 원, 오브 세이빙 진.

Original English: You're a devil for fighting, and will surely win.
English: you are a devil for fighting, and will surely win.
Hindi: यू आर अ डेविल फॉर फाइटिंग, एंड विल शुरली विन.
Korean: 유 아 아 데빌 포어 파이팅, 앤드 윌 슈어리 윈.

Original English: I'll only be in the way.
English: i will only be in the way.
Hindi: आई विल ओनली बी इन द वे.
Korean: 아이 윌 온리 비 인 더 웨이.

Original English: He lifted his eyes, and a strange cry burst from his lips.
English: he lifted his eyes, and a strange cry burst from his lips.
Hindi: ही लिफ्टेड हिज़ आइज़, एंड अ स्ट्रेंज क्राइ बर्स्ट फ्रॉम हिज़ लिप्स.
Korean: 히 리프티드 히즈 아이즈, 앤드 아 스트레인지 크라이 버스트 프럼 히즈 립스.

Original English: Shooting pains passed like flashes of electricity through his body.
English: shooting pains passed like flashes of electricity through his body.
Hindi: शूटिंग पेन्स पास्ट लाइक फ्लैशेस अव इलेक्ट्रिसिटी थ्रू हिज़ बॉडी.
Korean: 슈팅 페인즈 패스트 라이크 플래시즈 오브 일렉트리시티 쓰루 히즈 바디.

Original English: I know that you are in charge there, and Jeanne knows.
English: i know that you are in charge there, and jeanne knows.
Hindi: आई नो दैट यू आर इन चार्ज देर, ऐंड जीन नोज़.
Korean: 아이 노우 댓 유 아 인 차지 데어, 앤드 진 노우즈.

Original English: For a full minute the two men stared into each other's face.
English: for a full minute the two men stared into each other's face.
Hindi: फॉर अ फुल मिनट द टू मेन स्टेर्ड इंटू ईच अदर्स फेस.
Korean: 포 아 풀 미닛 더 투 멘 스테어드 인투 이치 어더즈 페이스.

Original English: He was sure, now, of but few things.
English: he was sure, now, of but few things.
Hindi: ही वज़ शुर, नाउ, अव बट फ्यू थिंग्स.
Korean: 히 워즈 슈어, 나우, 어브 벗 퓨 띵즈.

Original English: It was a miracle, and I owe you my life.
English: it was a miracle, and i owe you my life.
Hindi: इट वज़ अ मिरकल, ऐंड आई ओ यू माई लाइफ.
Korean: 잇 워즈 아 미라클, 앤드 아이 오우 유 마이 라이프.

Original English: Philip ate lightly of the food which Pierre had ready for him.
English: philip ate lightly of the food which pierre had ready for him.
Hindi: फिलिप एट लाइटली अव द फूड विच पिएर हैड रेडी फॉर हिम.
Korean: 필립 에이트 라잇리 어브 더 푸드 위치 피에르 해드 레디 포어 힘.

Original English: Such men believe, when they come together.
English: such men believe, when they come together.
Hindi: सच मेन बिलीव, वेन थे कम टुगेदर.
Korean: 서치 멘 빌리브, 웬 데이 컴 투게더.

Original English: The journey was continued at dawn.
English: the journey was continued at dawn.
Hindi: द जर्नी वज कंटिन्यूड एट डॉन.
Korean: 더 저니 워즈 컨티뉴드 앳 돈.

Original English: Jeanne and Pierre both gazed toward the great rock.
English: jeanne and pierre both gazed toward the great rock.
Hindi: जीन एंड पियर बोथ गेज्ड टुवर्ड द ग्रेट रॉक.
Korean: 진 앤드 피에르 보스 게이즈드 투워드 더 그레이트 락.

Original English: There was something pathetic in the girl's attitude now.
English: there was something pathetic in the girl's attitude now.
Hindi: देर वज़ समथिंग पथेटिक इन द गर्ल्स ऐटिट्यूड नाउ.
Korean: 데어 워즈 섬씽 패더릭 인 더 걸즈 애티튜드 나우.

Original English: He moved his position, and the illusion was gone.
English: he moved his position, and the illusion was gone.
Hindi: ही मूव्ड हिज पॉज़िशन, ऐंड दि इल्यूजन वज़ गॉन.
Korean: 히 무브드 히즈 퍼지션, 앤드 디 일루전 워즈 곤.

Original English: For two hours not a word passed between them.
English: for two hours not a word passed between them.
Hindi: फॉर टू आयुर्ज़ नॉट अ वर्ड पास्ट बिटवीन देम.
Korean: 포어 투 아이오즈 낫 아 워드 패스트 비트윈 뎀.

Original English: I have hunted along this ridge, replied Philip.
English: i have hunted along this ridge, replied philip.
Hindi: आई हैव हंटेड अलॉन्ग दिस रिज, रिप्लाइड फिलिप.
Korean: 아이 해브 헌티드 얼롱 디스 리지, 리플라이드 필립.

Original English: That's Thorpe's, said the young engineer.
English: that's thorpe's, said the young engineer.
Hindi: दैट्स थॉर्प्स, सेड द यंग इंजीनियर.
Korean: 댓츠 소프스, 쎄드 더 영 엔지니어.

Original English: We saw your light, and thought you wouldn't mind a call.
English: we saw your light, and thought you would not mind a call.
Hindi: वी सॉ यूर लाइट, ऐंड थॉट यू वुड नॉट माइंड अ कॉल.
Korean: 위 소 유어 라이트, 앤드 쏘트 유 우드 낫 마인드 아 콜.

Original English: Billinger may arrive in time.
English: billinger may arrive in time.
Hindi: बिलिंगर मे अराइव इन टाइम.
Korean: 빌링거 메이 어라이브 인 타임.

Original English: There's the hitch, replied Thorpe, rolling a cigarette.
English: there's the hitch, replied thorpe, rolling a cigarette.
Hindi: देरज़ द हिच, रिप्लाइड थॉर्प, रोलिंग अ सिगरेट.
Korean: 데어즈 더 히치, 리플라이드 소프, 롤링 아 시가렛.

Original English: I want my men to work by themselves.
English: i want my men to work by themselves.
Hindi: आई वांट माइ मेन टू वर्क बाय देम्सेल्व्ज़.
Korean: 아이 완트 마이 멘 투 워크 바이 뎀셀브즈.

Original English: Philip saw MacDougall soon after his short talk with Thorpe.
English: philip saw macdougall soon after his short talk with thorpe.
Hindi: फिलिप सॉ मकडूगल सून आफ्टर हिज शॉर्ट टॉक विद थॉर्प.
Korean: 필립 소 맥두걸 순 애프터 히즈 숏 톡 위드 소르프.

Original English: Neither could they understand the growing disaffection among Thorpe's men.
English: neither could they understand the growing disaffection among thorpe's men.
Hindi: नीदर कुड थे अंडरस्टैंड द ग्रोइंग डिसअफेक्शन अमंग थॉर्प्स मेन.
Korean: 니더 쿧 데이 언더스탠드 더 그로잉 디서펙션 어몽 소르프스 멘.

Original English: Two weeks passed, and in that time Thorpe left camp three times.
English: two weeks passed, and in that time thorpe left camp three times.
Hindi: टू वीक्स पास्ट, ऐंड इन दैट टाइम थॉर्प लेफ्ट कैम्प थ्री टाइम्स.
Korean: 투 윅스 패스트, 앤드 인 댓 타임 쏘프 레프트 캠프 쓰리 타임즈.

Original English: It was the third or fourth time that Philip had heard MacDougall swear.
English: it was the third or fourth time that philip had heard macdougall swear.
Hindi: इट वज़ द थर्ड और फोर्थ टाइम दैट फिलिप हैड हर्ड मैकडूगल स्वेअर.
Korean: 잇 워즈 더 서드 오어 포스 타임 댓 필립 해드 허드 맥두걸 스웨어.

Original English: Blood was oozing slowly from the wounded man's right breast.
English: blood was oozing slowly from the wounded man's right breast.
Hindi: ब्लड वज़ ऊज़िंग स्लोली फ्रॉम द वूंडेड मैन्स राइट ब्रेस्ट.
Korean: 블러드 워즈 우징 슬로울리 프럼 더 운디드 맨즈 라잇 브레스트.

Original English: He destroyed everything that had belonged to the woman.
English: he destroyed everything that had belonged to the woman.
Hindi: ही डिस्ट्रॉइड एव्रिथिंग दैट हैड बिलॉंग्ड टू द वुमन.
Korean: 히 디스트로이드 에브리띵 댓 핫 빌롱드 투 더 우먼.

Original English: Philip bent low over Pierre.
English: philip bent low over pierre.
Hindi: फिलिप बेंट लो ओवर पियर.
Korean: 필립 벤트 로우 오버 피에르.

Original English: Did Thorpe go to see any one in Churchill.
English: did thorpe go to see any one in churchill.
Hindi: डिड थॉर्प गो टू सी ऐनी वन इन चर्चिल.
Korean: 디드 토프 고 투 씨 애니 원 인 처칠.

Original English: She saw the answer in his face.
English: she saw the answer in his face.
Hindi: शी सॉ दि एंसर इन हिज़ फेस.
Korean: 쉬 소 디 앤서 인 히즈 페이스.

Original English: Thorpe and his men were to destroy this camp, and kill you.
English: thorpe and his men were to destroy this camp, and kill you.
Hindi: थॉर्प एंड हिज़ मेन वर टू डिस्ट्रॉय दिस कैम्प, एंड किल यू.
Korean: 쏘프 앤드 히즈 멘 워 투 디스트로이 디스 캠프, 앤드 킬 유.

Original English: There is no need of further detail, now, for you can understand.
English: there is no need of further detail, now, for you can understand.
Hindi: देर इज नो नीड अव फर्दर डिटेल, नाउ, फॉर यू कैन अंडरस्टैंड.
Korean: 데어 이즈 노 니드 어브 퍼더 디테일, 나우, 포어 유 캔 언더스탠드.

Original English: There followed a roar that shook the earth.
English: there followed a roar that shook the earth.
Hindi: देर फालोड अ रोर धैट शुक दि अर्थ.
Korean: 데어 팔로드 아 로어 댓 슉 디 어스.

Original English: Blind with rage, he darted in.
English: blind with rage, he darted in.
Hindi: ब्लाइंड विथ रेज, ही डार्टेड इन.
Korean: 블라인드 위드 레이지, 히 다티드 인.

Original English: In it was the joy of life.
English: in it was the joy of life.
Hindi: इन इट वस द जॉय अव लाइफ.
Korean: 인 잇 워즈 더 조이 어브 라이프.

Original English: Swiftly his eyes measured the situation.
English: swiftly his eyes measured the situation.
Hindi: स्विफ्टली हिज़ आईज़ मेजर्ड द सिचुएशन.
Korean: 스위프트리 히즈 아이즈 메저드 더 시추에이션.

Original English: But this little defect did not worry him.
English: but this little defect did not worry him.
Hindi: बट दिस लिटल डिफेक्ट डिड नॉट वरी हिम.
Korean: 벗 디스 리틀 디펙트 딛 낫 워리 힘.

Original English: And then, steadily, he began to chew.
English: and then, steadily, he began to chew.
Hindi: एंड धेन, स्टेडिली, ही बिगैन टू च्यू.
Korean: 앤드 덴, 스테딜리, 히 비갠 투 츄.

Original English: Together they ate the rabbit.
English: together they ate the rabbit.
Hindi: टुगेदर दे एट द रैबिट.
Korean: 투게더 데이 에잇 더 래빗.

Original English: They edged nearer, and stood shoulder to shoulder facing their world.
English: they edged nearer, and stood shoulder to shoulder facing their world.
Hindi: दे एज्ड नियरर, ऐंड स्टुड शोल्डर टू शोल्डर फेसिंग देयर वर्ल्ड.
Korean: 데이 에지드 니러, 앤드 스투드 쇼울더 투 쇼울더 페이싱 데어 월드.

Original English: It was beating and waiting in the ambush of those black pits.
English: it was beating and waiting in the ambush of those black pits.
Hindi: इट वज़ बीटिंग एंड वेटिंग इन दि ऐम्बुश अव धोज़ ब्लैक पिट्स.
Korean: 잇 워즈 비팅 앤드 웨이팅 인 디 앰부쉬 어브 도즈 블랙 피츠.

Original English: Something vastly more thrilling had come into it now.
English: something vastly more thrilling had come into it now.
Hindi: समथिंग वैस्टली मोर थ्रिलिंग हैड कम इंटु इट नाउ.
Korean: 썸씽 밧슬리 모어 쓰릴링 해드 컴 인투 잇 나우.

Original English: It took him half an hour to reach the edge of it.
English: it took him half an hour to reach the edge of it.
Hindi: इट टूक हिम हाफ अन आवर टू रीच दि एज अव इट.
Korean: 잇 툭 힘 해프 안 아우어 투 리치 디 에지 어브 잇.

Original English: But there was no longer the mother yearning in his heart.
English: but there was no longer the mother yearning in his heart.
Hindi: बट देर वस नो लॉन्गर द मदर यर्निंग इन हिज हार्ट.
Korean: 벗 데어 워즈 노 롱거 더 머더 이어닝 인 히즈 하트.

Original English: Besides, had he not whipped the big owl in the forest.
English: besides, had he not whipped the big owl in the forest.
Hindi: बिसाइड्स, हैड ही नॉट विप्ड द बिग आउल इन द फॉरेस्ट.
Korean: 비사이즈, 해드 히 낫 윕트 더 빅 아울 인 더 포레스트.

Original English: After all, it was simply a mistake in judgment.
English: after all, it was simply a mistake in judgment.
Hindi: आफ्टर ऑल, इट वस सिम्पली अ मिस्टेक इन जजमेंट.
Korean: 애프터 올, 잇 워즈 심플리 아 미스테이크 인 저지먼트.

Original English: Had it struck squarely it would have killed him.
English: had it struck squarely it would have killed him.
Hindi: हैड इट स्ट्रक स्क्वेरली इट वुड हैव किल्ड हिम.
Korean: 핻 잇 스트럭 스퀘얼리 잇 우드 해브 킬드 힘.

Original English: The Indian even poked his stick into the thick ground spruce.
English: the indian even poked his stick into the thick ground spruce.
Hindi: दि इंडियन ईवन पोकेड हिज़ स्टिक इंटू द थिक ग्राउंड स्प्रूस.
Korean: 디 인디언 이븐 포크트 히즈 스틱 인투 더 틱 그라운드 스프루스.

Original English: Pebbles and dirt flew along with hair and fur.
English: pebbles and dirt flew along with hair and fur.
Hindi: पेबल्स ऐंड डर्ट फ्लू अलॉन्ग विथ हेयर ऐंड फर.
Korean: 페블즈 앤드 더트 플루 얼롱 위드 헤어 앤드 퍼.

Original English: And he was filled with a strange and foreboding fear.
English: and he was filled with a strange and foreboding fear.
