Hindi: एंड ही वस फिल्ड विथ अ स्ट्रेंज एंड फोरबोडिंग फियर.
Korean: 앤드 히 워즈 필드 위드 아 스트레인지 앤드 포어보딩 피어.

Original English: It was steel, a fisher trap.
English: it was steel, a fisher trap.
Hindi: इट वज़ स्टील, अ फिशर ट्रैप.
Korean: 잇 워즈 스틸, 아 피셔 트랩.

Original English: OW, a wild dog, he growled.
English: ow, a wild dog, he growled.
Hindi: ओ, अ वाइल्ड डॉग, ही ग्राउल्ड.
Korean: 오, 아 와일드 독, 히 그라울드.

Original English: He was a pariah; a wanderer without a friend or a home.
English: he was a pariah a wanderer without a friend or a home.
Hindi: ही वज़ अ परिय अ वांडरर विधाउट अ फ्रेंड ओर अ होम.
Korean: 히 워즈 아 퍼라이아 아 완더러 위다웃 아 프렌드 오어 아 홈.

Original English: That is the strange part of it.
English: that is the strange part of it.
Hindi: दैट इस द स्ट्रेंज पार्ट अव इट.
Korean: 댓 이즈 더 스트레인지 파트 어브 잇.

Original English: His freshly caught furs he flung to the floor.
English: his freshly caught furs he flung to the floor.
Hindi: हिज़ फ्रेशली कॉट फर्स ही फ्लंग टू द फ्लोर.
Korean: 히즈 프레슐리 코트 퍼즈 히 플렁 투 더 플로어.

Original English: For that reason Le Beau had chosen him to fight the big fight.
English: for that reason le beau had chosen him to fight the big fight.
Hindi: फॉर धैट रीज़न ले बो हैड चोज़न हिम टू फाइट द बिग फाइट.
Korean: 포 댓 리즌 러 보우 햇 초즌 힘 투 파이트 더 빅 파이트.

Original English: In the crib the baby sat up and began to prattle.
English: in the crib the baby sat up and began to prattle.
Hindi: इन द क्रिब द बेबी सैट अप ऐंड बिगैन टू प्रैटल.
Korean: 인 더 크립 더 베이비 샛 업 앤드 비겐 투 프래틀.

Original English: She obeyed, shrinking back with the baby in her arms.
English: she obeyed, shrinking back with the baby in her arms.
Hindi: शी ओबेड, श्रिंकिंग बैक विथ द बेबी इन हर आर्म्स.
Korean: 시 오베이드, 슈링킹 백 위드 더 베이비 인 허 암즈.

Original English: His teeth shut with a last click.
English: his teeth shut with a last click.
Hindi: हिज़ टीथ शट विथ अ लास्ट क्लिक.
Korean: 히스 티쓰 셧 위드 아 래스트 클릭.

Original English: It was over when he made his way through the ring of spectators.
English: it was over when he made his way through the ring of spectators.
Hindi: इट वज़ ओवर वेन ही मेड हिज़ वे थ्रू द रिंग अव स्पेक्टेटरज़.
Korean: 잇 와즈 오버 웬 히 메이드 히즈 웨이 쓰루 더 링 어브 스펙테이터즈.

Original English: In a flash he was on his feet, facing him.
English: in a flash he was on his feet, facing him.
Hindi: इन अ फ्लैश ही वज़ ऑन हिस फीट, फेसिंग हिम.
Korean: 인 아 플래시 히 워즈 온 히즈 피트, 페이싱 힘.

Original English: He thought he saw a shudder pass through the Factor's shoulders.
English: he thought he saw a shudder pass through the factor's shoulders.
Hindi: ही थॉट ही सॉ अ शडर पास थ्रू द फैक्टर्स शोल्डर्स.
Korean: 히 쏨 히 서 아 셔더 패스 쓰루 더 팩터즈 숄더즈.

Original English: The moon had already begun its westward decline.
English: the moon had already begun its westward decline.
Hindi: द मून हैड ऑलरेडी बिगन इट्स वेस्टवर्ड डिक्लाइन.
Korean: 더 문 해드 알레디 비건 잇츠 웨스트워드 디클라인.

Original English: They laughed like two happy children.
English: they laughed like two happy children.
Hindi: दे लाफ्ड लाइक टू हैपी चिल्ड्रन.
Korean: 데이 래프드 라이크 투 해피 칠드런.

Original English: He pulled, and the log crashed down to break his back.
English: he pulled, and the log crashed down to break his back.
Hindi: ही पुल्ड, ऐंड द लॉग क्रैश्ड डाउन टू ब्रेक हिज बैक.
Korean: 히 풀드, 앤드 더 로그 크래쉬드 다운 투 브레이크 히즈 백.

Original English: Fast, but endure.
English: fast, but endure.
Hindi: फास्ट, बट एंड्यूर.
Korean: 패스트, 벗 엔듀어.

Original English: A little before dawn of the day following, the fire relief came.
English: a little before dawn of the day following, the fire relief came.
Hindi: अ लिटिल बिफोर डॉन अव द डे फॉलोइंग, द फायर रिलीफ केम.
Korean: 아 리틀 비포 돈 어브 더 데이 팔로잉, 더 파이어 릴리프 케임.

Original English: The Indian felt the worship of her warm in his heart.
English: the indian felt the worship of her warm in his heart.
Hindi: दि इंडियन फेल्ट द वर्शिप अव हर वॉर्म इन हिस हार्ट.
Korean: 디 인디언 펠트 더 워십 어브 허 웜 인 히즈 하트.

Original English: He drew in a deep breath as he looked at them.
English: he drew in a deep breath as he looked at them.
Hindi: ही ड्रू इन अ दीप ब्रेथ ऐज़ ही लुक्त ऐट देम.
Korean: 히 드루 인 아 딥 브레스 애즈 히 룩트 앳 뎀.

Original English: Then he shouted, Shut up.
English: then he shouted, shut up.
Hindi: देन ही शाऊतेद, शट अप.
Korean: 덴 히 샤우티드, 셧 업.

Original English: He changed his seat for a steamer reclining chair.
English: he changed his seat for a steamer reclining chair.
Hindi: ही चेंज्ड हिज़ सीट फॉर अ स्टीमर रिक्लाइनिंग चेयर.
Korean: 히 체인지드 히즈 시트 포어 아 스티머 리클라이닝 체어.

Original English: On the far corner of the compound fence a hawk brooded.
English: on the far corner of the compound fence a hawk brooded.
Hindi: ऑन द फार कॉर्नर अव द कॉम्पाउंड फेंस अ हॉक ब्रूडेड.
Korean: 온 더 파 코너 어브 더 컴파운드 펜스 아 호크 브루디드.

Original English: To these he gave castor oil.
English: to these he gave castor oil.
Hindi: टू दीज़ ही गेव कैस्टर ऑइल.
Korean: 투 디즈 히 게이브 캐스터 오일.

Original English: Hatred and murder and lust for revenge they possessed to overflowing.
English: hatred and murder and lust for revenge they possessed to overflowing.
Hindi: हेट्रिड ऐंड मर्डर ऐंड लस्ट फॉर रिवेंज धे पज़ेस्ट टू ओवरफ्लोइंग.
Korean: 헤이트리드 앤드 머더 앤드 러스트 포 리벤지 데이 포제스트 투 오버플로잉.

Original English: Sheldon glanced at the thermometer.
English: sheldon glanced at the thermometer.
Hindi: शेल्डन ग्लैन्स्ट ऐट द थर्मामीटर.
Korean: 셸든 글랜스트 앳 더 써모미터.

Original English: I'll see to poor Hughie.
English: i will see to poor hughie.
Hindi: आई विल सी टू पूर ह्यूई.
Korean: 아이 윌 씨 투 푸어 휴이.

Original English: Her gray eyes were flashing, and her lips were quivering.
English: her gray eyes were flashing, and her lips were quivering.
Hindi: हर ग्रे आइज़ वर फ्लैशिंग, ऐंड हर लिप्स वर क्विवरिंग.
Korean: 허 그레이 아이즈 워 플래싱, 앤드 허 립스 워 퀴버링.

Original English: Also, I want information.
English: also, i want information.
Hindi: ऑल्सो, आई वांट इन्फर्मेशन.
Korean: 알소, 아이 원트 인포메이션.

Original English: Let them go out and eat with my boys.
English: let them go out and eat with my boys.
Hindi: लेट देम गो आउट ऐंड ईट विथ माय बॉयज़.
Korean: 렛 뎀 고 아웃 앤드 잇 위드 마이 보이즈.

Original English: I, I beg pardon, he drawled.
English: i, i beg pardon, he drawled.
Hindi: आई, आई बेग पार्डन, ही ड्रॉल्ड.
Korean: 아이, 아이 벡 파든, 히 드롤드.

Original English: And you preferred a cannibal isle and a cartridge belt.
English: and you preferred a cannibal isle and a cartridge belt.
Hindi: एंड यू प्रिफर्ड अ कैनिबल आइल एंड अ कार्ट्रिज बेल्ट.
Korean: 앤드 유 프리퍼드 아 캐니벌 아일 앤드 아 카트리지 벨트.

Original English: I was in New York when the crash came.
English: i was in new york when the crash came.
Hindi: आई वज़ इन न्यू यॉर्क वेन द क्रैश केम.
Korean: 아이 워즈 인 뉴 요크 웬 더 크래시 케임.

Original English: No, I did not fall among thieves.
English: no, i did not fall among thieves.
Hindi: नो, आई डिड नॉट फॉल अमंग थीव्ज़.
Korean: 노, 아이 딛 낫 폴 어몽 씨브즈.

Original English: Such things in her brain were like so many oaths on her lips.
English: such things in her brain were like so many oaths on her lips.
Hindi: सच थिंग्स इन हर ब्रेन वेर लाइक सो मैनी ओथ्स ऑन हर लिप्स.
Korean: 서치 띵스 인 허 브레인 워 라이크 소 메니 오쓰 온 허 립스.

Original English: Your being wrecked here has been a godsend to me.
English: your being wrecked here has been a godsend to me.
Hindi: योर बीइंग रेक्ट हियर हैज़ बीन अ गॉडसेंड टू मी.
Korean: 유어 빙 렉트 히어 해즈 빈 아 갓센드 투 미.

Original English: I can't go elsewhere, by your own account.
English: i can not go elsewhere, by your own account.
Hindi: आई कैन नॉट गो एल्सवेयर, बाइ योर ओन अकाउंट.
Korean: 아이 캔 낫 고 엘스웨어, 바이 유어 온 어카운트.

Original English: Her achievements with cocoanuts were a revelation.
English: her achievements with cocoanuts were a revelation.
Hindi: हर अचीवमेंट्स विद कोकोनट्स वर अ रेवलेशन.
Korean: 허 어치브먼츠 위드 코코넛 워 아 레벨레이션.

Original English: He glanced down at her helplessly, and moistened his lips.
English: he glanced down at her helplessly, and moistened his lips.
Hindi: ही ग्लैन्स्ट डाउन ऐट हर हेल्पलेस्ली, ऐंड मॉइस्टन्ड हिज लिप्स.
Korean: 히 글랜스트 다운 앳 허 헬플리슬리, 앤드 모이슨드 히즈 립스.

Original English: That is what distinguishes all of us from the lower animals.
English: that is what distinguishes all of us from the lower animals.
Hindi: धैट इज़ वट डिस्टिंग्विश ऑल अव अस फ्रम द लोअर ऐनिमल्स.
Korean: 댓 이즈 왓 디스팅귀시즈 올 어브 어스 프롬 더 로우어 애니멀즈.

Original English: Idealism led him to philosophic anarchy, and his family threw him off.
English: idealism led him to philosophic anarchy, and his family threw him off.
Hindi: आईडीअलिज़म लेड हिम टू फिलॉसॉफिक अनार्की, एंड हिस फैमिली थ्रू हिम ऑफ.
Korean: 아이디얼리즘 레드 힘 투 필로소픽 애나키, 앤드 히즈 패밀리 쓰루 힘 오프.

Original English: He also contended that better confidence was established by carrying no weapons.
English: he also contended that better confidence was established by carrying no weapons.
Hindi: ही ऑल्सो कन्तेंडेड दैट बेटर कॉन्फिडेंस वज एस्टैब्लिश्ड बाय कैरीइंग नो वेपन्स.
Korean: 히 알소 컨텐디드 댓 베러 컨피던스 워즈 이스태블리쉬트 바이 캐링 노 웨폰즈.

Original English: Outsiders are allowed five minute speeches, the sick man urged.
English: outsiders are allowed five minute speeches, the sick man urged.
Hindi: आउटसाइडर्स आर अलाउड फाइव मिनट स्पीचेस, द सिक मैन अर्ज्ड.
Korean: 아웃사이더즈 아르 알라우드 파이브 미니트 스피치스, 더 식 맨 어지드.

Original English: So was Packard's finish suicide.
English: so was packard's finish suicide.
Hindi: सो वज़ पैकर्ड्स फिनिश सुइसाइड.
Korean: 소 워즈 팩커즈 피니쉬 수이사이드.

Original English: Joan cried, with shining eyes.
English: joan cried, with shining eyes.
Hindi: जोन क्राइड, विथ शाइनिंग आइज़.
Korean: 존 크라이드, 위드 샤이닝 아이즈.

Original English: Nobody knows how the natives got them.
English: nobody knows how the natives got them.
Hindi: नोबडी नोज़ हाऊ द नेटिव्स गॉट धेम.
Korean: 노바디 노즈 하우 더 네이티브즈 갓 뎀.

Original English: How can you manage all alone, Mr Young.
English: how can you manage all alone, mister young.
Hindi: हाउ कैन यू मैनेज ऑल अलोन, मिस्टर यंग.
Korean: 하우 캔 유 매니지 올 알론, 미스터 영.

Original English: The planters are already considering the matter.
English: the planters are already considering the matter.
Hindi: द प्लैन्टर्स आर ऑलरेडी कंसिडरिंग द मैटर.
Korean: 더 플랜터즈 아 올레디 컨시더링 더 매터.

Original English: I use great trouble advisedly.
English: i use great trouble advisedly.
Hindi: आई यूज़ ग्रेट ट्रबल एडवाइजड्ली.
Korean: 아이 유스 그레이트 트러블 어드바이즈드리.

Original English: Dear Sir, Your second victim has fallen on schedule time.
English: dear sir, your second victim has fallen on schedule time.
Hindi: डियर सर, योर सेकंड विक्टिम हैस फॉलन ऑन शेड्यूल टाइम.
Korean: 디어 서, 유어 세컨드 빅팀 해즈 폴른 온 스케줄 타임.

Original English: We leave the eventuality to time and law.
English: we leave the eventuality to time and law.
Hindi: वी लीव दि इवेंट्चुअॅलिटी टू टाइम ऐंड लॉ.
Korean: 위 리브 디 이벤츄얼리티 투 타임 앤드 로.

Original English: I also understand that similar branch organizations have made their appearance in Europe.
English: i also understand that similar branch organizations have made their appearance in europe.
Hindi: आई ऑल्सो अंडरस्टैंड दैट सिमिलर ब्रांच ऑर्गनाइजेशंस हैव मेड देयर अपीरेंस इन यूरोप.
Korean: 아이 올소 언더스탠드 댓 시밀러 브랜치 오르가나이제이션즈 해브 메이드 데어 어피어런스 인 유럽.

Original English: Society is shaken to its foundations.
English: society is shaken to its foundations.
Hindi: सोसाइटी इस शेकन टू इट्स फाउंडेशन्स.
Korean: 소사이어티 이즈 쉐이컨 투 잇츠 파운데이션즈.

Original English: A month in Australia would finish me.
English: a month in australia would finish me.
Hindi: अ मन्थ इन ऑस्ट्रेलिया वुड फिनिश मी.
Korean: 아 먼스 인 오스트레일리아 우드 피니시 미.

Original English: Down through the perfume weighted air fluttered the snowy fluffs of the cottonwoods.
English: down through the perfume weighted air fluttered the snowy fluffs of the cottonwoods.
Hindi: डाउन थ्रू द परफ्यूम वेटेड एयर फ्लटरड द स्नोई फ्लफ्स ऑव द कॉटनवुड्स.
Korean: 다운 쓰루 더 퍼퓸 웨이티드 에어 플러터드 더 스노위 플러프스 어브 더 코튼우즈.

Original English: You were destroying my life.
English: you were destroying my life.
Hindi: यू वेर डिस्ट्रॉइंग माय लाइफ.
Korean: 유 워 디스트로잉 마이 라이프.

Original English: Horses and rifles had been her toys, camp and trail her nursery.
English: horses and rifles had been her toys, camp and trail her nursery.
Hindi: हॉर्सेस एंड राइफल्स हैड बीन हर टॉइज, कैंप एंड ट्रेल हर नर्सरी.
Korean: 호스 앤드 라이플스 해드 빈 허 토이즈, 캠프 앤드 트레일 허 너서리.

Original English: I'm as good as a man, she urged.
English: i am as good as a man, she urged.
Hindi: आई ऐम ऐज गुड ऐज अ मैन, शी अर्ज्ड.
Korean: 아이 앰 애즈 굿 애즈 아 맨, 시 어지드.

Original English: You read the quotations in today's paper.
English: you read the quotations in today's paper.
Hindi: यू रीड द कोटेशन्स इन टुडे'स पेपर.
Korean: 유 리드 더 쿼테이션즈 인 투데이즈 페이퍼.

Original English: He's terribly touchy about his black wards, as he calls them.
English: he's terribly touchy about his black wards, as he calls them.
Hindi: हीज़ टेरेबली टची अबाउट हिज़ ब्लैक वॉर्ड्स, ऐज़ ही कॉल्स देम.
Korean: 히즈 테러블리 터치 어바웃 히즈 블랙 워즈, 애즈 히 콜즈 뎀.

Original English: Whatever he guessed he locked away in the taboo room of Naomi.
English: whatever he guessed he locked away in the taboo room of naomi.
Hindi: व्हटएव ही गेस्ट ही लॉक्ट अवे इन द टैबू रूम ऑफ नाओमी.
Korean: 왓에버 히 게스트 히 락트 어웨이 인 더 타부 룸 오브 나오미.

Original English: This is eighteen eighty.
English: this is eighteen eighty.
Hindi: दिस इज एटीन ऐटी.
Korean: 디스 이즈 에이틴 에이리.

Original English: Death is and has been ever since old Maui died.
English: death is and has been ever since old maui died.
Hindi: डेथ इस एंड हैज़ बीन एवर सिंस ओल्ड माउई डाइड.
Korean: 데스 이즈 앤드 해즈 빈 에버 신스 올드 마우이 다이드.

Original English: Some boy, she laughed acquiescence.
English: some boy, she laughed acquiescence.
Hindi: सम बॉय, शी लाफ्ड अक्विसेन्स.
Korean: 썸 보이, 쉬 래프드 애퀴에센스.

Original English: Let us talk it over and find a way out.
English: let us talk it over and find a way out.
Hindi: लेट अस टॉक इट ओवर ऐंड फाइंड अ वे आउट.
Korean: 렛 어스 톡 잇 오버 앤드 파인드 아 웨이 아웃.

Original English: It is a good property, and worth more than that.
English: it is a good property, and worth more than that.
Hindi: इट इस अ गुड प्रॉपर्टी, ऐंड वर्थ मोर धन धैट.
Korean: 잇 이즈 아 굿 프라퍼티, 앤드 워스 모어 댄 댓.

Original English: I wish you were more adaptable, Joan retorted.
English: i wish you were more adaptable, joan retorted.
Hindi: आई विश यू वर मोर अडैप्टेबल, जोअन रिटॉर्टेड.
Korean: 아이 위시 유 워 모어 어댑터블, 조안 리토티드.

Original English: Such is my passage engaged on the steamer.
English: such is my passage engaged on the steamer.
Hindi: सच इज़ माई पासेज एंगेज्ड ऑन द स्टीमर.
Korean: 서치 이즈 마이 패시지 엔게이지드 안 더 스티머.

Original English: The issue was not in doubt.
English: the issue was not in doubt.
Hindi: दि इश्यू वस नाट इन डाउट.
Korean: 디 이슈 워즈 낫 인 다우트.

Original English: Well, there are better men in Hawaii, that's all.
English: well, there are better men in hawaii, that's all.
Hindi: वेल, देर आर बेटर मेन इन हवाई, दैट्स ऑल.
Korean: 웰, 데어 아 베터 멘 인 하와이, 댓츠 올.

Original English: Harry Bancroft, Dave lied.
English: harry bancroft, dave lied.
Hindi: हैरी बैंकरॉफ्ट, डेव लाइड.
Korean: 해리 뱅크로프트, 데이브 라이드.

Original English: It's a Yankee, Joan cried.
English: it's a yankee, joan cried.
Hindi: इट्स अ यांकी, जोन क्राइड.
Korean: 잇츠 아 양키, 조운 크라이드.

Original English: He was the leader, and Tudor was his lieutenant.
English: he was the leader, and tudor was his lieutenant.
Hindi: ही वज़ द लीडर, एंड ट्यूडर वज़ हिज़ लूटेनेंट.
Korean: 히 워즈 더 리더, 앤드 튜더 워즈 히즈 루테넌트.

Original English: They likewise are disinclined to being eaten.
English: they likewise are disinclined to being eaten.
Hindi: दे लाइकवाइज आर डिसिन्क्लाइंड टू बीइंग ईटन.
Korean: 데이 라이크와이즈 아르 디스인클라인드 투 빙 이튼.

Original English: But to culture the Revolution thus far had exhausted the Junta.
English: but to culture the revolution thus far had exhausted the junta.
Hindi: बट टू कल्चर द रेवोल्यूशन दस फार हैड एग्जॉस्टेड द जुंटा.
Korean: 벗 투 컬처 더 레볼루션 더스 파 해드 이그조스티드 더 준타.

Original English: The President of the United States was his friend.
English: the president of the united states was his friend.
Hindi: द प्रेज़िडेंट ऑफ द यूनाइटेड स्टेट्स वज़ हिज़ फ्रेंड.
Korean: 더 프레지던트 어브 더 유나이티드 스테이츠 워즈 히즈 프렌드.

Original English: Your face was the personification of duplicity.
English: your face was the personification of duplicity.
Hindi: योर फेस वज द पर्सनिफिकेशन अव डुप्लिसिटी.
Korean: 유어 페이스 워즈 더 퍼서니피케이션 어브 듀플리시티.

Original English: Shorty turned to their employers.
English: shorty turned to their employers.
Hindi: शॉर्टी टर्न्ड टू देर एम्प्लॉयर्स.
Korean: 쇼티 턴드 투 데어 엠플로이어즈.

Original English: You were engaged.
English: you were engaged.
Hindi: यू वेर एंगेज्ड.
Korean: 유 워 엔게이지드.

Original English: I saw it all myself, and it was splendid.
English: i saw it all myself, and it was splendid.
Hindi: आई सॉ इट ऑल मायसेल्फ, ऐंड इट वज़ स्प्लेंडिड.
Korean: 아이 쏘 잇 올 마이셀프, 앤드 잇 워즈 스플렌디드.

Original English: Now run along, and tell them to hurry.
English: now run along, and tell them to hurry.
Hindi: नाउ रन अलॉन्ग, एंड टेल देम टू हुरी.
Korean: 나우 런 알롱, 앤드 텔 뎀 투 허리.

Original English: What's that grub-thief got to do with it.
English: what's that grub-thief got to do with it.
Hindi: वट्स दॅट ग्रबथीफ गॉट टू डू विथ इट.
Korean: 왓츠 댓 그럽시프 갓 투 두 위드 잇.

Original English: It was a superb picture.
English: it was a superb picture.
Hindi: इट वस अ सुपर्ब पिक्चर.
Korean: 잇 워즈 아 수퍼브 픽처.

Original English: So she said, the irate skipper dashed on.
English: so she said, the irate skipper dashed on.
Hindi: सो शी सेड, दि आइरेट स्किपर डैश्ट ऑन.
Korean: 소 시 셋, 디 아이레이트 스키퍼 대쉬드 온.

Original English: And watch out for wet feet, was his parting advice.
English: and watch out for wet feet, was his parting advice.
Hindi: एंड वॉच आउट फॉर वेट फीट, वज़ हिज़ पार्टिंग एडवाइस.
Korean: 앤드 와치 아웃 포 웻 핏, 워즈 히즈 파링 어드바이스.

Original English: Raoul yelled, in order to make himself heard.
English: raoul yelled, in order to make himself heard.
Hindi: राउल येल्ड, इन ऑर्डर टू मेक हिम्सेल्फ हर्ड.
Korean: 라울 옐드, 인 오더 투 메이크 힘셀프 허드.

Original English: Oolong was two hundred and fifty miles from the nearest land.
English: oolong was two hundred and fifty miles from the nearest land.
Hindi: ऊलांग वज टू हंड्रेड ऐन्ड फिफ्टी माइल्स फ्रम द नियरेस्ट लैंड.
Korean: 울랑 워즈 투 헌드레드 앤드 피프티 마일즈 프롬 더 니어리스트 랜드.

Original English: They just lay off in the bush and plugged away.
English: they just lay off in the bush and plugged away.
Hindi: थे जस्ट ले ऑफ इन द बुश एंड प्लग्ड अवे.
Korean: 데이 저스트 레이 오프 인 더 부쉬 앤드 플러그드 어웨이.

Original English: The very thought of the effort to swim over was nauseating.
English: the very thought of the effort to swim over was nauseating.
Hindi: द वेरी थॉट अव दि एफर्ट टू स्विम ओवर वज़ नॉसिएटिंग.
Korean: 더 베리 쏫 어브 디 에퍼트 투 스윔 오버 워즈 노시에이팅.

Original English: And there was a dog that barked.
English: and there was a dog that barked.
Hindi: ऐंड देर वस अ डॉग दैट बार्क्ड.
Korean: 앤드 데어 워즈 아 도그 댓 바크트.

Original English: There are four, all low, McCoy answered.
English: there are four, all low, mccoy answered.
Hindi: देर आर फोर, ऑल लो, मकॉय ऐन्सर्ड.
Korean: 데어 아르 포, 올 로우, 맥코이 앤서드.

Original English: The women they carried away with them to the Big Valley.
English: the women they carried away with them to the big valley.
Hindi: द विमन दे कैरेड अवे विथ देम टू द बिग वैली.
Korean: 더 위민 데이 캐리드 어웨이 위드 뎀 투 더 빅 밸리.

Original English: The Japanese understood as we could never school ourselves or hope to understand.
English: the japanese understood as we could never school ourselves or hope to understand.
Hindi: द जापानीज़ अंडरस्टूड ऐज़ वी कुड नेवर स्कूल आउर्सेल्वज़ ऑर होप टू अंडरस्टैंड.
Korean: 더 자패니즈 언더스투드 애즈 위 쿧 네버 스쿨 아워셀브즈 오어 호프 투 언더스탠드.

Original English: They had been on the same lay as ourselves.
English: they had been on the same lay as ourselves.
Hindi: थे हैड बीन ऑन द सेम ले अस आइउर्सेल्व्ज़.
Korean: 데이 해드 빈 온 더 세임 레이 애즈 아우어셀브즈.

Original English: You are positively soulless, he said savagely.
English: you are positively soulless, he said savagely.
Hindi: यू आर पॉज़िटिवली सोललेस, ही सैड सेवेजली.
Korean: 유 아 포지티블리 소울레스, 히 세드 새비지리.

Original English: Harrison is still my chauffeur.
English: harrison is still my chauffeur.
Hindi: हैरिसन इज स्टिल माई शोफर.
Korean: 해리슨 이즈 스틸 마이 쇼퍼.

Original English: The boy grew and prospered.
English: the boy grew and prospered.
Hindi: द बॉय ग्रू एंड प्रॉस्पर्ड.
Korean: 더 보이 그루 앤드 프로스퍼드.

Original English: He wanted to give the finish to this foe already so far gone.
English: he wanted to give the finish to this foe already so far gone.
Hindi: ही वांटेड टू गिव द फिनिश टू दिस फो ऑलरेडी सो फार गॉन.
Korean: 히 원티드 투 기브 더 피니쉬 투 디스 포 올레디 소 파 곤.

Original English: Exciting times are the lot of the fish patrol.
English: exciting times are the lot of the fish patrol.
Hindi: एक्साइटिंग टाइम्स आर द लॉट ऑफ द फिश पैट्रोल.
Korean: 엑사이팅 타임즈 아 더 랏 오브 더 피쉬 패트롤.

Original English: I know they are my oysters.
English: i know they are my oysters.
Hindi: आई नो थे आर माई ऑयस्टर्स.
Korean: 아이 노우 데이 아 마이 오이스터즈.

Original English: By this time Charley was as enraged as the Greek.
English: by this time charley was as enraged as the greek.
Hindi: बाई दिस टाइम चार्ली वज़ ऐज एनरेज्ड ऐज द ग्रीक.
Korean: 바이 디스 타임 찰리 워즈 애즈 엔레이지드 애즈 더 그릭.

Original English: They must have been swept away by the chaotic currents.
English: they must have been swept away by the chaotic currents.
Hindi: थे मस्ट हैव बीन स्वेप्ट अवे बाई द केऑटिक करेंट्स.
Korean: 데이 머스트 해브 빈 스웹트 어웨이 바이 더 카오틱 커런츠.

Original English: It resembled tea less than lager beer resembles champagne.
English: it resembled tea less than lager beer resembles champagne.
Hindi: इट रिसेम्बल्ड टी लेस धन लागर बीर रिसेम्बल्स शैम्पेन.
Korean: 잇 리셈벌드 티 레스 댄 라거 비어 리셈블즈 샴페인.

Original English: The very opposite is true; they are discouraged vagabonds.
English: the very opposite is true they are discouraged vagabonds.
Hindi: द वेरी आपॉसित इस ट्रू दै आर डिस्करिज्ड वैगाबॉन्ड्स.
Korean: 더 베리 어포짓 이즈 트루 데이 아르 디스커리지드 배거본즈.

Original English: At the same time spears and arrows began to fall among the invaders.
English: at the same time spears and arrows began to fall among the invaders.
Hindi: ऐट द सेम टाइम स्पियर्स ऐंड ऐरोज़ बिगैन टू फॉल अमंग दि इन्वेडर्स.
Korean: 앳 더 세임 타임 스피어즈 앤드 애로우즈 비갠 투 폴 어몽 디 인베이더즈.

Original English: Then, again, Tudor had such an irritating way about him.
English: then, again, tudor had such an irritating way about him.
Hindi: धेन, अगेन, ट्यूडर हैड सच अन इरिटेटिंग वे अबाउट हिम.
Korean: 덴, 어겐, 튜더 해드 서치 안 이리테이팅 웨이 어바웃 힘.

Original English: Outwardly, he maintained a calm and smiling aspect.
English: outwardly, he maintained a calm and smiling aspect.
Hindi: आउटवर्डली, ही मेन्टेन्ड अ काम ऐंड स्माइलिंग ऐस्पेक्ट.
Korean: 아웃워들리, 히 메인테인드 아 캄 앤드 스마일링 애스펙트.

Original English: Tudor surveyed him with withering disgust.
English: tudor surveyed him with withering disgust.
Hindi: ट्यूडर सर्वेड हिम विथ विथरिंग डिसगस्ट.
Korean: 튜더 서베이드 힘 위드 위더링 디스거스트.

Original English: You fired me out of your house, in short.
English: you fired me out of your house, in short.
Hindi: यू फायर्ड मी आउट अव योर हाउस, इन शॉर्ट.
Korean: 유 파이어드 미 아웃 어브 유어 하우스, 인 숏.

Original English: Her mouth opened, but instead of speaking she drew a long sigh.
English: her mouth opened, but instead of speaking she drew a long sigh.
Hindi: हेर माउथ ओपेंड, बट इन्स्टेड अव स्पीकिंग शी ड्रू अ लॉन्ग साइ.
Korean: 허 마우스 오픈드, 벗 인스테드 어브 스피킹 쉬 드루 아 롱 사이.

Original English: It's worth eight dollars.
English: it's worth eight dollars.
Hindi: इट्स वर्थ एट डॉलर.
Korean: 잇츠 워스 에잇 달러즈.

Original English: And he did hurt my arm.
English: and he did hurt my arm.
Hindi: ऐंड ही डिड हर्ट माई आर्म.
Korean: 앤드 히 딛 허트 마이 암.

Original English: Saxon's onto her job.
English: saxon's onto her job.
Hindi: सैक्सन्स आंतु हर जॉब.
Korean: 섹슨즈 온투 허 잡.

Original English: Only once did I confide the strangeness of it all to another.
English: only once did i confide the strangeness of it all to another.
Hindi: ओनली वन्स डिड आई कन्फाइड द स्ट्रेंजनेस अव इट ऑल टू अनदर.
Korean: 온리 원스 디드 아이 컨파이드 더 스트레인지니스 어브 잇 올 투 어나더.

Original English: But this time it was Saxon who rebelled.
English: but this time it was saxon who rebelled.
Hindi: बट दिस टाइम इट वज सैक्सन हू रिबेल्ड.
Korean: 벗 디스 타임 잇 워즈 섹슨 후 리벨드.

Original English: I was not to cry out in the face of fear.
English: i was not to cry out in the face of fear.
Hindi: आई वज नॉट टू क्राई आउट इन द फेस अव फियर.
Korean: 아이 워즈 낫 투 크라이 아웃 인 더 페이스 어브 피어.

Original English: And now put yourself in my place for a moment.
English: and now put yourself in my place for a moment.
Hindi: एंड नाऊ पुट योर्सेल्फ इन माय प्लेस फॉर अ मोमेंट.
Korean: 앤드 나우 풋 유어셀프 인 마이 플레이스 포어 아 모먼트.

Original English: The boy threw back his head with pride.
English: the boy threw back his head with pride.
Hindi: द बॉय थ्रू बैक हिज़ हेड विथ प्राइड.
Korean: 더 보이 스루 백 히즈 헤드 위드 프라이드.

Original English: Saxon nodded, and the boy frowned.
English: saxon nodded, and the boy frowned.
Hindi: सैक्सन नॉडेड, ऐंड द बॉय फ्राउन्ड.
Korean: 색슨 나디드, 앤드 더 보이 프라운드.

Original English: Why not like any railroad station or ferry depot.
English: why not like any railroad station or ferry depot.
Hindi: वाई नाट लाइक एनी रेलरोड स्टेशन ऑर फेरी डीपो.
Korean: 와이 낫 라이크 에니 레일로드 스테이션 오어 페리 디포.

Original English: We could throw stones with our feet.
English: we could throw stones with our feet.
Hindi: वी कुड थ्रो स्टोन्स विथ आउर फीट.
Korean: 위 쿨드 스로우 스톤즈 위드 아워 피트.

Original English: It was put together in a casual, helter-skelter sort of way.
English: it was put together in a casual, helter-skelter sort of way.
Hindi: इट वज़ पुट टुगेदर इन अ कैजुअल, हेल्टर-स्केल्टर सॉर्ट अव वे.
Korean: 잇 워즈 풋 투게더 인 아 캐주얼, 헬터스켈터 솟 업 웨이.

Original English: These were merely stout sticks an inch or so in diameter.
English: these were merely stout sticks an inch or so in diameter.
Hindi: दीज वर मेरली स्टाउट स्टिक्स अन इंच ऑर सो इन डायमीटर.
Korean: 디즈 워 미얼리 스타우트 스틱스 안 인치 오어 소 인 다이아미터.

Original English: Then it was that a strange thing happened.
English: then it was that a strange thing happened.
Hindi: देन इट वज़ धैट अ स्ट्रेंज थिंग हैपनड.
Korean: 덴 잇 워즈 댓 아 스트레인지 띵 해펜드.

Original English: From the source of light a harsh voice said.
English: from the source of light a harsh voice said.
Hindi: फ्रॉम द सोर्स अव लाइट अ हर्ष वॉइस सैड.
Korean: 프럼 더 소스 어브 라이트 아 하쉬 보이스 세드.

Original English: But I did not enjoy it long.
English: but i did not enjoy it long.
Hindi: बट आई डिड नॉट एन्जॉय इट लॉन्ग.
Korean: 벗 아이 딛 낫 엔조이 잇 롱.

Original English: We were now good friends.
English: we were now good friends.
Hindi: वी वर नाऊ गुड फ्रेंड्स.
Korean: 위 워 나우 굿 프렌즈.

Original English: Two of the Folk were already up.
English: two of the folk were already up.
Hindi: टू अव द फोक वर ऑलरेडी अप.
Korean: 투 어브 더 포크 워 올레디 업.

Original English: Now animals do not like mockery.
English: now animals do not like mockery.
Hindi: नाउ ऐनिमल्स डू नाट लाइक मॉकरी.
Korean: 나우 애니멀즈 두 낫 라이크 모커리.

Original English: He gave one last snarl and slid from view among the trees.
English: he gave one last snarl and slid from view among the trees.
Hindi: ही गेव वन लास्ट स्नार्ल एंड स्लिड फ्रम व्यू अमंग द ट्रीज.
Korean: 히 게이브 원 라스트 스날 앤드 슬리드 프럼 뷰 어몽 더 트리즈.

Original English: Again the girls applauded, and Mrs Hall cried.
English: again the girls applauded, and missus hall cried.
Hindi: अगैन द गर्ल्स अप्लॉडेड, ऐंड मिसस हॉल क्राइड.
Korean: 어겐 더 걸즈 어플로디드, 앤드 미써스 홀 크라이드.

Original English: Just the same I'd sooner be myself than have book indigestion.
English: just the same i would sooner be myself than have book indigestion.
Hindi: जस्ट द सेम आई वुड सूनर बी मायसेल्फ धन हैव बुक इन्डिजेशन.
Korean: 저스트 더 세임 아이 우드 수너 비 마이셀프 댄 해브 북 인디제스천.

Original English: Some of the smaller veins had doubtless been ruptured.
English: some of the smaller veins had doubtless been ruptured.
Hindi: सम अव द स्मालर वेन्स हैड डाउटलेस बीन रप्चर्ड.
Korean: 썸 업 더 스몰러 베인즈 해드 다우트레스 빈 럽처드.

Original English: But we were without this momentum.
English: but we were without this momentum.
Hindi: बट वी वर विदाउट दिस मोमेंटम.
Korean: 벗 위 워 위다웃 디스 모멘텀.

Original English: There was one difficulty, however.
English: there was one difficulty, however.
Hindi: देर वज़ वन डिफिकल्टी, हावेवर.
Korean: 데어 워즈 원 디피컬티, 하우에버.

Original English: The hyena proceeded to dine.
English: the hyena proceeded to dine.
Hindi: द हैना प्रोसीडेड टू डाइन.
Korean: 더 하이에나 프로시디드 투 다인.

Original English: The time was considered auspicious.
English: the time was considered auspicious.
Hindi: द टाइम वज़ कंसिडर्ड ऑस्पिशस.
Korean: 더 타임 워즈 컨시더드 오스피셔스.

Original English: Or have they already devised one.
English: or have they already devised one.
Hindi: ऑर हैव दे ऑलरेडी डिवाइज़्ड वन.
Korean: 오어 헤브 데이 올레디 디바이즈드 원.

Original English: We would not spend another such night.
English: we would not spend another such night.
Hindi: वी वुड नॉट स्पेंड अनदर सच नाइट.
Korean: 위 우드 낫 스펜드 어나더 서치 나잇.

Original English: At first his progress was slow and erratic.
English: at first his progress was slow and erratic.
Hindi: ऐट फर्स्ट हिज़ प्रोग्रेस वज़ स्लो ऐंड एरेटिक.
Korean: 앳 퍼스트 히즈 프로그레스 워즈 슬로우 앤드 에라틱.

Original English: He placed his paw on one, and its movements were accelerated.
English: he placed his paw on one, and its movements were accelerated.
Hindi: ही प्लेस्ट हिज़ पॉ ऑन वन, ऐंड इट्स मूवमेंट्स वर एक्सेलरेटेड.
Korean: 히 플레이스트 히즈 포 안 원, 앤드 잇츠 무브먼츠 워 액셀러레이티드.

Original English: The awe of man rushed over him again.
English: the awe of man rushed over him again.
Hindi: दि ऑ अव मैन रश्ट ओवर हिम अगेन.
Korean: 디 오 어브 맨 러쉬트 오버 힘 어겐.

Original English: The Fire-Men wore animal skins around their waists and across their shoulders.
English: the fire-men wore animal skins around their waists and across their shoulders.
Hindi: द फायरमेन वोर ऐनिमल स्किन्स अराउंड देर वेस्ट्स एंड अक्रॉस देर शोल्डर्स.
Korean: 더 파이어맨 워 애니멀 스킨즈 어라운드 데어 웨이스트 앤드 어크로스 데어 숄더즈.

Original English: Between him and all domestic animals there must be no hostilities.
English: between him and all domestic animals there must be no hostilities.
Hindi: बिटवीन हिम एंड ऑल डोमेस्टिक ऐनिमल्स देर मस्ट बी नो होस्टिलिटीज़.
Korean: 비트윈 힘 앤드 올 도메스틱 애니멀스 데어 머스트 비 노 호스틸리티즈.

Original English: For a much longer time Lop-Ear and I remained and watched.
English: for a much longer time lop-ear and i remained and watched.
Hindi: फॉर अ मच लॉन्गर टाइम लॉप-ईर ऐंड आई रिमेन्ड ऐंड वॉच्ड.
Korean: 포어 아 머치 롱거 타임 랍이얼 앤드 아이 리메인드 앤드 와치드.

Original English: All right, Sir, replied Jock with great regret.
English: all right, sir, replied jock with great regret.
Hindi: ऑल राइट, सर, रिप्लाइड जॉक विद ग्रेट रेग्रेट.
Korean: 올 라잇, 서, 리플라이드 조크 위드 그레이트 리그렛.

Original English: At times I wondered where Sir Archibald got his style.
English: at times i wondered where sir archibald got his style.
Hindi: ऐट टाइम्स आई वंडर्ड वेयर सर आर्चिबॉल्ड गॉट हिज़ स्टाइल.
Korean: 앳 타임즈 아이 원더드 웨어 서 아치볼드 갓 히즈 스타일.

Original English: Why should a fellow throw up the sponge after the first round.
English: why should a fellow throw up the sponge after the first round.
Hindi: वाय शुड अ फेलो थ्रो अप द स्पंज आफ्टर द फर्स्ट राउंड.
Korean: 와이 슛 아 펠로우 스로우 업 더 스펀지 애프터 더 퍼스트 라운드.

Original English: His hand shot out and clutched Crooked-Leg by the neck.
English: his hand shot out and clutched crooked-leg by the neck.
Hindi: हिस हैंड शॉट आउट ऐंड क्लच्ड क्रुकिड-लेग बाई द नेक.
Korean: 히즈 핸드 샷 아웃 앤드 클러치드 크룩킷레그 바이 더 넥.

Original English: Miss Brodie's smile was slightly sarcastic.
English: miss brodie's smile was slightly sarcastic.
Hindi: मिस ब्रोडीज़ स्माइल वज़ स्लाइटली सार्कैस्टिक.
Korean: 미스 브로디스 스마일 워즈 슬라잇리 사카스틱.

Original English: Does the old boy often go off at half-cock that way.
English: does the old boy often go off at half-cock that way.
Hindi: डज दि ओल्ड बॉय ऑफन गो ऑफ ऐट हैफ्कॉक दैट वे.
Korean: 더즈 디 올드 보이 오픈 고 오프 앳 헤프콕 댓 웨이.

Original English: A flying arrow passed between us.
English: a flying arrow passed between us.
Hindi: अ फ्लाइंग ऐरो पैस्ट बिटवीन अस.
Korean: 아 플라잉 애로우 패스트 비트윈 어스.

Original English: I pulled, suddenly, with all my might.
English: i pulled, suddenly, with all my might.
Hindi: आई पुल्ड, सडनली, विथ ऑल माई माइट.
Korean: 아이 풀드, 서든리, 위드 올 마이 마이트.

Original English: Here we allow our solicitors to look after our legal work.
English: here we allow our solicitors to look after our legal work.
Hindi: हीर वी अलाउ आऊर सॉलिसिटर्स टू लुक आफ्टर आऊर लीगल वर्क.
Korean: 히어 위 얼라우 아우어 솔리시터즈 투 룩 애프터 아우어 리걸 워크.

Original English: His previous wives had never lived long enough to bear him children.
English: his previous wives had never lived long enough to bear him children.
Hindi: हिस प्रीवियस वाइव्ज़ हैड नेवर लिव्ड लॉंग इनफ टू बेअर हिम चिल्ड्रन.
Korean: 히즈 프리비어스 와이브스 해드 네버 리브드 롱 이너프 투 베어 힘 칠드런.

Original English: It was our river emerging like ourselves from the great swamp.
English: it was our river emerging like ourselves from the great swamp.
Hindi: इट वस आउर रिवर इमर्जिंग लाइक आउर्सेल्व्स फ्रम द ग्रेट स्वाम्प.
Korean: 잇 워즈 아우어 리버 이머징 라이크 아우셀브즈 프럼 더 그레이트 스왐프.

Original English: Cameron looked at his hands with their long, sinewy fingers.
English: cameron looked at his hands with their long, sinewy fingers.
Hindi: कैमरन लुक्ट ऐट हिस हैंड्स विथ देर लॉन्ग, सिन्यूई फिंगर्स.
Korean: 카메런 룩트 앳 히즈 핸즈 위드 데어 롱, 시뉴이 핑거즈.

Original English: We got few vegetables and fruits, and became fish eaters.
English: we got few vegetables and fruits, and became fish eaters.
Hindi: वी गॉट फ्यू वेजिटेबल्स एंड फ्रूट्स, एंड बिकेम फिश ईटर्स.
Korean: 위 갓 퓨 베지터블스 앤드 프루츠, 앤드 비케임 피쉬 이터즈.

Original English: We never made another migration.
English: we never made another migration.
Hindi: वी नेवर मेड अनदर माइग्रेशन.
Korean: 위 네버 메이드 어나더 마이그레이션.

Original English: Nor was Elam Harnish an exception.
English: nor was elam harnish an exception.
Hindi: नॉर वज़ इलैम हार्निश अन एक्सेप्शन.
Korean: 노어 워즈 일램 하니쉬 안 엑셉션.

Original English: A little treatment, massage, with some help from the doctor.
English: a little treatment, massage, with some help from the doctor.
Hindi: अ लिटल ट्रीटमेंट, मसाज, विद सम हेल्प फ्रॉम द डॉक्टर.
Korean: 아 리틀 트리트먼트, 마사지, 위드 썸 헬프 프롬 더 닥터.

Original English: The 29th very foggy.
English: the 29th very foggy.
Hindi: द ट्वेन्टी-नाइन्थ वेरी फॉगी.
Korean: 더 트웬티나인쓰 베리 포기.

Original English: Dig in; you're sure good, was Daylight's answer.
English: dig in you are sure good, was daylight's answer.
Hindi: डिग इन यू आर शुर गुड, वज़ डेलाइट्स ऐंसर.
Korean: 딕 인 유 아 슈어 굿, 워즈 데이라이츠 앤서.

Original English: The apron string loomed near and he shied like an unbroken colt.
English: the apron string loomed near and he shied like an unbroken colt.
Hindi: दि एप्रन स्ट्रिंग लूम्ड निअर ऐंड ही शाइड लाइक अन अनब्रोकन कोल्ट.
Korean: 디 에이프론 스트링 룸드 니어 앤드 히 샤이드 라이크 안 언브로큰 콜트.

Original English: He had been born with this endowment.
English: he had been born with this endowment.
Hindi: ही हैड बीन बॉर्न विद धिस एंडाउमेंट.
Korean: 히 해드 빈 본 위드 디스 엔다우먼트.

Original English: And this was their sole conversation throughout the meal.
English: and this was their sole conversation throughout the meal.
Hindi: ऐंड दिस वज़ धेर सोल कन्वर्सेशन थ्रूआउट द मील.
Korean: 앤드 디스 워즈 데어 솔 컨버세이션 쓰루아웃 더 밀.

Original English: Though the aurora still flamed, another day had begun.
English: though the aurora still flamed, another day had begun.
Hindi: दो दि औरोरा स्टिल फ्लेम्ड, अनदर डे हैड बिगन.
Korean: 도 디 오로라 스틸 플레임드, 어나더 데이 해드 비건.

Original English: He did not believe in the burning of daylight for such a luxury.
English: he did not believe in the burning of daylight for such a luxury.
Hindi: ही डिड नॉट बिलीव इन द बर्निंग अव डेलाइट फॉर सच अ लक्ज़री.
Korean: 히 딛 낫 빌리브 인 더 버닝 오브 데이라이트 포 서치 아 럭셔리.

Original English: Again he had done the big thing.
English: again he had done the big thing.
Hindi: अगेन ही हैड डन द बिग थिंग.
Korean: 어게인 히 해드 던 더 빅 띵.

Original English: Daylight was tired, profoundly tired.
English: daylight was tired, profoundly tired.
Hindi: डेलाइट वस टायर्ड, प्रफाउंडली टायर्ड.
Korean: 데이라이트 워즈 타이어드, 프로파운들리 타이어드.

Original English: The regret in his voice was provocative of a second burst of laughter.
English: the regret in his voice was provocative of a second burst of laughter.
Hindi: द रिग्रेट इन हिस वॉइस वस प्रवोकटिव अव अ सेकंड बर्स्ट अव लाफ्टर.
Korean: 더 리그렛 인 히즈 보이스 워즈 프로바커티브 오브 아 세컨드 버스트 오브 래프터.

Original English: Instead, he arrived on the night of the second day.
English: instead, he arrived on the night of the second day.
Hindi: इंस्टेड, ही अराइव्ड ऑन द नाइट अव द सेकंड डे.
Korean: 인스테드, 히 어라이브드 온 더 나잇 어브 더 세컨드 데이.

Original English: Their supply of grub was gone.
English: their supply of grub was gone.
Hindi: देर सप्लाई अव ग्रब वस गॉन.
Korean: 데얼 서플라이 어브 그럽 워즈 곤.

Original English: Crickets began to chirp, and more geese and ducks flew overhead.
English: crickets began to chirp, and more geese and ducks flew overhead.
Hindi: क्रिकेट्स बिगैन टू चिरप, ऐंड मोर गीस ऐंड डक्स फ्लू ओवरहेड.
Korean: 크리켓츠 비갠 투 칩, 앤드 모어 기스 앤드 덕스 플루 오버헤드.

Original English: Not till the twentieth of May did the river break.
English: not till the twentieth of may did the river break.
Hindi: नॉट टिल द ट्वेंटीएथ अव मे डिड द रिवर ब्रेक.
Korean: 낫 틸 더 투엔티에쓰 어브 메이 딛 더 리버 브레이크.

Original English: It was a gigantic inadequacy.
English: it was a gigantic inadequacy.
Hindi: इट वज़ अ जायगैंटिक इनैडिक्वेसी.
Korean: 잇 워즈 아 자이갠틱 인애드퀘시.

Original English: Our Mr Howison will call upon you at your hotel.
English: our mister howison will call upon you at your hotel.
Hindi: आउर मिस्टर हाउइसन विल कॉल अपॉन यू ऐट योर होटेल.
Korean: 아워 미스터 하우이슨 윌 콜 어폰 유 앳 유어 호텔.

Original English: He had been so easy.
English: he had been so easy.
Hindi: ही हैड बिन सो ईज़ी.
Korean: 히 핻 빈 소 이지.

Original English: Change chairs, Daylight commanded.
English: change chairs, daylight commanded.
Hindi: चेंज चेयर्स, डेलाइट कमांडेड.
Korean: 체인지 체어즈, 데이라이트 커맨디드.

Original English: I'd sooner have my chips back.
English: i would sooner have my chips back.
Hindi: आई वुड सूनर हैव माई चिप्स बैक.
Korean: 아이 우드 수너 해브 마이 칩스 백.

Original English: They only had a little thirty thousand dollar fire.
English: they only had a little thirty thousand dollar fire.
Hindi: थे ओनली हैड अ लिटल थर्टी थाउज़ंड डॉलर फायर.
Korean: 데이 온리 해드 아 리틀 써티 싸우전드 달러 파이어.

Original English: His partners had starved and died on the Stewart.
English: his partners had starved and died on the stewart.
Hindi: हिस पार्टनर्स हैड स्टार्व्ड ऐंड डाइड ऑन द स्टीवर्ट.
Korean: 히즈 파트너즈 햇 스타브드 앤드 다이드 온 더 스튜어트.

Original English: As to how she dressed, he had no ideas at all.
English: as to how she dressed, he had no ideas at all.
Hindi: ऐस टू हाउ शी ड्रेस्ट, ही हैड नो आइडियाज़ ऐट ऑल.
Korean: 애즈 투 하우 시 드레스트, 히 해드 노 아이디어스 앳 올.

Original English: It does, was her audacious answer.
English: it does, was her audacious answer.
Hindi: इट डज़, वज हर ऑडेशस ऐन्सर.
Korean: 잇 더즈, 워즈 허 오데이셔스 앤서.

Original English: Oh, it's just a novel, a love story.
English: oh, it's just a novel, a love story.
Hindi: ओ, इट्स जस्ट अ नॉवेल, अ लव स्टोरी.
Korean: 오, 잇츠 저스트 아 노블, 아 러브 스토리.

Original English: Whoever lived on the ranch did that.
English: whoever lived on the ranch did that.
Hindi: हूएवर लिव्ड ऑन द रैंच डिड दैट.
Korean: 후에버 리브드 온 더 랜치 디드 댓.

Original English: How old are you, mother.
English: how old are you, mother.
Hindi: हाउ ओल्ड आर यू, मदर.
Korean: 하우 올드 아르 유, 머더.

Original English: Here he got a fresh thrill.
English: here he got a fresh thrill.
Hindi: हीर ही गॉट अ फ्रेश थ्रिल.
Korean: 히어 히 갓 아 프레시 쓰릴.

Original English: It was unobtrusive, yet it was there.
English: it was unobtrusive, yet it was there.
Hindi: इट वज़ अनअबट्रूसिव, येट इट वज़ देर.
Korean: 잇 와즈 언어브트루시브, 옛 잇 와즈 데어.

Original English: Well, I'll be plumb gosh darned.
English: well, i will be plumb gosh darned.
Hindi: वेल, आई विल बी प्लम गॉश डार्न्ड.
Korean: 웰, 아이 윌 비 플럼 가쉬 다른드.

Original English: These quick little joys of hers were sources of joy to him.
English: these quick little joys of hers were sources of joy to him.
Hindi: दीज़ क्विक लिटल जॉइज़ अव हर्स वेर सोर्सिज़ अव जॉय टू हिम.
Korean: 디즈 퀵 리틀 조이즈 오브 허즈 워 소시즈 오브 조이 투 힘.

Original English: I play that choice wide open to win.
English: i play that choice wide open to win.
Hindi: आई प्ले दैट चॉइस वाइड ओपन टू विन.
Korean: 아이 플레이 댓 초이스 와이드 오픈 투 윈.

Original English: Each improvement makes the value of everything else pump up.
English: each improvement makes the value of everything else pump up.
Hindi: ईच इम्प्रूवमेंट मेक्स द वैल्यू अव एवरीथिंग एल्स पम्प अप.
Korean: 이치 임프루브먼트 메익스 더 밸류 어브 에브리씽 엘스 펌프 업.

Original English: But how are you going to do it.
English: but how are you going to do it.
Hindi: बट हाउ आर यू गोइंग टू डू इट.
Korean: 벗 하우 아르 유 고잉 투 두 잇.

Original English: Lots of men take women buggy riding.
English: lots of men take women buggy riding.
Hindi: लॉट्स ऑफ मेन टेक विमेन बगी राइडिंग.
Korean: 라츠 어브 멘 테이크 위민 버기 라이딩.

Original English: Daylight made no answer, and the door closed behind him.
English: daylight made no answer, and the door closed behind him.
Hindi: डेलाइट मेड नो आंसर, ऐंड द डोर क्लोज़्ड बिहाइंड हिम.
Korean: 데이라이트 메이드 노 앤서, 앤드 더 도어 클로즈드 비하인드 힘.

Original English: There's not an iota of truth in it.
English: there's not an iota of truth in it.
Hindi: देरज़ नाट अन आयोरा अव ट्रूथ इन इट.
Korean: 데얼즈 낫 안 아이오타 어브 트루스 인 잇.

Original English: But ever his gaze returned to that Crouched Venus on the piano.
English: but ever his gaze returned to that crouched venus on the piano.
Hindi: बट एवर हिज गैज़ रिटर्न्ड टू दैट क्राउच्ड वीनस ऑन द पियानो.
Korean: 벗 에버 히즈 게이즈 리턴드 투 댓 크라우치드 비너스 온 더 피아노.

Original English: Would you be satisfied with that one hundredth part of me.
English: would you be satisfied with that one hundredth part of me.
Hindi: वुड यू बी सैटिस्फाइड विथ दैट वन हंड्रेडथ पार्ट अव मी.
Korean: 우드 유 비 새티스파이드 위드 댓 원 헌드레드 파트 오브 미.

Original English: In such a tumbling of values was no time to sell.
English: in such a tumbling of values was no time to sell.
Hindi: इन सच अ टम्बलिंग अव वैल्यूज़ वज़ नो टाइम टू सेल.
Korean: 인 서치 아 텀블링 오브 밸류즈 워즈 노 타임 투 셀.

Original English: Stand off butcher and baker and all the rest.
English: stand off butcher and baker and all the rest.
Hindi: स्टैंड ऑफ बुचर ऐंड बेकर ऐंड ऑल द रेस्ट.
Korean: 스탠드 오프 부처 앤드 베이커 앤드 올 더 레스트.

Original English: Matthewson, who's this bookkeeper, Rogers.
English: matthewson, who's this bookkeeper, rogers.
Hindi: मैथ्यूसन, हूज़ दिस बुककीपर, रॉजर्स.
Korean: 매튜슨, 후즈 디스 북키퍼, 로저스.

Original English: Now just what do you want to know.
English: now just what do you want to know.
Hindi: नाउ जस्ट वट डू यू वांट टू नो.
Korean: 나우 저스트 왓 두 유 원트 투 노우.

Original English: I want to know how all this is possible.
English: i want to know how all this is possible.
Hindi: आई वांट टू नो हाउ ऑल दिस इज़ पॉसिबल.
Korean: 아이 원트 투 노우 하우 올 디스 이즈 파서블.

Original English: It's that much junk.
English: it's that much junk.
Hindi: इट्स दैट मच जंक.
Korean: 잇츠 댓 머치 정크.

Original English: There was proper division of labor in the work they individually performed.
English: there was proper division of labor in the work they individually performed.
Hindi: देर वस प्रॉपर डिवीजन अव लेबर इन द वर्क दे इंडिविजुअली परफॉर्म्ड.
Korean: 데어 워즈 프로퍼 디비전 어브 레이버 인 더 워크 데이 인디비쥬얼리 퍼폼드.

Original English: He loved to play Chinese lottery.
English: he loved to play chinese lottery.
Hindi: ही लव्ड टू प्ले चाइनीज़ लॉटरी.
Korean: 히 러브드 투 플레이 차이니즈 로터리.

Original English: The Law of Club and Fang
English: the law of club and fang
Hindi: द लॉ अव क्लब ऐंड फैंग
Korean: 더 로 어브 클럽 앤드 팽

Original English: The temperature dropped to fifty below zero and remained there the whole trip.
English: the temperature dropped to fifty below zero and remained there the whole trip.
Hindi: द टेम्परेचर ड्रॉप्ड टू फिफ्टी बिलो ज़ीरो एंड रिमेंड देर द होल ट्रिप.
Korean: 더 템퍼러처 드랍트 투 피프티 빌로우 제로 앤드 리메인드 데어 더 홀 트립.

Original English: And as never before, he was ready to obey.
English: and as never before, he was ready to obey.
Hindi: ऐंड ऐज़ नेवर बिफोर, ही वज़ रेडी टू ओबे.
Korean: 앤드 애즈 네버 비포, 히 워즈 레디 투 오베이.

Original English: This state of mind comes of an undue prominence of the ego.
English: this state of mind comes of an undue prominence of the ego.
Hindi: थिस स्टेट अव माइंड कम्स अव अन अंडू प्रामिनेंस अव दि ईगो.
Korean: 디스 스테이트 어브 마인드 컴즈 어브 안 언두 프라미넌스 어브 디 이고.

Original English: There are the canals of China, and the Yang-tse River.
English: there are the canals of china, and the yang-tse river.
Hindi: देर आर द कनाल्स अव चाइना, ऐंड द यैंग-सि रिवर.
Korean: 데어 아어 더 커낼즈 어브 차이나, 앤드 더 양츠 리버.

Original English: We threaten to be of the one mind before the voyage is completed.
English: we threaten to be of the one mind before the voyage is completed.
Hindi: वी थ्रेटन टू बी अव द वन माइंड बिफोर द वॉयज इज़ कम्प्लीटेड.
Korean: 위 쓰레튼 투 비 어브 더 원 마인드 비포어 더 보이지 이즈 컴플리티드.

Original English: She was built primarily to sail.
English: she was built primarily to sail.
Hindi: शी वज़ बिल्ट प्राइमरिली टू सेल.
Korean: 쉬 워즈 빌트 프라이머리 투 세일.

Original English: In the Bohemian Club of San Francisco there are some crack sailors.
English: in the bohemian club of san francisco there are some crack sailors.
Hindi: इन द बोहेमियन क्लब अव सैन फ्रान्सिस्को देर आर सम क्रैक सेलर्स.
Korean: 인 더 보헤미안 클럽 어브 산 프란시스코 데어 아 썸 크랙 세일러즈.

Original English: My age, in years, is twenty two.
English: my age, in years, is twenty two.
Hindi: माई एज, इन इयर्स, इज़ ट्वेंटी टू.
Korean: 마이 에이지, 인 이어즈, 이즈 트웬티 투.

Original English: I forgot how easily I had taught myself from the printed page.
English: i forgot how easily i had taught myself from the printed page.
Hindi: आई फर्गट हाउ ईजिली आई हैड टॉट मायसेल्फ फ्रॉम द प्रिंटेड पेज.
Korean: 아이 퍼갓 하우 이지리 아이 해드 토트 마이셀프 프롬 더 프린티드 페이지.

Original English: Any average young fellow can teach himself in a week.
English: any average young fellow can teach himself in a week.
Hindi: एनी एवरिज यंग फेलो कैन टीच हिम्सेल्फ इन अ वीक.
Korean: 에니 애버리지 영 펠로 캔 티치 힘셀프 인 아 위크.

Original English: Please do not think that I already know it all.
English: please do not think that i already know it all.
Hindi: प्लीज़ डू नॉट थिंक दैट आई ऑलरेडी नो इट ऑल.
Korean: 플리즈 두 낫 띵크 댓 아이 올레디 노 잇 올.

Original English: You see, we were teaching ourselves.
English: you see, we were teaching ourselves.
Hindi: यू सी, वी वर टीचिंग आउर्सेल्व्ज़.
Korean: 유 씨, 위 워 티칭 아우어셀브즈.

Original English: And now behold the perversity of things.
English: and now behold the perversity of things.
Hindi: ऐंड नाउ बिहोल्ड द परवर्सिटी अव थिंग्स.
Korean: 앤드 나우 비홀드 더 퍼버시티 오브 띵즈.

Original English: Yield yourself to the waters that are ripping and tearing at you.
English: yield yourself to the waters that are ripping and tearing at you.
Hindi: यील्ड योर्सेल्फ टू द वॉटर्ज़ दैट आर रिपिंग ऐंड टेरिंग ऐट यू.
Korean: 이일드 유어셀프 투 더 워터즈 댓 아르 리핑 앤드 테어링 앳 유.

Original English: Mr McVeigh told me about him.
English: mister mcveigh told me about him.
Hindi: मिस्टर म्क्वे टोल्ड मी अबाउट हिम.
Korean: 미스터 맥베이 톨드 미 어바웃 힘.

Original English: Unlike Joshua, he stood in no need of divine assistance.
English: unlike joshua, he stood in no need of divine assistance.
Hindi: अनलाइक जोशुआ, ही स्टूड इन नो नीड अव डिवाइन असिस्टेंस.
Korean: 언라이크 조슈아, 히 스투드 인 노 니드 어브 디바인 어시스턴스.

Original English: To say the least, Captain Cook was a rather thorough going empiricist.
English: to say the least, captain cook was a rather thorough going empiricist.
Hindi: टू से द लीस्ट, कैप्टन कुक वस अ रादर थरो गोइंग एम्पिरिसिस्ट.
Korean: 투 세이 더 리스트, 캡틴 쿡 워즈 아 래더 써로우 고잉 엠피리시스트.

Original English: Man could not conquer them.
English: man could not conquer them.
Hindi: मैन कुड नॉट कांकर देम.
Korean: 맨 쿧 낫 칸커 뎀.

Original English: Thought I, and a worthy fool he proved.
English: thought i, and a worthy fool he proved.
Hindi: थॉट आई, एंड अ वर्थी फूल ही प्रूव्ड.
Korean: 쏘트 아이, 앤드 아 워디 풀 히 프루브드.

Original English: A scarlet loincloth completed his costume.
English: a scarlet loincloth completed his costume.
Hindi: अ स्कारलेट लॉइनक्लॉथ कम्प्लीटेड हिस कॉस्ट्यूम.
Korean: 아 스칼렛 로인클로스 컴플리티드 히즈 코스튬.

Original English: I like to speculate upon the glorious future of man.
English: i like to speculate upon the glorious future of man.
Hindi: आई लाइक टू स्पेक्युलेट अपॉन द ग्लोरियस फ्यूचर अव मैन.
Korean: 아이 라이크 투 스펙큘레이트 어폰 더 글로리어스 퓨처 오브 맨.

Original English: Christmas is an easy problem compared with a Polynesian giving-feast.
English: christmas is an easy problem compared with a polynesian giving-feast.
Hindi: क्रिसमस इज अन ईज़ी प्रॉब्लम कम्पेर्ड विथ अ पॉलिनीशियन गिविंगफीस्ट.
Korean: 크리스마스 이즈 안 이지 프라블럼 컴페어드 위드 아 폴리네시안 기빙 피스트.

Original English: He had peeled off his shirt and was wildly waving it.
English: he had peeled off his shirt and was wildly waving it.
Hindi: ही हैड पील्ड ऑफ हिस शर्ट ऐंड वज़ वाइल्डली वेविंग इट.
Korean: 히 핻 필드 오프 히즈 셔츠 앤드 워즈 와일들리 웨이빙 잇.

Original English: And how would we ever find ourselves.
English: and how would we ever find ourselves.
Hindi: एंड हाउ वुड वी एवर फाइंड आयोर्सेल्व्ज़.
Korean: 앤드 하우 우드 위 에버 파인드 아우어셀브스.

Original English: I defy any man to get a Solomon Island sore in California.
English: i defy any man to get a solomon island sore in california.
Hindi: आई डिफाई ऐनी मैन टू गेट अ सोलोमन आइलैंड सोर इन कैलिफोर्निया.
Korean: 아이 디파이 애니 맨 투 겟 아 솔로몬 아일랜드 소어 인 캘리포니아.

Original English: A bush chief had died a natural death.
English: a bush chief had died a natural death.
Hindi: अ बुश चीफ हैड डाइड अ नैचरल डेथ.
Korean: 아 부쉬 치프 해드 다이드 아 내추럴 데스.

Original English: The skipper's and Nakata's gymnastics served as a translation without words.
English: the skipper's and nakata's gymnastics served as a translation without words.
Hindi: द स्किपर एंड नकाटा जिमनैस्टिक्स सर्व अस अ ट्रांसलेशन विथाउट वर्ड्स.
Korean: 더 스키퍼스 앤드 나카타즈 짐내스틱스 서브드 애즈 아 트랜슬레이션 위드아웃 워즈.

Original English: Last night he showed all the symptoms of coming down with pneumonia.
English: last night he showed all the symptoms of coming down with pneumonia.
Hindi: लास्ट नाइट ही शोड ऑल द सिम्पटम्स अव कमिंग डाउन विथ न्यूमोनिया.
Korean: 라스트 나이트 히 쇼드 올 더 심텀즈 어브 커밍 다운 위드 뉴모니아.

Original English: My idea was that he would have more influence over the natives.
English: my idea was that he would have more influence over the natives.
Hindi: माई आइडिया वस धैट ही वुड हैव मोर इन्फ्लूएंस ओवर द नेटिव्स.
Korean: 마이 아이디어 와즈 댓 히 우드 해브 모어 인플루언스 오버 더 네이티브스.

Original English: It is merely the simple superlative.
English: it is merely the simple superlative.
Hindi: इट इज़ मिर्ली द सिम्पल सुपरलेटिव.
Korean: 잇 이즈 미얼리 더 심플 슈퍼라티브.

Original English: I made no more overtures.
English: i made no more overtures.
Hindi: आई मेड नो मोर ओवरचर.
Korean: 아이 메이드 노 모어 오버츄어즈.

Original English: Among my minor afflictions, I may mention a new and mysterious one.
English: among my minor afflictions, i may mention a new and mysterious one.
Hindi: अमंग माय माइनर अफ्लिक्शंस, आई मे मेंशन अ न्यू ऐंड मिस्टेरियस वन.
Korean: 아몽 마이 마이너 어플릭션즈, 아이 메이 멘션 아 누 앤드 미스테리어스 원.

Original English: The voyage was our idea of a good time.
English: the voyage was our idea of a good time.
Hindi: द वॉयज वज़ और आईडिया अव अ गुड टाइम.
Korean: 더 보야지 워즈 아우어 아이디어 어브 아 굿 타임.

Original English: At sea, Tuesday, March 17, 1908.
English: at sea, tuesday, march 17, 1908.
Hindi: ऐट सी, ट्यूज़डे, मार्च सेवनटीन, नाइन्टीन हंड्रेड.
Korean: 앳 씨, 튜즈데이, 마치 세븐틴, 나인틴헌드레드.

Original English: Yes, sir, he answered, with cheerful alacrity.
English: yes, sir, he answered, with cheerful alacrity.
Hindi: येस, सर, ही आन्सर्ड, विथ चियरफुल अलाक्रिटी.
Korean: 예스, 서, 히 앤서드, 위드 치어풀 알래크리티.

Original English: I was still weak from my prolonged immersion.
English: i was still weak from my prolonged immersion.
Hindi: आई वज़ स्टिल वीक फ्रॉम माई प्रोलॉंग्ड इमर्शन.
Korean: 아이 워즈 스틸 위크 프럼 마이 프롤롱드 이머전.

Original English: The boy hesitated, then mastered his temper.
English: the boy hesitated, then mastered his temper.
Hindi: द बॉय हेसिटेटेड, देन मास्टर्ड हिस टेम्पर.
Korean: 더 보이 해시티티드, 덴 매스터드 히즈 템퍼.

Original English: I was beneath the water, suffocating and drowning.
English: i was beneath the water, suffocating and drowning.
Hindi: आई वस बिनीथ द वॉटर, सफोकेटिंग एंड ड्राउनिंग.
Korean: 아이 워즈 비니쓰 더 워터, 서포케이팅 앤드 드라우닝.

Original English: The pain from my hurt knee was agonizing.
English: the pain from my hurt knee was agonizing.
Hindi: द पेन फ्रम माई हर्ट नी वस ऐगनाइजिंग.
Korean: 더 페인 프럼 마이 허트 니 워즈 애고나이징.

Original English: The hunters were still arguing and roaring like some semi-human amphibious breed.
English: the hunters were still arguing and roaring like some semi-human amphibious breed.
Hindi: द हंटर्स वर स्टिल आर्ग्यूइंग एंड रोरिंग लाइक सम सेमिह्यूमन एम्फिबियस ब्रीड.
Korean: 더 헌터즈 워 스틸 아규잉 앤드 로어링 라이크 섬 세마이휴먼 앰피비어스 브리드.

Original English: I have been robbed, sir, I amended.
English: i have been robbed, sir, i amended.
Hindi: आई हैव बीन रॉब्ड, सर, आई अमेंडिड.
Korean: 아이 해브 빈 롭드, 서, 아이 어멘디드.

Original English: You were looking squeamish this afternoon, he began.
English: you were looking squeamish this afternoon, he began.
Hindi: यू वर लुकिंग स्क्वीमिश दिस आफ्टरनून, ही बिगैन.
Korean: 유 워 루킹 스퀴미쉬 디스 애프터눈, 히 비갠.

Original English: How could I answer the question on the spur of the moment.
English: how could i answer the question on the spur of the moment.
Hindi: हाउ कुड आई आंसर द क्वेश्चन आन द स्पर अव द मोमेंट.
Korean: 하우 쿧 아이 앤서 더 퀘스천 온 더 스퍼 오브 더 모먼트.

Original English: I learned it myself in English ships.
English: i learned it myself in english ships.
Hindi: आई लर्न्ड इट मायसेल्फ इन इंग्लिश शिप्स.
Korean: 아이 런드 잇 마이셀프 인 잉글리쉬 쉽스.

Original English: An altruistic act is an act performed for the welfare of others.
English: an altruistic act is an act performed for the welfare of others.
Hindi: अन अल्ट्रूइस्टिक ऐक्ट इज अन ऐक्ट परफॉर्म्ड फॉर द वेलफेयर अव अदर्स.
Korean: 안 알트루이스틱 액트 이즈 안 액트 퍼폼드 포어 더 웰페어 어브 어더즈.

Original English: Knowing him, I review the old Scandinavian myths with clearer understanding.
English: knowing him, i review the old scandinavian myths with clearer understanding.
Hindi: नोइंग हिम, आई रिव्यू दि ओल्ड स्कैंडिनेवियन मिथ्स विद क्लियरर अंडरस्टैंडिंग.
Korean: 노잉 힘, 아이 리뷰 디 올드 스칸디네이비언 미쓰 위드 클리러 언더스탠딩.

Original English: Yes, and no, sir, was the slow reply.
English: yes, and no, sir, was the slow reply.
Hindi: यस, ऐंड नो, सर, वस द स्लो रिप्लाई.
Korean: 예스, 앤드 노, 서, 워즈 더 슬로우 리플라이.

Original English: And each year something happened, and I did not go.
English: and each year something happened, and i did not go.
Hindi: ऐंड ईच यर समथिंग हॅपेन्ड, ऐंड आई डिड नाट गो.
Korean: 앤드 이치 이어 섬씽 해펀드, 앤드 아이 딛 낫 고.

Original English: How in hell did he know it was you in the dark.
English: how in hell did he know it was you in the dark.
Hindi: हाउ इन हेल डिड ही नो इट वाज यू इन द डार्क.
Korean: 하우 인 헬 디드 히 노우 잇 워즈 유 인 더 다크.

Original English: Of course much grumbling went on, and little outbursts were continually occurring.
English: of course much grumbling went on, and little outbursts were continually occurring.
Hindi: अफ कोर्स मच ग्रम्बलिंग वेंट ऑन, एंड लिटल आउटबर्स्ट्स वेर कंटिन्यूअली अकरिंग.
Korean: 어브 코스 머치 그럼블링 웬트 온, 앤드 리틀 아웃버스트 워 컨티뉴얼리 어커링.

Original English: You have all the advantage.
English: you have all the advantage.
Hindi: यू हैव ऑल दि एडवांटेज.
Korean: 유 해브 올 디 어드밴티지.

Original English: The dirk mentioned by Wolf Larsen rested in its sheath on my hip.
English: the dirk mentioned by wolf larsen rested in its sheath on my hip.
Hindi: द डर्क मेंशनड बाई वुल्फ लार्सन रेस्टेड इन इट्स शीथ ऑन माई हिप.
Korean: 더 더크 멘션드 바이 울프 라슨 레스티드 인 잇츠 시스 온 마이 힙.

Original English: Have you ever earned a dollar by your own labour.
English: have you ever earned a dollar by your own labor.
Hindi: हैव यू एवर अर्न्ड अ डॉलर बाय योर ओन लेबर.
Korean: 해브 유 에버 언드 아 달러 바이 유어 온 레이버.

Original English: He gave no reason, but his motive was obvious enough.
English: he gave no reason, but his motive was obvious enough.
Hindi: ही गेव नो रीज़न, बट हिज़ मोटिव वज़ ऑब्वियस इनफ.
Korean: 히 게이브 노 리즌, 벗 히즈 모티브 워즈 어비어스 이너프.

Original English: Ah, it was sweet in my ears.
English: ah, it was sweet in my ears.
Hindi: आ, इट वस स्वीट इन माई इअर्स.
Korean: 아, 잇 와즈 스위트 인 마이 이어즈.

Original English: He may desire to escape pain, or to enjoy pleasure.
English: he may desire to escape pain, or to enjoy pleasure.
Hindi: ही मे डिज़ायर टू एस्केप पेन, ऑर टू एन्जॉय प्लेजर.
Korean: 히 메이 디자이어 투 에스케이프 페인, 오어 투 엔조이 플레저.

Original English: It was impossible to hoist sail and claw off that shore.
English: it was impossible to hoist sail and claw off that shore.
Hindi: इट वस इम्पासिबल टू हॉइस्ट सेल ऐंड क्लॉ ऑफ दैट शोर.
Korean: 잇 워즈 임파서블 투 호이스트 세일 앤드 클로 오프 댓 쇼어.

Original English: There was nothing for us but the wide raw ocean.
English: there was nothing for us but the wide raw ocean.
Hindi: देर वस नथिंग फॉर अस बट द वाइड रॉ ओशन.
Korean: 데어 워즈 너씽 포어 어스 벗 더 와이드 로 오션.

Original English: I arose obediently and went down the beach.
English: i arose obediently and went down the beach.
Hindi: आई अरोज़ ओबीडियन्ट्ली एंड वेंट डाउन द बीच.
Korean: 아이 어로즈 오비디언틀리 앤드 웬트 다운 더 비치.

Original English: The next thing to watch out for is bed sores.
English: the next thing to watch out for is bed sores.
Hindi: द नेक्स्ट थिंग टू वॉच आउट फॉर इज़ बेड सोर्स.
Korean: 더 넥스트 띵 투 와치 아웃 포 이즈 베드 소어즈.

Original English: At that moment I got the impression that she was willowy.
English: at that moment i got the impression that she was willowy.
Hindi: ऐट दॅट मोमेंट आई गॉट दि इम्प्रेशन दॅट शी वज़ विलोवी.
Korean: 앳 댓 모먼트 아이 갓 디 임프레션 댓 쉬 워즈 윌로위.

Original English: Your father's fifth command, he nodded.
English: your father's fifth command, he nodded.
Hindi: योर फ़ादर्स फिफ्थ कमांड, ही नॉडेड.
Korean: 유어 파더즈 피프스 커맨드, 히 나디드.

Original English: On occasion, on this traverse, the Cape Verde Islands are raised.
English: on occasion, on this traverse, the cape verde islands are raised.
Hindi: ऑन अकेशन, ऑन दिस ट्रवर्स, द केप वर्ड आइलैंड्स आर रेज़्ड.
Korean: 온 어케이전, 온 디스 트래버스, 더 케이프 버드 아일랜드즈 아 레이즈드.

Original English: She is essentially the life-giving, life-conserving female of the species.
English: she is essentially the life-giving, life-conserving female of the species.
Hindi: शी इज़ इसेंशली द लाइफगिविंग, लाइफकंसर्विंग फीमेल अव द स्पीसीज़.
Korean: 쉬 이즈 이센셜리 더 라이프기빙, 라이프컨서빙 피메일 오브 더 스피시즈.

Original English: This was when the explosion occurred.
English: this was when the explosion occurred.
Hindi: दिस वस वेन दि एक्सप्लोजन अकर्ड.
Korean: 디스 워즈 웬 디 익스플로전 어커드.

Original English: Also, at regular intervals, he would mutter.
English: also, at regular intervals, he would mutter.
Hindi: ऑल्सो, ऐट रेग्यूलर इंटरवल्स, ही वुड मटर.
Korean: 알소, 앳 레귤러 인터벌즈, 히 우드 머터.

Original English: It is a very tenable hypothesis, and will bear looking into.
English: it is a very tenable hypothesis, and will bear looking into.
Hindi: इट इज अ वेरी टेनेबल हाइपोथेसिस, ऐंड विल बेअर लुकिंग इंटू.
Korean: 잇 이즈 아 베리 테너블 하이퍼시스, 앤드 윌 베어 루킹 인투.

Original English: There were orange-green, gold-green, and a copper-green.
English: there were orange-green, gold-green, and a copper-green.
Hindi: देर वेर ऑरेंज-ग्रीन, गोल्डग्रीन, ऐंड अ कॉपरग्रीन.
Korean: 데어 워 오렌지그린, 골드그린, 엔드 아 카퍼그린.

Original English: The Gabriel voice of the Samurai rang out.
English: the gabriel voice of the samurai rang out.
Hindi: द गैब्रियल वॉइस अव द सैमुराई रैंग आउट.
Korean: 더 가브리엘 보이스 어브 더 사무라이 랭 아웃.

Original English: The sunsets grow more bizarre and spectacular off this coast of the Argentine.
English: the sunsets grow more bizarre and spectacular off this coast of the argentine.
Hindi: द सनसेट्स ग्रो मोर बिज़ार ऐंड स्पेक्टैक्युलर ऑफ दिस कोस्ट अव दि आर्जेंटाइन.
Korean: 더 선셋 그로우 모어 비자 앤드 스펙타큘러 오프 디스 코스트 오브 디 아르헨티나.

Original English: The history of our westward-faring race is written in it.
English: the history of our westward-faring race is written in it.
Hindi: द हिस्ट्री अव आवर वेस्टवर्ड-फेरिंग रेस इस रिटन इन इट.
Korean: 더 히스토리 어브 아우어 웨스트워드페어링 레이스 이즈 리튼 인 잇.

Original English: And the Eurasian Chinese-Englishman bowed himself away.
English: and the eurasian chinese-englishman bowed himself away.
Hindi: ऐंड द यूरैशियन चाइनीज़ इंग्लिशमैन बाउड हिम्सेल्फ अवे.
Korean: 앤드 더 유레이지언 차이니즈잉글리시맨 바우드 힘셀프 어웨이.

Original English: They were babbling and chattering all together.
English: they were babbling and chattering all together.
Hindi: थे वेर बबलिंग एंड चैटरिंग ऑल टुगेदर.
Korean: 데이 워 배블링 앤드 채터링 올 투게더.

Original English: Too much, he told me, with ominous rolling head.
English: too much, he told me, with ominous rolling head.
Hindi: टू मच, ही टोल्ड मी, विथ आमिनस रोलिंग हेड.
Korean: 투 머치, 히 톨드 미, 위드 어미너스 롤링 헤드.

Original English: He is a candidate, rising from the serf class to our class.
English: he is a candidate, rising from the serf class to our class.
Hindi: ही इस अ कैंडिडेट, राइजिंग फ्रम द सर्फ क्लास टू आवर क्लास.
Korean: 히 이즈 아 캔디데이트, 라이징 프럼 더 서프 클래스 투 아워 클래스.

Original English: We are cooking on the coal stove and on the oil burners.
English: we are cooking on the coal stove and on the oil burners.
Hindi: वी आर कुकिंग ऑन द कोल स्टोव एंड ऑन दि ऑइल बर्नर्स.
Korean: 위 아르 쿠킹 온 더 콜 스토브 앤드 온 디 오일 버너스.

Original English: The steward has just tendered me a respectful bit of advice.
English: the steward has just tendered me a respectful bit of advice.
Hindi: द स्टूवर्ड हैज़ जस्ट टेंडर्ड मी अ रिस्पेक्टफुल बिट अव ऐडवाइस.
Korean: 더 스튜어드 해즈 저스트 텐더드 미 아 리스펙트풀 빗 어브 어드바이스.

Original English: Well, did they eat.
English: well, did they eat.
Hindi: वेल, डिड देई ईट.
Korean: 웰, 딛 데이 잇.

Original English: Famine had been my great ally.
English: famine had been my great ally.
Hindi: फैमिन हैड बिन माय ग्रेट ऐलाई.
Korean: 패민 해드 빈 마이 그레이트 앨라이.

Original English: Nowhere in the North is the soil so prolific.
English: nowhere in the north is the soil so prolific.
Hindi: नोवेर इन द नॉर्थ इस द सॉइल सो प्रलिफिक.
Korean: 노웨어 인 더 노스 이즈 더 소일 쏘 프로리픽.

Original English: They ran the canoe in and climbed the high earth bank.
English: they ran the canoe in and climbed the high earth bank.
Hindi: थे रैन द कनू इन ऐंड क्लाइम्ड द हाई अर्थ बैंक.
Korean: 데이 랜 더 카누 인 앤드 클라임드 더 하이 어스 뱅크.

Original English: The land exchanged its austere robes for the garb of a smiling wanton.
English: the land exchanged its austere robes for the garb of a smiling wanton.
Hindi: द लैंड एक्सचेंज्ड इट्स ऑस्टियर रोब्स फॉर द गार्ब अव अ स्माइलिंग वांटन.
Korean: 더 랜드 익스체인지드 잇츠 오스티어 로브즈 포어 더 가브 어브 아 스마일링 완튼.

Original English: There were stir and bustle, new faces, and fresh facts.
English: there were stir and bustle, new faces, and fresh facts.
Hindi: देर वर स्टर एंड बसल, न्यू फेसेस, एंड फ्रेश फैक्ट्स.
Korean: 데어 워 스터 앤드 버슬, 뉴 페이시즈, 앤드 프레쉬 팩츠.

Original English: And there was Ethel Baird, whom also you must remember.
English: and there was ethel baird, whom also you must remember.
Hindi: ऐंड थेर वस एथल बेर्ड, हूम आल्सो यू मस्ट रिमेम्बर.
Korean: 앤드 데어 워즈 에설 베어드, 훔 알소 유 머스트 리멤버.

Original English: He had become a man very early in life.
English: he had become a man very early in life.
Hindi: ही हैड बिकम अ मैन वेरी अर्ली इन लाइफ.
Korean: 히 핻 비컴 아 맨 베리 얼리 인 라이프.

Original English: I did not think you would be so early.
English: i did not think you would be so early.
Hindi: आई डिड नॉट थिंक यू वुड बी सो अर्ली.
Korean: 아이 디드 낫 씽크 유 우드 비 소 얼리.

Original English: He did not know what went on in the minds of his superiors.
English: he did not know what went on in the minds of his superiors.
Hindi: ही डिड नॉट नो वट वेंट ऑन इन द माइंड्स ऑव हिज सुपीरियर्स.
Korean: 히 디드 낫 노 왓 웬트 온 인 더 마인즈 어브 히즈 수피어리어스.

Original English: Mops, sir, eagerly answered the sailor at the wheel.
English: mops, sir, eagerly answered the sailor at the wheel.
Hindi: मॉप्स, सर, ईगरली एन्सर्ड द सेलर ऐट द व्हील.
Korean: 맙스, 서, 이거리 앤서드 더 세일러 앳 더 윌.

Original English: Some one had thrust a large sheath-knife into his hand.
English: some one had thrust a large sheath-knife into his hand.
Hindi: सम वन हैड थ्रस्ट अ लार्ज शीथ-नाइफ इंटू हिज़ हैंड.
Korean: 썸 원 핫 쓰러스트 아 라지 시스나이프 인투 히즈 핸드.

Original English: O'Brien emitted a shriek that sank swiftly to a gurgling sob.
English: o'brien emitted a shriek that sank swiftly to a gurgling sob.
Hindi: ओब्रियन इमिटेड अ श्रीक दैट सैंक स्विफ्टली टू अ गर्गलिंग सॉब.
Korean: 오브라이언 이밋드 아 쉬릭 댓 생크 스위프트리 투 아 거글링 솝.

Original English: Sandel would never become a world champion.
English: sandel would never become a world champion.
Hindi: सैंडल वुड नेवर बिकम अ वर्ल्ड चैंपियन.
Korean: 샌들 우드 네버 비컴 아 월드 챔피언.

Original English: Also, she wouldn't walk.
English: also, she would not walk.
Hindi: आलसो, शी वुड नॉट वॉक.
Korean: 알소, 시 우드 낫 워크.

Original English: To my dearest and always appreciated friend, I submit myself.
English: to my dearest and always appreciated friend, i submit myself.
Hindi: टू माई डिअरेस्ट ऐंड ऑलवेज़ अप्रेशिएटेड फ्रेंड, आई सबमिट मायसेल्फ.
Korean: 투 마이 디어레스트 앤드 올웨이즈 어프리시에이티드 프렌드, 아이 서브밋 마이셀프.

Original English: You used to joyride like the very devil.
English: you used to joyride like the very devil.
Hindi: यू यूज़्ड टू जॉयराइड लाइक द वेरी डेविल.
Korean: 유 유즈드 투 조이라이드 라이크 더 베리 데블.

Original English: They saw each other for the first time in Boston.
English: they saw each other for the first time in boston.
Hindi: दे सॉ ईच अधर फॉर द फर्स्ट टाइम इन बॉस्टन.
Korean: 데이 소 이치 어더 포어 더 퍼스트 타임 인 보스턴.

Original English: Isaac Ford, the austere soldier of the Lord, the old hypocrite.
English: isaac ford, the austere soldier of the lord, the old hypocrite.
Hindi: आइसक फोर्ड, दि ऑस्टीर सोल्जर अव द लॉर्ड, दि ओल्ड हिपोक्रिट.
Korean: 아이삭 포드, 디 오스티어 솔져 오브 더 로드, 디 올드 히포크릿.

Original English: Eighteen, he added.
English: eighteen, he added.
Hindi: एटीन, ही ऐडेड.
Korean: 에이틴, 히 애드.

Original English: His reward should have been peace and repose.
English: his reward should have been peace and repose.
Hindi: हिज रिवॉर्ड शुड हैव बीन पीस ऐंड रिपोज़.
Korean: 히즈 리워드 슈드 해브 빈 피스 앤드 리포즈.

Original English: He was an amphibian and a mountaineer.
English: he was an amphibian and a mountaineer.
Hindi: ही वज़ अन ऐम्फिबियन ऐंड अ माउंटेनियर.
Korean: 히 워즈 안 앰피비언 앤드 아 마운티니어.

Original English: It was sanctification and salvation.
English: it was sanctification and salvation.
Hindi: इट वज़ सैंक्टिफिकेशन ऐंड साल्वेशन.
Korean: 잇 워즈 생티피케이션 앤드 살베이션.

Original English: The history of the eighteenth century is written, Ernest prompted.
English: the history of the eighteenth century is written, ernest prompted.
Hindi: द हिस्ट्री अव दि एटीन्थ सेंचुरी इस रिटन, अर्नेस्ट प्राम्पटेड.
Korean: 더 히스토리 어브 디 에이틴쓰 센추리 이즈 리튼, 어니스트 프롬티드.

Original English: They are not biologists nor sociologists.
English: they are not biologists nor sociologists.
Hindi: धे आर नाट बायोलॉजिस्ट्स नॉर सोशियोलॉजिस्ट्स.
Korean: 데이 아 낫 바이올로지스트 노어 소시오알러지스트.

Original English: The more his opponents grew excited, the more Ernest deliberately excited them.
English: the more his opponents grew excited, the more ernest deliberately excited them.
Hindi: द मोर हिस ऑपोनेंट्स ग्रू एक्साइटेड, द मोर अर्नेस्ट डिलिबरेटली एक्साइटेड देम.
Korean: 더 모어 히즈 어포넌츠 그루 엑사이티드, 더 모어 어니스트 딜리버럿리 엑사이티드 뎀.

Original English: By virtue of that power we shall remain in power.
English: by virtue of that power we shall remain in power.
Hindi: बाई वर्चू अव दॅट पावर वी शैल रिमेन इन पावर.
Korean: 바이 버츄 어브 댓 파워 위 셜 리메인 인 파워.

Original English: One guess will do, Ernest retorted.
English: one guess will do, ernest retorted.
Hindi: वन गेस विल डू, अर्नेस्ट रिटॉर्टेड.
Korean: 원 게스 윌 두, 어니스트 리토티드.

Original English: Take my advice and accept the vacation.
English: take my advice and accept the vacation.
Hindi: टेक माई एडवाइस ऐंड एक्सेप्ट द वेकेशन.
Korean: 테이크 마이 어드바이스 앤드 엑셉트 더 베케이션.

Original English: I could not agree with Ernest.
English: i could not agree with ernest.
Hindi: आई कुड नाट अग्री विथ अर्नेस्ट.
Korean: 아이 쿳 낫 어그리 위드 어네스트.

Original English: But such divergence of opinion would constitute no menace to society.
English: but such divergence of opinion would constitute no menace to society.
Hindi: बट सच डाइवर्जन्स अव ओपिनियन वूड कॉनस्टिट्यूट नो मेनस टू सोसाइटी.
Korean: 벗 서치 다이버전스 어브 오피니언 우드 컨스티튜트 노 메니스 투 소사이어티.

Original English: It is dog eat dog, and you ate them up.
English: it is dog eat dog, and you ate them up.
Hindi: इट इस डॉग ईट डॉग, ऐंड यू एट देम अप.
Korean: 잇 이즈 독 잇 독, 앤드 유 에이트 뎀 업.

Original English: Let us run them for ourselves.
English: let us run them for ourselves.
Hindi: लेट अस रन देम फॉर आउर्सेल्व्ज़.
Korean: 렛 어스 런 뎀 포 아우어셀브스.

Original English: It was introduced by Representative Dick of Ohio.
English: it was introduced by representative dick of ohio.
Hindi: इट वज इंट्रोड्यूस्ट बाई रिप्रेज़ेंटेटिव डिक अव ओहायो.
Korean: 잇 워즈 인트로듀스트 바이 레프러젠터티브 딕 오브 오하이오.

Original English: Very few people knew of the existence of this law.
English: very few people knew of the existence of this law.
Hindi: वेरी फ्यू पीपल न्यू अव दि एग्जिस्टन्स अव दिस लॉ.
Korean: 베리 퓨 피플 뉴 어브 디 엑시스턴스 어브 디스 로.

Original English: The very thing, Ernest agreed.
English: the very thing, ernest agreed.
Hindi: द वेरी थिंग, अर्नेस्ट एग्रीड.
Korean: 더 베리 띵, 어니스트 어그리드.

Original English: Also a fellow Senator, Chauncey Depew, said.
English: also a fellow senator, chauncey depew, said.
Hindi: ऑल्सो अ फेलो सेनेटर, चॉन्सी डेप्यू, सेड.
Korean: 알소 아 펠로 세너터, 챈시 디퓨, 세드.

Original English: Ernest saw in the affair the most sinister import.
English: ernest saw in the affair the most sinister import.
Hindi: अर्नेस्ट सॉ इन दि अफेयर द मोस्ट सिनिस्टर इम्पोर्ट.
Korean: 어니스트 소 인 디 어페어 더 모스트 시니스터 임포트.

Original English: Then there was the campaign.
English: then there was the campaign.
Hindi: देन धेर वज़ द कैम्पेन.
Korean: 덴 데어 와즈 더 캠페인.

Original English: He was manifestly distressed by my coming.
English: he was manifestly distressed by my coming.
Hindi: ही वज़ मैनिफ़ेस्टली डिस्ट्रेस्ट बाय माई कमिंग.
Korean: 히 워즈 매니페스트리 디스트레스트 바이 마이 커밍.

Original English: Not a wheel moved in his empire.
English: not a wheel moved in his empire.
Hindi: नॉट अ व्हील मूव्ड इन हिज़ एम्पायर.
Korean: 낫 아 윌 무브드 인 히즈 엠파이어.

Original English: The reorganization of these countries took the form of revolution.
English: the reorganization of these countries took the form of revolution.
Hindi: द रीऑर्गनाइजेशन अव दीज़ कंट्रीज़ टुक द फॉर्म अव रेवोल्यूशन.
Korean: 더 리오르거나이제이션 어브 디즈 컨트리즈 툭 더 폼 어브 레볼루션.

Original English: You're going in for grab sharing.
English: you are going in for grab sharing.
Hindi: यू आर गोइंग इन फॉर ग्रैब शेरिंग.
Korean: 유 아르 고잉 인 포 그랩 쉐어링.

Original English: The Oligarchy will encourage such ambition and the consequent competition.
English: the oligarchy will encourage such ambition and the consequent competition.
Hindi: दि ऑलिगार्की विल एन्करिज सच ऐम्बिशन ऐंड द कांसिक्वेंट कम्पटीशन.
Korean: 디 알리가키 윌 엔커리지 서치 앰비션 앤드 더 컨시퀀트 컴페티션.

Original English: Violation of this law was made a high misdemeanor and punished accordingly.
English: violation of this law was made a high misdemeanor and punished accordingly.
Hindi: वायलेशन अव दिस लॉ वस मेड अ हाई मिस्डेमीनर ऐंड पनिश्ट अकॉर्डिंगली.
Korean: 바이올레이션 어브 디스 로 워즈 메이드 아 하이 미스디미너 앤드 퍼니쉬드 어코딩리.

Original English: Without discussion, it was the agents provocateurs who caused the Peasant Revolt.
English: without discussion, it was the agents provocateurs who caused the peasant revolt.
Hindi: विदाउट डिस्कशन, इट वज़ दि एजेंट्स प्रवोकटर्स हू कॉज़्ड द पेज़न्ट रिवोल्ट.
Korean: 위다웃 디스커션, 잇 워즈 디 에이전츠 프로보커터즈 후 코즈드 더 페전트 리볼트.

Original English: The task we set ourselves was threefold.
English: the task we set ourselves was threefold.
Hindi: द टास्क वी सेट आउर्सेल्वस वस थ्रीफोल्ड.
Korean: 더 태스크 위 셋 아우어셀브즈 워즈 쓰리폴드.

Original English: Many other similar disconcerting omissions will be noticed in the Manuscript.
English: many other similar disconcerting omissions will be noticed in the manuscript.
Hindi: मेनी अदर सिमिलर डिस्कनसर्टिंग ओमिशन्स विल बी नोटिस्ड इन द मैन्युस्क्रिप्ट.
Korean: 메니 어더 시밀러 디스컨서팅 오미션즈 윌 비 노티스드 인 더 매뉴스크립트.

Original English: The flower of the artistic and intellectual world were revolutionists.
English: the flower of the artistic and intellectual world were revolutionists.
Hindi: द फ्लावर अव दि आर्टिस्टिक एंड इंटलेक्चुअल वर्ल्ड वर रेवोल्यूशनिस्ट्स.
Korean: 더 플라워 어브 디 아티스틱 앤드 인텔렉추얼 월드 워 레볼루션니스트.

Original English: This the Iron Heel foresaw and laid its schemes accordingly.
English: this the iron heel foresaw and laid its schemes accordingly.
Hindi: दिस दि आयरन हील फॉरसॉ ऐंड लेड इट्स स्कीम्स अकोर्डिंगली.
Korean: 디스 디 아이언 힐 포어소 앤드 레이드 잇츠 스킴즈 어코딩리.

Original English: The mob came on, but it could not advance.
English: the mob came on, but it could not advance.
Hindi: द माब केम ऑन, बट इट कुड नाट एडवांस.
Korean: 더 마브 케임 온, 벗 잇 쿧 낫 어드밴스.

Original English: But why continue the tirade, for tirade it was.
English: but why continue the tirade, for tirade it was.
Hindi: बट वाय कंटिन्यू द तायरेड, फॉर तायरेड इट वज़.
Korean: 벗 와이 컨티뉴 더 타이레이드, 포 타이레이드 잇 워즈.

Original English: After all superfluous flesh is gone what is left is stringy and resistant.
English: after all superfluous flesh is gone what is left is stringy and resistant.
Hindi: आफ्ट़र ऑल सूपरफ्लूअस फ्लेश इस गॉन व्हट इस लेफ्ट इस स्ट्रिंगी एंड रेज़िस्टंट.
Korean: 애프터 올 수퍼플루어스 플레쉬 이즈 곤 왓 이즈 레프트 이즈 스트링이 앤드 리지스턴트.

Original English: Beyond refusing to sell us food, they left us to ourselves.
English: beyond refusing to sell us food, they left us to ourselves.
Hindi: बियॉन्ड रिफ्यूज़िंग टू सेल अस फूड, थे लेफ्ट अस टू आउर्सेल्फ़्स.
Korean: 비욘드 리퓨징 투 셀 어스 푸드, 데이 레프트 어스 투 아우어셀브즈.

Original English: He was a merry monarch, especially so for an Asiatic.
English: he was a merry monarch, especially so for an asiatic.
Hindi: ही वज़ अ मेरी मोनार्क, इस्पेशली सो फॉर अन एशियाटिक.
Korean: 히 워즈 아 메리 모나크, 이스페셜리 소 포어 안 에시아틱.

Original English: What an excited whispering and conferring took place.
English: what an excited whispering and conferring took place.
Hindi: व्हाट अन एक्साइटेड विस्परिंग एंड कनफरिंग टुक प्लेस.
Korean: 왓 안 익사이티드 위스퍼링 앤드 컨퍼링 툭 플레이스.

Original English: Jacob Brinker, who was his roadmate, brought the news.
English: jacob brinker, who was his roadmate, brought the news.
Hindi: जेकब ब्रिंकर, हू वज़ हिज़ रोडमेट, ब्रॉट द न्यूज़.
Korean: 제이콥 브링커, 후 워즈 히즈 로드메이트, 브로트 더 뉴스.

Original English: Thus he turned the tenets and jargon of psychology back on me.
English: thus he turned the tenets and jargon of psychology back on me.
Hindi: धस ही टर्न्ड द टेनेट्स एंड जार्गन अव साइकोलॉजी बैक ऑन मी.
Korean: 더스 히 턴드 더 테니츠 앤드 자르건 어브 사이콜로지 백 안 미.

Original English: You yellow giant thing of the frost.
English: you yellow giant thing of the frost.
Hindi: यू येलो जायंट थिंग अव द फ्रॉस्ट.
Korean: 유 옐로우 자이언트 띵 어브 더 프로스트.

Original English: Never so strange a prophet came up to Jerusalem.
English: never so strange a prophet came up to jerusalem.
Hindi: नेवर सो स्ट्रेंज अ प्रॉफिट केम अप टू जेरूसलम.
Korean: 네버 소 스트레인지 아 프라핏 케임 업 투 제루살렘.

Original English: We who have endured so much surely can endure a little more.
English: we who have endured so much surely can endure a little more.
Hindi: वी हू हैव एन्डुर्ड सो मच शुरली कैन एन्ड्योर अ लिटल मोर.
Korean: 위 후 해브 엔듀어드 소 머치 슈얼리 캔 엔듀어 아 리틀 모어.

Original English: I have seen myself that one man contemplated by Pascal's philosophic eye.
English: i have seen myself that one man contemplated by pascal's philosophic eye.
Hindi: आई हैव सीन मायसेल्फ धैट वन मैन कॉन्टेम्प्लेटेड बाई पैस्कल्स फिलोसोफिक आई.
Korean: 아이 해브 신 마이셀프 댓 원 맨 컨템플레이트 바이 파스칼스 필로소픽 아이.

Original English: One great drawback to farming in California is our long dry summer.
English: one great drawback to farming in california is our long dry summer.
Hindi: वन ग्रेट ड्रॉबैक टू फार्मिंग इन कैलिफोर्निया इस आवर लॉंग ड्राई समर.
Korean: 원 그레이트 드로백 투 파밍 인 캘리포니아 이즈 아워 롱 드라이 서머.

Original English: I remembered the red wine of the Italian rancho, and shuddered inwardly.
English: i remembered the red wine of the italian rancho, and shuddered inwardly.
Hindi: आई रिमेंबर्ड द रेड वाइन अव दि इटैलियन रैंचो, एंड शडर्ड इनवर्डली.
Korean: 아이 리멤버드 더 레드 와인 어브 디 이탤리언 랜초, 앤드 셔더드 인워들리.

Original English: I said, and dismissed the matter as not worth thinking about.
English: i said, and dismissed the matter as not worth thinking about.
Hindi: आई सैड, ऐंड डिस्मिस्ट द मैटर ऐज नॉट वर्थ थिंकिंग अबाउट.
Korean: 아이 세드, 앤드 디스미스트 더 매터 애즈 낫 워스 띵킹 어바웃.

Original English: Then came my boy code.
English: then came my boy code.
Hindi: धेन केम माई बॉय कोड.
Korean: 덴 케임 마이 보이 코드.

Original English: And wherever I ranged, the way lay along alcohol-drenched roads.
English: and wherever i ranged, the way lay along alcohol-drenched roads.
Hindi: ऐंड वेरेवर आई रेंज्ड, द वे ले अलॉन्ग ऐल्कोहल-ड्रेंच्ड रोड्स.
Korean: 앤드 웨레버 아이 레인지드, 더 웨이 레이 얼롱 알코올 드렌치드 로드즈.

Original English: And as we hurried up town, Joe Goose explained.
English: and as we hurried up town, joe goose explained.
Hindi: ऐंड ऐज़ वी हरीड़ अप टाउन, जो गूस एक्सप्लेंड.
Korean: 앤드 애즈 위 허리드 업 타운, 조 구스 익스플레인드.

Original English: The scents of strange vegetation blew off the tropic land.
English: the scents of strange vegetation blew off the tropic land.
Hindi: द सेंट्स अव स्ट्रेंज वेजिटेशन ब्लू ऑफ द ट्रॉपिक लैंड.
Korean: 더 센츠 어브 스트레인지 베지테이션 블루 오프 더 트로픽 랜드.

Original English: The life there was healthful and athletic, but too juvenile.
English: the life there was healthful and athletic, but too juvenile.
Hindi: द लाइफ धेर वस हेल्थफ़ुल एंड ऐथलेटिक, बट टू जुवेनाइल.
Korean: 더 라이프 데어 워즈 헬스풀 앤드 애슬레틱, 벗 투 주브나일.

Original English: How valiantly I went at it that first day.
English: how valiantly i went at it that first day.
Hindi: हाउ वैलियंटली आई वेंट ऐट इट दैट फर्स्ट डे.
Korean: 하우 밸리언틀리 아이 웬트 앳 잇 댓 퍼스트 데이.

Original English: It would help to tide me along until I got steady employment.
English: it would help to tide me along until i got steady employment.
Hindi: इट वुड हेल्प टू टाइड मी अलॉन्ग अन्टिल आई गॉट स्टेडी एम्प्लॉयमेंट.
Korean: 잇 우드 헬프 투 타이드 미 어롱 언틸 아이 갓 스테디 엠플로이먼트.

Original English: Did I possess too much vitality.
English: did i possess too much vitality.
Hindi: डिड आई पज़ेस टू मच वाइटैलिटी.
Korean: 디드 아이 퍼제스 투 머치 바이털리티.

Original English: In his anxiety and solicitude and love they did not count.
English: in his anxiety and solicitude and love they did not count.
Hindi: इन हिज़ एंग्जायटी ऐंड सोलिसिट्यूड ऐंड लव थे डिड नॉट काउंट.
Korean: 인 히즈 앵자이어티 앤드 솔리시튜드 앤드 러브 데이 디드 낫 카운트.

Original English: He had fulfilled his duty and paid properly.
English: he had fulfilled his duty and paid properly.
Hindi: ही हैड फुल्फिल्ड हिज ड्यूटी ऐंड पेड प्रॉपरली.
Korean: 히 핻 풀필드 히즈 듀티 앤드 페이드 프라퍼리.

Original English: He knew what taboos he was violating.
English: he knew what taboos he was violating.
Hindi: ही न्यू वट टैबूज़ ही वज़ वायलेटिंग.
Korean: 히 누 왓 태부즈 히 워즈 바이얼레이팅.

Original English: Do you value your hide.
English: do you value your hide.
Hindi: डू यू वैल्यू योर हाइड.
Korean: 두 유 밸류 유어 하이드.

Original English: You should have seen them when they heard me spitting Chinook.
English: you should have seen them when they heard me spitting chinook.
Hindi: यू शुड हैव सीन देम वेन धेइ हर्ड मी स्पिटिंग चिनूक.
Korean: 유 슛 해브 신 뎀 웬 데이 허드 미 스피팅 치눅.

Original English: He plodded on for half an hour, when the hallucination arose again.
English: he plodded on for half an hour, when the hallucination arose again.
Hindi: ही प्लॉडिड ऑन फॉर हाफ अन आवर, वेन द हल्लूसिनेशन अरोज़ अगेन.
Korean: 히 플로디드 온 포 해프 언 아우어, 웬 더 할루시네이션 어로즈 어게인.

Original English: Tomorrow or next day it might he gone.
English: tomorrow or next day it might he gone.
Hindi: टमॉरो ऑर नेक्स्ट डे इट माइट ही गॉन.
Korean: 투모로우 오 넥스트 데이 잇 마잇 히 곤.

Original English: But already he had composed himself.
English: but already he had composed himself.
Hindi: बट ऑलरेडी ही हैड कंपोज़्ड हिम्सेल्फ.
Korean: 벗 알레디 히 해드 컴포즈드 힘셀프.

Original English: Zilla relaxed her sour mouth long enough to sigh her satisfaction.
English: zilla relaxed her sour mouth long enough to sigh her satisfaction.
Hindi: ज़िला रिलैक्स्ड हर सौर माउथ लॉन्ग इनफ टू साइ हर सैटिस्फैक्शन.
Korean: 질라 릴랙스트 허 사우어 마우스 롱 이너프 투 사이 허 새티스팩션.

Original English: Eggshell is not good to eat.
English: eggshell is not good to eat.
Hindi: एगशेल इज़ नॉट गुड टू ईट.
Korean: 에그셸 이즈 낫 굿 투 잇.

Original English: But there was also talk of witchcraft in the village.
English: but there was also talk of witchcraft in the village.
Hindi: बट देर वज ऑल्सो टॉक अव विचक्राफ्ट इन द विलेज.
Korean: 벗 데어 워즈 알소 톡 옵 위치크래프트 인 더 빌리지.

Original English: Yea, I will tell thee.
English: yea, i will tell thee.
Hindi: ये, आई विल टेल दी.
Korean: 예이, 아이 윌 텔 디.

Original English: Hans hurled himself upon the prostrate man, striking madly with his fists.
English: hans hurled himself upon the prostrate man, striking madly with his fists.
Hindi: हैंस हर्ल्ड हिम्सेल्फ अपॉन द प्रॉस्ट्रेट मैन, स्ट्राइकिंग मैडली विद हिस फिस्ट्स.
Korean: 한즈 헐드 힘셀프 어폰 더 프로스트레이트 맨, 스트라이킹 매들리 위드 히즈 피스츠.

Original English: And he thought of Oona, and of her words.
English: and he thought of oona, and of her words.
Hindi: ऐंड ही थॉट अव ऊना, ऐंड अव हर वर्ड्स.
Korean: 앤드 히 쏘트 어브 우나, 앤드 어브 허 워즈.

Original English: Nor would it thaw out his hands and feet.
English: nor would it thaw out his hands and feet.
Hindi: नॉर वुड इट थॉ आउट हिज़ हैंड्स ऐंड फीट.
Korean: 노어 우드 잇 태우 아웃 히즈 핸즈 앤드 피트.

Original English: The Russian music player, the Count, was her obedient slave.
English: the russian music player, the count, was her obedient slave.
Hindi: द रशियन म्यूजिक प्लेयर, द काउंट, वज हर ओबीडिएंट स्लेव.
Korean: 더 러시안 뮤직 플레이어, 더 카운트, 워즈 허 오비디언트 슬레이브.

Original English: So far as flags were concerned, they were beyond all jurisdiction.
English: so far as flags were concerned, they were beyond all jurisdiction.
Hindi: सो फार ऐज़ फ्लैग्स वेर कन्सर्न्ड, दे वेर बियॉंड ऑल ज्यूरिस्डिक्शन.
Korean: 소 파 애즈 플래그즈 워 컨서언드, 데이 워 비욘드 올 저리스딕션.

Original English: New idea, he volunteered, brand new idea.
English: new idea, he volunteered, brand new idea.
Hindi: न्यू आइडिया, ही वॉलन्टीर्ड, ब्रैंड न्यू आइडिया.
Korean: 뉴 아이디어, 히 볼런티어드, 브랜드 뉴 아이디어.

Original English: Thirty pounds, said the captain with finality.
English: thirty pounds, said the captain with finality.
Hindi: थर्टी पाउंड्स, सैड द कैप्टन विद फाइनलिटी.
Korean: 써티 파운즈, 쎄드 더 캡틴 위드 파이날리티.

Original English: The very idea of it was preposterous.
English: the very idea of it was preposterous.
Hindi: द वेरी आइडिया अव इट वज़ प्रिपॉस्टरस.
Korean: 더 베리 아이디어 오브 잇 워즈 프리포스터러스.

Original English: Captain Doane's orders were swiftly obeyed.
English: captain doane's orders were swiftly obeyed.
Hindi: कैप्टन डोआन्स ऑर्डर्स वेर स्विफ्टली ओबेइड.
Korean: 캡틴 도운즈 오더즈 워 스위프트리 오베이드.

Original English: Come on, Del Mar challenged.
English: come on, del mar challenged.
Hindi: कम ऑन, डेल मार चैलेंज्ड.
Korean: 컴 안, 델 마 챌린지드.

Original English: He had a big chimpanzee that was a winner.
English: he had a big chimpanzee that was a winner.
Hindi: ही हैड अ बिग चिम्पान्ज़ी दैट वज़ अ विनर.
Korean: 히 핻 아 빅 침팬지 댓 워즈 아 위너.

Original English: I am sure it must have been some adventure.
English: i am sure it must have been some adventure.
Hindi: आई ऐम शुअर इट मस्ट हैव बीन सम एडवेंचर.
Korean: 아이 앰 슈어 잇 머스트 해브 빈 썸 어드벤처.

Original English: That Longfellow chap most likely had written countless books of poetry.
English: that longfellow chap most likely had written countless books of poetry.
Hindi: धैट लॉन्गफेलो चैप मोस्ट लाइकली हॅड रिटन काउंटलेस बुक्स ऑफ पोएट्री.
Korean: 댓 롱펠로우 챕 모스트 라이클리 해드 리튼 카운틀리스 북스 어브 포이트리.

Original English: His abnormal power of vision made abstractions take on concrete form.
English: his abnormal power of vision made abstractions take on concrete form.
Hindi: हिज़ अब्नॉर्मल पावर अव विजन मेड एब्स्ट्रैक्शन्स टेक ऑन कंक्रीट फॉर्म.
Korean: 히즈 압노멀 파워 어브 비전 메이드 앱스트랙션즈 테이크 온 콘크리트 폼.

Original English: I'll tell you, the librarian said with a brightening face.
English: i will tell you, the librarian said with a brightening face.
Hindi: आई विल टेल यू, द लाइब्रेरियन सैड विद अ ब्राइटनिंग फेस.
Korean: 아이 윌 텔 유, 더 라이브러리언 세드 위드 아 브라이트닝 페이스.

Original English: He read his fragments aloud.
English: he read his fragments aloud.
Hindi: ही रीड हिज़ फ्रैगमेंट्स अलाउड.
Korean: 히 리드 히즈 프래그먼츠 얼라우드.

Original English: Typhoid, did I tell you.
English: typhoid, did i tell you.
Hindi: टाइफॉइड, डिड आई टेल यू.
Korean: 타이포이드, 디드 아이 텔 유.

Original English: But she had become an automaton.
English: but she had become an automaton.
Hindi: बट शी हैड बिकम अन ऑटोमेटन.
Korean: 벗 쉬 햇 비컴 안 오토마톤.

Original English: At the best, they were necessary accessories.
English: at the best, they were necessary accessories.
Hindi: ऐट द बेस्ट, दे वर नेसेसरी अक्सेसरीज़.
Korean: 앳 더 베스트, 데이 워 네세서리 악세서리즈.

Original English: You were making them talk shop, Ruth charged him.
English: you were making them talk shop, ruth charged him.
Hindi: यू वर मेकिंग धेम टॉक शॉप, रूथ चार्ज्ड हिम.
Korean: 유 워 메이킹 덤 톡 샵, 루스 차지드 힘.
